NK030(a)002:1: gnyis pa nang dbang gi chu bo las /
NK030(a)002:2: sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i dbang gi cho ga bzhugs so /
NK030(a)002:5: khro bo dam pa brgyan gyi mngon pa rtogs pa mtshams med pa lnga'i dri ma 'khrud par /
NK030(a)002:7: bla ma dang dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:8: chos sku zhi ba'i tshul las ma g.yos kyang //
NK030(a)002:9: gzug dag gar dgu'i ro yis bdud dpung 'joms //
NK030(a)002:10: kun bzang he ru ka dpal lha'i lha //
NK030(a)002:11: gang zhig gus pas rab tu phyag 'tshal lo /
NK030(a)002:13: / 'di nyid kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur thob cing //
NK030(a)002:14: dam tshig dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK030(a)002:15: de ltar mngon par rtogs pa 'di la don bzhis shes par bya ste /
NK030(a)002:16: sngon du bya ba'i rim pa dang //
NK030(a)002:17: sngon gyi gleng bzhis khro bor bsgom pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK030(a)002:18: ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa dngos dang /
NK030(a)002:20: de la sngon du bya ba'i rim pa rnams legs
NK030(a)002:21: par tshar nas dngos gzhi khro bor sgom pa'i dgos
NK030(a)002:22: pa rnams ni / 'dzin pa'i dbang gi sdug bsngal zhing //
NK030(a)002:23: gdug pa srid gsum 'dul ba yi //
NK030(a)002:24: nga rgyal chen po bstan pa'i phyir //
NK030(a)002:25: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom /
NK030(a)002:26: de'i don gzung 'dzin gyi rgyud mthu ba rtas pas
NK030(a)002:27: sngags la gol ba'i rgyud gdug pa ru tra khro
NK030(a)002:28: bo'i nga rgyal gyis btul ba bzhin /
NK030(a)002:29: bdag gi zhe sdang la sogs pa'i dug gsum sku gsum du gnas gyur pa'i thabs la /
NK030(a)002:30: snang stong gnyis med kyi ting 'dzin bsgom par bya /
NK030(a)002:33: rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa brten pa lha bskyed dang gsum las /
NK030(a)002:35: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos /
NK030(a)002:36: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis gsang //
NK030(a)002:37: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK030(a)002:38: skyes pa nyid nas skye ba med //
NK030(a)002:39: de'i don phyi nang gi gdos pa thams cad rang gi sems su snang ba'i phyir /
NK030(a)002:40: ma skyes pa'i skyes pa gnyis su med pa'i de
NK030(a)002:41: bzhin nyid bsgom pa smra bsam las 'das pa'i ngang
NK030(a)002:43: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK030(a)002:44: e ma kun tu bzang mo ni //
NK030(a)002:45: bde chen spros bral thig le la //
NK030(a)002:46: stong pa nyid du rab gsal ba'i //
NK030(a)002:47: snying rje'i yul ni sgom par bya //
NK030(a)002:49: bdag dang yul gnyis ka mi dmigs par /
NK030(a)002:50: rang byung gi ye shes nam mkha' lta bur sangs
NK030(a)002:51: rgyas par gsal ba'i snying rje chen po'i ye shes
NK030(a)002:52: sgom mo / rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK030(a)002:53: mkha' mnyam dbyings nyid dag pa las //
NK030(a)002:54: bde gshegs thugs kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK030(a)002:55: sems nyid yi ge h+aum du snang //
NK030(a)002:56: thams cad ye shes 'byung gnas rgyu //
NK030(a)002:57: de'i don rang gi rig pa thabs dang shes rab
NK030(a)002:58: dbyer med pa nyid yi ge h+aum mthing nag 'bar
NK030(a)002:59: bar sgom / de yongs su gyur ba las /
NK030(a)002:60: badz+ra he ru ka gar dgu dang ldan pa sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK030(a)002:61: rdo rje rtse lnga pa dang thod pa 'dzin pa rin po che dang /
NK030(a)002:62: dur khrod kyi chas brgyad dang rus pa'i brgyan gyis spras pa /
NK030(a)002:65: mi mgo skam po lngas dbu brgyan pa //
NK030(a)002:66: rlon pa'i do shal byas pa mkha' la sgom //
NK030(a)002:67: rten gzhal yas khang sgom pa ni //
NK030(a)002:69: e yam ram kem ram b+h+r+au rnams su gyur /
NK030(a)002:70: e las chos kyi 'byung gnas gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba dang bcas pa'i nang du /
NK030(a)002:71: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor gzhu brdungs ba'i rnam
NK030(a)002:72: pa mchog ma dang 'chang gzung la yam dang ba
NK030(a)002:73: dan gyis mtshan pa de'i steng du /
NK030(a)002:74: ram las rak+ta'i rgya mtsho gting mtha' med pa zlum po ra yis mtshan pa /
NK030(a)002:75: de'i steng du kem las keng rus kyi ri rab dpag tshad brgyad khri gyen du 'phags pa /
NK030(a)002:76: gnam lcags kyi gzer gyis gda' pa /
NK030(a)002:78: mchur bzhir khro bo rdo rje rtse lnga pa phyed pas gtams pa la keng gis mtshan pa /
NK030(a)002:79: de'i steng du ram las me'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum mar nag ram gyis mtshan pa /
NK030(a)002:80: h+aum de'i dkyil gzhal yas brten gyur pa'i rlung nag
NK030(a)002:81: dkyil 'khor rdo rje rgya gram dbang chen gtams pas
NK030(a)002:82: kyang / thams cad 'degs pa'i shugs dang ldan pa //
NK030(a)002:84: de'i steng du b+h+r+au las 'od zer 'phros pas sems can gyis don byas /
NK030(a)002:87: b+han+d+ha dz+nya na tsakra man+dala la de ba ti ra nan tu kri tsakra nan tam ram bam /
NK030(a)002:89: gzhal yas khang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa rdo rje'i ra ba zlum po //
NK030(a)002:90: gru chad bzhi pa 'khyams gnyis sgo bzhi mu khyud dang bcas pa /
NK030(a)002:91: nang du mchog brgyad kyi ka ba'i steng du //
NK030(a)002:92: tshangs pa'i gdung bzhi mig mang ris su phub pa la /
NK030(a)002:93: zhing gi lcam dang gral ma la sbrul nag gi thog byas pa /
NK030(a)002:94: zhing gi sgo la skar ma'i zer sgrul 'bar ba'i skyes bu /
NK030(a)002:95: rus spal gyis ma them byas shing //
NK030(a)002:96: gru chad thod skam gyis rtsigs pa sgo dang rtsig
NK030(a)002:97: pa phyi nang nyis rim gyi sgo phyi ma bzhi'i
NK030(a)002:98: thad sor / zhing gi ka ba bzhi bzhis bteg pa'i steng du /
NK030(a)002:99: rta babs bang rim bzhi dang ldan pa'i steng du chos kyi 'khor lo dang /
NK030(a)002:100: keng rus gyis gdugs byas pa zhing dang chu srin
NK030(a)002:101: gyi rgyal mtshan la sogs pas mdzes par brgyan pa
NK030(a)002:102: / phyi'i 'khyams rin chen sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang pa /
NK030(a)002:103: nang nas rim pa bzhin nag po ljang khu dmar po ser po /
NK030(a)002:104: dkar po'i rtsigs pa lnga dang ldan pa //
NK030(a)002:105: rtsigs pa'i steng du rin po che'i pha gu ser
NK030(a)002:106: po la d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa 'chang
NK030(a)002:107: ba zla g.yab dang pu shus mdzes par brgyan pa
NK030(a)002:108: / dbus byur por gyur pa'i steng du rdo rje rtse lnga pas mtshan pa /
NK030(a)002:109: rtsigs pa'i rtsa ba'i stegs bu la /
NK030(a)002:111: / 'dod yon gyi lha mo rnams kyis he ru ka la mchod pa /
NK030(a)002:112: 'khyams nang ma thod pa'i rtsig pa byas shing /
NK030(a)002:113: nyi zla'i mthong khung dang gza' brgyad kyi glo skar /
NK030(a)002:114: thod pa'i kha bad las rgyu zhags 'phyangs pas h+aum
NK030(a)002:115: gi thog dang me 'bar ba snol bar 'khrug pa
NK030(a)002:116: / de lta bu'i gzhal yas khang gi phyi rol
NK030(a)002:117: du dur khrod brgyad phyogs skyong ba brgyad shing brgyad
NK030(a)002:123: grub pa thob pa'i rnal 'byor pa brgyad /
NK030(a)002:130: sha za la sogs pas gang ba'i /
NK030(a)002:131: gzhal yas khang gi nang du /
NK030(a)002:132: 'khor rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang bcas pa'i lte ba'i dbus su /
NK030(a)002:133: bdud bzhi'i ngo bo ru tra pho mo byi chings
NK030(a)002:134: su snol ba'i steng na dom brgyad gnyis gnyis gshibs
NK030(a)002:135: te phyogs bzhir bltas pa'i steng na nyi ma /
NK030(a)002:136: rtsibs shar du dri za'i steng du khyu mchog brgyad kyi steng du nyi ma /
NK030(a)002:137: lhor gshin rje'i steng du ma he brgyad kyi steng du nyi ma /
NK030(a)002:138: nub tu klu byi chings kyi steng du gzig brgyad kyi steng du nyi ma /
NK030(a)002:139: byang du gnod sbyin brgyad kyi steng du nyi ma /
NK030(a)002:140: rtsibs mchan rnams su ko'u ri la sogs pa'i gdan re re la /
NK030(a)002:142: / 'khyams nang mar sing ha ma'i gdan ro rlon pa re'o //
NK030(a)002:143: sgo nang mar sgo ma'i gdan ro re re /
NK030(a)002:144: 'khyams phyi mar dbang po rnams kyi gdan zhing skam po re re bsam la /
NK030(a)002:145: dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa'i //
NK030(a)002:146: khrag gi rgya mtsho 'khrug pa'i dkyil /
NK030(a)002:147: keng rus chen po'i ri rab gyis //
NK030(a)002:148: stong gi 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK030(a)002:149: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK030(a)002:150: phyogs bcu rgya yangs ma chad pa'i //
NK030(a)002:151: phyi dang nang med kun tu nang /
NK030(a)002:154: gru chad bzhi'i rnam par brgyan //
NK030(a)002:155: kun du gru bzhi sgo khyud ldan /
NK030(a)002:158: thod sbrul sna tshogs nyi zlas brjid /
NK030(a)002:161: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK030(a)002:162: gtum po dom gyi spar bas ni /
NK030(a)002:163: dbang phyug lha chen la sogs gzungs //
NK030(a)002:165: de rnams kyis rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'o //
NK030(a)002:166: brten pa lha bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)002:167: bdag sngon gyi sangs rgyas yin pa'i phyir bdag gi sras su de bzhin gshegs pa bye ba dang /
NK030(a)002:168: rigs mi nub cing lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su bdag bya'o //
NK030(a)002:170: badz+ra kro ta sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:172: dbus kyi gdan gyi steng du /
NK030(a)002:173: badz+ra he ru ka sku mdog mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi pa /
NK030(a)002:174: zhal g.yas dkar ba g.yon dmar ba /
NK030(a)002:176: phyag g.yas kyi dang po rdo rje rtse dgu pa /
NK030(a)002:179: g.yon gyi dang po dril bu /
NK030(a)002:180: bar ba thod pa khrag gi bkang ba /
NK030(a)002:181: tha ma na 'jig rten snams pa /
NK030(a)002:184: gar dgu dang ldan pa bskyed //
NK030(a)002:185: h+aum nges pa las ni rdo rje che //
NK030(a)002:186: de las dpal chen he ru ka  /
NK030(a)002:187: 'bar ba chen po gar dgu yis /
NK030(a)002:189: / 'jigs pa yis ni dus ltar drag /
NK030(a)002:191: badz+ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:193: lus dang grib ma'i tshul du he ru ka'i thugs ka nas yum bton te /
NK030(a)002:194: sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK030(a)002:195: g.yas pa yab la 'khyud cing rdo rje snams pa /
NK030(a)002:196: g.yon pa dung dmar gtso la stobs pa /
NK030(a)002:197: gnyis ka dur khrod chas brgyad dang /
NK030(a)002:199: rin po che la sogs pas brgyan par bskyed /
NK030(a)002:200: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK030(a)002:201: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK030(a)002:202: khro rgyal ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK030(a)002:203: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas ni //
NK030(a)002:204: khro mo dbang phyug sngon phyung nas /
NK030(a)002:205: he he dgyes pa'i gzi mdangs kyi /
NK030(a)002:206: rin chen pad+ma rgyas mdzad nas //
NK030(a)002:207: gnyis med 'khril ba'i dgyes pas thim //
NK030(a)002:209: de nas yab yum gyi mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs te /
NK030(a)002:211: badz+ra pad+ma man+da la ces pas /
NK030(a)002:213: rdo rje sngon po rtse lnga pa rwa lnga la yab kyi 'bru lngas mtshan pa /
NK030(a)002:214: rdo rje'i bum pa'i nang du /
NK030(a)002:217: rtse mor phata nag pos gcad pa /
NK030(a)002:218: yum gyi mkha' pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i ze'u 'bru la ahs mtshan pa /
NK030(a)002:219: dbus dang phyogs bzhi'i 'dab ma la /
NK030(a)002:221: de nas brdas bskul ste sa ma ya stam /
NK030(a)002:223: a nu ra ga ya mi /
NK030(a)002:226: ces yab yum dgyes pa'i rol byang sems 'phros pas /
NK030(a)002:227: byang sems dkar dmar 'dres pa las /
NK030(a)002:228: h'u h'u h'u bi shwa badz+ra kro ta /
NK030(a)002:229: dz+wa la man+da la phata phata phata /
NK030(a)002:232: khro bo dpag tu med pa byang sems las /
NK030(a)002:234: / 'phros nas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams cad khyab par g.yos pas /
NK030(a)002:235: gdug pa can thams cad cig car du brtul bar gyur /
NK030(a)002:237: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:239: stong pa'i ngang las dbus kyi khro bo thams cad
NK030(a)002:240: gcig du gyur nas badz+ra he ru ka yab yum
NK030(a)002:241: gyi rang bzhin du gyur te /
NK030(a)002:242: gong du bshad pa'i yab yum la thim /
NK030(a)002:243: chos kyi dbyings gyi ye shes kyi ngo bor gyur /
NK030(a)002:245: bud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:247: shar du me long lta bu'i ye shes las su
NK030(a)002:248: gyur pa'i b+hud+d+ha he ru ka sku mdog smug go
NK030(a)002:251: rat+na kro ti shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:252: lhor mnyam nyid ye shes las gyur pa'i rat+na he ru ka lho'i gdan thog tu bskyed pa'o //
NK030(a)002:254: pad+ma kro ti shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:256: nub tu sor sor rtog pa'i ye shes las gyur pa'i khro bo thams cad gcig tu gyur nas /
NK030(a)002:257: pad+ma he ru ka yab yum gyi skur gyur pa'o //
NK030(a)002:259: karma kro ti shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:261: byang du bya ba grub pa'i ye shes las gyur
NK030(a)002:262: pa'i khro bo thams cad karma he ru ka yab
NK030(a)002:263: yum du gyur ste ljang nag go /
NK030(a)002:264: de nas byang sems las ha brgyad bton /
NK030(a)002:265: rtsibs mchan la phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi la gnas pa'i khro mo brgyad du gyur /
NK030(a)002:266: de nas yab yum rol pa'i byang sems las he brgyad bton /
NK030(a)002:267: 'khyams nang ma'i phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi la gnas pa'i seng ha ma brgyad du gyur /
NK030(a)002:268: yang byang sems las phata bzhi bton //
NK030(a)002:269: sgo nang ma bzhir gnas pa'i sgo ma bzhir gyur /
NK030(a)002:271: / 'di rnams kyi sngags yid kyis brjod nas bskyed kyang chog gsungs /
NK030(a)002:272: lha thams cad gtso bo la zhal bstan la ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK030(a)002:273: de rnams bdag sras yin la /
NK030(a)002:274: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su bdag byas ste /
NK030(a)002:275: bdag rgyu'i he ru ka mtshon gang ba de gtso bo'i thugs kha nas byung ste /
NK030(a)002:276: srin po'i bu da gu'i cha byed bzung nas shar sgor phyin la /
NK030(a)002:277: thal mo sbyar ba la sogs pa byas nas sgrib
NK030(a)002:278: pa sbyang phyir rigs de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras kyis
NK030(a)002:279: // zhes gsol ba gdab pa ni //
NK030(a)002:280: sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni /
NK030(a)002:281: 'jig rten ma lus thams cad kun //
NK030(a)002:282: rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyor bas na //
NK030(a)002:283: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor gcig /
NK030(a)002:284: ces pas gsol ba gdab par bya /
NK030(a)002:285: de nas lha thams cad kyi sbyor mtsham su //
NK030(a)002:286: sku gsung thugs kyi gnas gsum las //
NK030(a)002:287: +aahh+aum ces pa 'od 'phros pas lus ngag yid gsum gyi dri ma dag /
NK030(a)002:288: bdag gi sems gser zhun ma lta bu 'am dngul
NK030(a)002:289: zhun ma lta bu dkar ldeng ldeng gnas pa las
NK030(a)002:291: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan par gyur nas /
NK030(a)002:292: byang sems kyi chu de h+aum mthing nag gcig tu gyur /
NK030(a)002:294: h+aum de zla ba'i steng du bzhag la rlung gis btegs //
NK030(a)002:295: g.yas phyogs nas lha rnams la bskor ba lan gsum byas /
NK030(a)002:296: gtso bo'i thugs kar thim pas yab yum rol 'od du zhu ba las /
NK030(a)002:299: rtsa ba'i lha khrag 'thung yab yum dang khro mo nyi shu yang 'od du zhu /
NK030(a)002:300: dbus kyi gdan thog na gnas la //
NK030(a)002:301: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i ye shes zer gyi lus rtogs sbyangs /
NK030(a)002:302: gser zhun lta bu'i sems dag las //
NK030(a)002:304: thugs kar thim nas sku'i dbyings //
NK030(a)002:305: rdo rje las byung yum gyi mkha' /
NK030(a)002:307: / chos kun byang chub sems su gnas //
NK030(a)002:308: lha rnams so so'i snying po'i sgra //
NK030(a)002:309: h+aum h+aa he phata ces byung nas ni //
NK030(a)002:310: byang chub sems su gcig par thim /
NK030(a)002:312: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+aii he ru ka /
NK030(a)002:313: ma h+aa tsan+ta sa t+wa dusha da na ta ka
NK030(a)002:314: ha na d+ha ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata
NK030(a)002:315: / badz+ra da ra ma h+aa kro ti dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:317: dbus kyi gdan gyis steng du /
NK030(a)002:318: badz+ra he ru ka zhal gsum phyag drug pa gong du bshad pa'i mtshan nyid bstan pa /
NK030(a)002:319: zhabs g.yas brkyang bas ru tra'i gdan la gnan pa /
NK030(a)002:320: g.yon bskum pas ru tra mo'i nu ma brang nas rdzis pa /
NK030(a)002:321: skabs 'dir lha kun tshang bar bskyed na /
NK030(a)002:322: sku mdog phyag mtshan 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin shes par bya /
NK030(a)002:323: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen pa //
NK030(a)002:324: bsgrub pa dang ni bsgrub chen po //
NK030(a)002:326: bde ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor spro //
NK030(a)002:327: sangs rgyas sprin tshogs ma lus la //
NK030(a)002:328: dgyes snyam mchog gi mchod pa stim //
NK030(a)002:329: de nas yab kyi gsang ba'i gnas byin gyis rlobs pa nas /
NK030(a)002:330: yum gyi mkha' byin gyis rlobs pa 'dra la /
NK030(a)002:334: yab yum gnyis snyom par zhugs pa'i bde ba chen po'i sgras /
NK030(a)002:337: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpal thams cad spyan drangs zhal du zhugs thugs khar zhu /
NK030(a)002:338: yab kyi gsang ba'i gnas nas babs /
NK030(a)002:339: yum gyi mkhar thig le bzhir gyur //
NK030(a)002:340: de rnams nyi zla kha sbyor gyi spros pas byang sems la h+aum ha he phata /
NK030(a)002:341: zhes pa'i yi ge 'bru bzhir gyur //
NK030(a)002:342: de rnams yongs su gyur pa las /
NK030(a)002:343: rtsa ba'i lha rnams yum gyi mkhar tshar bar bskyed la /
NK030(a)002:344: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK030(a)002:345: sa t+wa dush+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa
NK030(a)002:347: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:348: de'i sngags rnams mgo dpyad dang 'jug gi 'agre'o /
NK030(a)002:349: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa /
NK030(a)002:350: sarba ta th+aa ga ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri sarba dush+tana h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:351: badz+ra he ru ka yab yum gyi sngags brjod pas /
NK030(a)002:352: yum gyis mkha' nas badz+ra he ru ka yab yum thon //
NK030(a)002:353: sku mdog phyag mtshan gong ltar gyur pas gtso bo yab yum la thim /
NK030(a)002:354: sarba ta th+aa ga ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri sarba dush+tana h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:355: zhes b+hud+ha he ru ka'i sngags brjod pas bud+d+ha he
NK030(a)002:356: ru ka yum gyi mkha' las shar rtsibs su khyu
NK030(a)002:358: sku mdog smug nag zhal gsum phyag drug pa //
NK030(a)002:359: zhal g.yas dkar g.yon ser dbus smug po /
NK030(a)002:360: phyag g.yas kyi dang po na 'khor lo //
NK030(a)002:362: tha ma na ti ra dril bu /
NK030(a)002:363: g.yon gyi dang po na dril bu //
NK030(a)002:365: tha ma na dri shul bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:366: phyag dang po gnyis yum la 'khyud pa //
NK030(a)002:367: yum gyi phyag g.yas yab la 'khyud pa //
NK030(a)002:368: g.yon dung dmar gtso la stobs pa /
NK030(a)002:369: yum thams cad zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa sku mdog gtso bo dang mthun pa brgyan yang 'dra //
NK030(a)002:370: phyag mtshan g.yas pa'i gtso bo dang po dang mthun la //
NK030(a)002:372: rad na ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK030(a)002:373: ma h+aa su r+ya ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri ba ta b+aa mu khe h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:375: lho ru rat+na he ru ka yum gyi mkha' las thon /
NK030(a)002:376: gdan thog tu sku mdog ser nag zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK030(a)002:377: g.yas sngo g.yon mar dbus ser //
NK030(a)002:378: phyag g.yas dang po na rin chen bar ma rdo rje //
NK030(a)002:380: g.yon dang po na dril bu /
NK030(a)002:383: phyag dang po gnyis kyis yum la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)002:384: pad+ma ma h+aa h+r+aihshu ta pa ma te pad+ma ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri kh+aa hi h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:385: ces pas nub tu pad+ma he ru ka yum gyi mkha' la thon /
NK030(a)002:386: sku mdog dmar nag zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK030(a)002:387: zhal g.yas dkar g.yon ser dbus dmar ba phyag g.yas dang po na pad+ma /
NK030(a)002:390: g.yon gyi dang po na dril bu /
NK030(a)002:392: tha ma na gsang ba'i rnge'u chung /
NK030(a)002:393: phyag dang po gnyis yum la 'khyud pa //
NK030(a)002:394: yum pad+ma kro ti dmar mo pad+ma dang dung dmar bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)002:395: karma ma h+aa sarba mo g+ha ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri bi shwa h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:397: byang du karma he ru ka yum gyi mkha' las byang gi gdan thog tu 'khod /
NK030(a)002:398: sku mdog ljang nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhal g.yas dkar g.yon dmar ba /
NK030(a)002:400: g.yas kyi dang po sna tshogs rdo rje /
NK030(a)002:403: g.yon gyi dang po na dril bu /
NK030(a)002:405: tha ma na thong gshol bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:406: phyag dang po gnyis yum la 'khyud pa //
NK030(a)002:407: yum kar ma kro ti sna tshogs rdo rje dang dung dmar bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)002:408: yab yum bcu po rus pa dang rin po che dang dur khrod kyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK030(a)002:410: sgeg pa dpal ba mi sdugs pa //
NK030(a)002:411: rgod pa drag shul 'jigs su rung //
NK030(a)002:412: snying rje rngams dang zhi ba yis //
NK030(a)002:413: gar dgu'i nyams dang ldan pa nyid /
NK030(a)002:414: yum rnams la rus pa'i rgyan dang /
NK030(a)002:415: mi mgo skam po'i do shal byas pa /
NK030(a)002:416: gzig gi lpags pa'i sham thabs can no //
NK030(a)002:417: yang 'khor lo'i rtsibs mchan nang mar khro mo nyi shu so so'i gdan re re bsam /
NK030(a)002:418: yum gyi mkha' la ha las koo ri sogs bton te /
NK030(a)002:421: yum gyis mkha' las goo ri thon te /
NK030(a)002:422: shar gyi rtsibs mchan la goo ri sngon mo phyag g.yas pas zhing dbyug g.yon pas ban+d+ha bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:424: yum gyi mkha' las thon pa kun la 'gre //
NK030(a)002:425: lhor tsoo ri ma ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa /
NK030(a)002:427: nub kyi rtsibs mchan la pra mo dmar mo chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan bsnams pa //
NK030(a)002:430: b+ae ta ljang nag phyag g.yas pas rdo rje 'chang zhing /
NK030(a)002:431: g.yon pa zhing chung za ba /
NK030(a)002:433: shar lho'i rtsibs mchan la puk+ka si dmar ser phyag
NK030(a)002:434: g.yon pa zhing chung bsnams shing g.yas pas de'i rgyu
NK030(a)002:435: ma 'dren pa / badz+ra g+hasma r+ai ha /
NK030(a)002:436: lho nub kyi rtsibs mchan la g+hasma ri ljang khu /
NK030(a)002:437: phyag g.yon pas thod pa dung dmar gang ba bsnams shing /
NK030(a)002:438: g.yas pa rdo rje'i skya bas dkrug pa /
NK030(a)002:440: nub byang gi rtsibs mchan la sme sh+aa ni mthing
NK030(a)002:441: kha phyag gnyis kyis byis pa'i snying zhal du gsol
NK030(a)002:443: byang shar gyi rtsibs mchan la /
NK030(a)002:444: tsan+da li ser skya phyag gnyis kyis zhing khog pa'i stod smad 'phral ba /
NK030(a)002:447: khyams nang ma'i phyogs mtshams su /
NK030(a)002:448: badz+ra seng ha mu kha he /
NK030(a)002:449: shar du seng ha mu kha smug nag seng ge'i
NK030(a)002:450: mgo bo can phyag gnyis brang khar bsnol zhing kha'i
NK030(a)002:451: nang du ro thogs nas ral pa bsigs pa /
NK030(a)002:452: badz+ra bya g+h+ri mu kha he /
NK030(a)002:453: lhor b+y+aa g+h+ri ma dmar mo stag gi mgo can
NK030(a)002:454: phyag gnyis thur du bsnol nas mig gnyis 'bur tshugs
NK030(a)002:455: su lta ba / badz+ra sri g+ha la mu khe he /
NK030(a)002:456: nub tu sri la ma nag mo wa'i mgo can phyag g.yas spu gri thogs shing /
NK030(a)002:457: g.yon pa rgyu ma gzung nas khrag ldag pa //
NK030(a)002:458: badz+ra shwa na mu kha he /
NK030(a)002:459: byang du shwa na sku mdog mthing nag spyang mo'i
NK030(a)002:460: mgo bo can phyag gnyis ro'i kha phye nas mig
NK030(a)002:462: badz+ra kri ta mu kha he /
NK030(a)002:463: gru chad kyi shar lhor kri d+ha ma dmar ser
NK030(a)002:464: bya rgod kyi mgo can zhing chen phrag pa la
NK030(a)002:465: bkal nas kong rus phyag du thogs pa /
NK030(a)002:466: badz+ra kam ka mu kh+aa he /
NK030(a)002:467: lho nub tu kam ka mu kha dmar nag dur bya'i mgo can /
NK030(a)002:468: zhing chen phrag pa la bkal nas phyag gnyis kyi 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)002:469: badz+ra kh+aa kha mu kha he /
NK030(a)002:470: nub byang du kh+aa kha ma nag mo bya rog
NK030(a)002:471: gi mgo can phyag g.yon na ban+d+ha bsnams shing g.yas
NK030(a)002:472: na ral gri thogs nas blo snying za ba /
NK030(a)002:473: badz+ra u lu ka mu kha he /
NK030(a)002:474: byang shar du u lu ma mthing ka 'ug pa'i mgo can /
NK030(a)002:475: phyag g.yas pa rdo rje g.yon pa ral gri thogs pa /
NK030(a)002:476: thams cad gcer bu rus pa'i rgyan lngas brgyan pa /
NK030(a)002:477: dur khrod rin po che'i rgyan gyis mdzes pa //
NK030(a)002:478: sgo nang ma bzhir yum gyi mkha' las /
NK030(a)002:479: badz+ra ar+ya re dza b+ai d+ham dza /
NK030(a)002:480: shar sgor rta gdong ma dkar mo //
NK030(a)002:482: g.yon pa na thod pa khrag gis bkang ba bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:483: badz+ra ha ya mu khi h+aum /
NK030(a)002:484: lho sgor phag gdong ma ser mo phyag gnyis rgyu ma'i zhags pa /
NK030(a)002:485: phag rgod kyi mche bas mtshan pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:487: nub sgor seng ge'i mgo can dmar mo phyag gnyis lcags sgrogs bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:488: badz+ra b+ha smi ba la ya ba ti ho /
NK030(a)002:489: byang sgor spyang khu'i mgo can sna tshogs mdog /
NK030(a)002:490: zhal dang spyan gnyis nas zhal gyi bar dkar po /
NK030(a)002:491: zhal gyis 'og nas sked pa'i bar dmar skya /
NK030(a)002:494: phyag gnyis dril bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:495: rgyan cha lugs rnams gong dang mthun la /
NK030(a)002:496: 'di yan rnams yum gyi mkha' las sngags brjod pas rang gi gnas su skyed pa'o //
NK030(a)002:497: dbang mo rnams khyams phyi ma la phyogs re re
NK030(a)002:498: gdan zhing skam po drug drug 'god la sngags brjod
NK030(a)002:499: pa tsam gyis krong krong bskyed /
NK030(a)002:501: b+h+yo ma nu rag sha si srin mo smug nag g.yag gi mgo can /
NK030(a)002:502: phyag g.yon pas thod khrag bsnams pa //
NK030(a)002:503: dbang mo thams g.yas pas rdo rje thugs khar 'dzin pa kun la 'gre /
NK030(a)002:505: tshangs pa dmar ser sbrul gyi mgo can phyag g.yon rdo rje rtse lnga pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:506: b+h+yo ro'u dri lha chen dkar ljang gzig gi mgo can phyag g.yas tri shul 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)002:509: srin mo'i mgo can phyag g.yon pa 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:511: gzhon nu dmar mo pha wam gi mgo can phyag g.yon pa mdung thung bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:513: brgya byin dkar mo dred kyi mgo can phyag g.yon pa bam dbyug 'dzin pa shar du gnas pa'o /
NK030(a)002:515: rdo rje dmar mo dom gyi mgo can /
NK030(a)002:516: phyag ga yon pas dung chos kyi nang nas tsan dan gyi chu 'thung ba /
NK030(a)002:517: b+h+yo a mri ta bdud rtsi dmar mo /
NK030(a)002:521: zla ba dkar mo sdig pa'i mgo can /
NK030(a)002:522: g.yon pa me tog spun d+ha ri bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:524: be con ldan ljang nag khra'i mgo can /
NK030(a)002:525: g.yon pa dbyug tho bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:527: srin mo dmar mo wa'i mgo can dung chos kyi nang nas khrag 'thung ba /
NK030(a)002:529: za ba ljang nag stag gi mgo can g.yon pas rgyu ma 'dren pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:532: dga' ba dmar mo rgod kyi mgo can /
NK030(a)002:535: stobs chen dmar mo rta'i mgo can g.yon pas gshol 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)002:536: b+h+yo e ka tsa ri ni /
NK030(a)002:537: rdo rje ser mo khyung gi mgo can g.yon pas spu gri bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:539: 'dod pa dmar mo khyi'ii mgo can mda' gzhu 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)002:541: nor bsrung dkar mo pu shud kyi mgo can g.yon pas bum pa 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)002:543: rlung lha sngon mo sha ba'i mgo can ba dan 'dzin pa nub du gnas pa'o //
NK030(a)002:544: b+h+yo ma h+aa m+aa ra na /
NK030(a)002:545: gsod byed ljang nag spyang ki'i mgo can g.yon pas ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)002:547: me mo dmar mo skyin gyi mgo can g.yon pa gsal shing 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)002:549: phag mo nag mo phag gi mgo can zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)002:551: rgan byed dmar mo kha kha'i mgo can g.yon zhing chung bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:553: sna chen dkar mo glang gi mgo can g.yon pas thod khrag zhal du stobs pa /
NK030(a)002:555: chu lha dkar mo sbrul gyi mgo can zhags pa 'dzin pa byang du gnas pa'o /
NK030(a)002:556: b+h+yo badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa li /
NK030(a)002:557: rdo rje nag po khu byug gi mgo can lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)002:559: rdo rje ser mo ra'i mgo can zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)002:561: rdo rje dmar mo seng ge'i mgo can lcagala sgrog bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:563: rdo rje ljang nag skya ka'i mgo can dril bu bsnams pa'o //
NK030(a)002:564: phyi ma bzhi po phyogs kyi sgo bzhir rim pa bzhin du gnas so //
NK030(a)002:565: de nas lha thams cad h+aum h+aa he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK030(a)002:567: me dpung gi dbus na gnas so //
NK030(a)002:568: dbang mo rnams kyi sngags gyi mgor b+h+yo btags par bya'o //
NK030(a)002:569: sgo ba rnams la gdan zhing skam po re bsam /
NK030(a)002:570: de la sogs par phyag rgyar bcas //
NK030(a)002:571: rnams grol rim par thob par 'gyur //
NK030(a)002:572: dag pa'i ye shes kyis sbyangs ba //
NK030(a)002:573: smos ci dgos ta de nyid yin //
NK030(a)002:574: smug nag sngo nag ser nag dang /
NK030(a)002:575: dmar nag ljang nag 'jig pa'i sku //
NK030(a)002:576: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bsgrad //
NK030(a)002:577: ko rlon gos ni sna tshogs gyon //
NK030(a)002:578: rngam pa'i sgra chen 'jigs par sgrog //
NK030(a)002:579: sbrul dang thod 'phreng nyi zlar bcas //
NK030(a)002:581: rdo rje dung chen gang pa dang //
NK030(a)002:582: ral gri dgra sta gshol la sogs //
NK030(a)002:583: rang gi lag cha sna tshogs ldan //
NK030(a)002:585: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya dang //
NK030(a)002:586: sgo bzhi phyag rgya rab mdzes shing //
NK030(a)002:587: slas dang byi mo tshogs kyi gtso //
NK030(a)002:588: bcu gnyis dang ni brgyad kyis mdzes //
NK030(a)002:589: rang gi stan dang lag char bcas /
NK030(a)002:590: ci bgyis zhes te chas ste gnas //
NK030(a)002:591: de ltar dkyil 'khor gsal bkod nas /
NK030(a)002:592: mtha' dbus med par khyab pa yis /
NK030(a)002:594: / 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na /
NK030(a)002:597: de ltar bskyed pa'i lha rnams kyis dpral bar las
NK030(a)002:598: zla ba'i steng du sku rdo rje dkar po 'khor
NK030(a)002:600: mgrin par +aahls pad+ma'i steng du gsung rdo rje dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)002:601: thugs kar h+aum las thugs rdo rje mthing kha rdo
NK030(a)002:602: rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa nyi ma'i steng du
NK030(a)002:603: bskyed cing / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ka y+aa badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:604: sarba ta th+aa ga ta wa ga badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK030(a)002:605: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:606: brjod pas sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje 'chang yin mnyam pa'i nga rgyal 'dzin pa'o //
NK030(a)002:607: de nas rang gi snying ka'i h+aum las 'od zer
NK030(a)002:608: 'phros pas rang bzhin gnas nas khro bo'i dkyil 'khor
NK030(a)002:609: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i bskor ba mdun
NK030(a)002:610: gyi nam mkha' rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgyas spyan
NK030(a)002:611: drangs shing / h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo /
NK030(a)002:612: sa pa ri wa ra badz+ra sa ma dza dza h+aum bam ho /
NK030(a)002:613: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum //
NK030(a)002:615: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag gi che //
NK030(a)002:616: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor las //
NK030(a)002:617: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drangs so //
NK030(a)002:618: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor las /
NK030(a)002:620: / 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK030(a)002:621: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yin //
NK030(a)002:622: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rab tu rdzogs //
NK030(a)002:623: nye bar gyur ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK030(a)002:625: badz+ra pus pe h+aum zhes dang /
NK030(a)002:631: zhes mchod pa rnams kyis mchod /
NK030(a)002:632: badz+ra am g+hu sha dzah badz+ra pa sha h+aum /
NK030(a)002:635: zhes phyag rgya dang bcas pas gnyis su med par bstim mo //
NK030(a)002:637: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah dbang gi lha rigs lnga yab yum bzhi /
NK030(a)002:638: byang sems khro bo bcu rnams spyan drangs la mchod pas mchod cing /
NK030(a)002:639: bcom ldan de bzhin gshegs pa rnams //
NK030(a)002:640: bcom ldan bdag nyid chen mo rnams //
NK030(a)002:641: thugs rje'i rang bzhin can rnams kyis //
NK030(a)002:642: khyed kyis bdag la dbang bskur gsol //
NK030(a)002:643: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi shiny+tsa tu mam zhes gsol ba btab pas /
NK030(a)002:644: de ba rnams kyis dbang bskur rigs mas glu len /
NK030(a)002:645: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis bkra shis brjod /
NK030(a)002:646: khro bo rnams kyis bgegs bskrad dbang bskur ba'i chu rgyun gyis rkang mthil yan chad gang /
NK030(a)002:647: dri ma dag dbang bzhi rdzogs par thob /
NK030(a)002:648: lhag ma yar lud pas gtso bo yab yum la badz+ra he ru ka yab yum gyis dbu brgyan /
NK030(a)002:649: shar dang shar lho'i lha rnams la /
NK030(a)002:650: b+hud+d+ha he ru yab yum gyis dbu brgyan /
NK030(a)002:651: lho dang lho nub kyi lha thams cad la rat+na he ru yab yum gyis dbu brgyan //
NK030(a)002:652: nub dang nub byang gi lha rnams la /
NK030(a)002:653: pad+ma he ru yab yum gyis dbu brgyan /
NK030(a)002:654: byang dang byang shar gyi lha rnams la karma he ru yab yum gyis dbu brgyan pa'o /
NK030(a)002:655: ma h+aa shu nye ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:656: ma h+aa a dar sha dz+nya nabadz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:657: ma h+aa sa man ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:658: ma h+aa pra ta pra b+he sha dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:659: ma h+aa kri t+ya nush+thana ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:661: rigs lnga ye shes lnga gang yin pa'o //
NK030(a)002:663: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu ra ga swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK030(a)002:665: sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bo yin pa'i nga rgyal 'dzin pa'o //
NK030(a)002:666: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pu tsa badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:667: zhes pas mchod pa 'phrin las thams cad kyi nga rgyal bskyed do //
NK030(a)002:669: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gnyis ka dbyer med du 'gyur ba la /
NK030(a)002:670: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum //
NK030(a)002:671: zhes rig pa'i me tog dor /
NK030(a)002:672: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK030(a)002:673: thugs rje khro dpal rngams pa'i tshogs /
NK030(a)002:675: / 'bar ba'i byin brlabs rmad po che //
NK030(a)002:676: de nyid du ni bdag la gsol //
NK030(a)002:677: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya s+t+wam //
NK030(a)002:678: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya swam //
NK030(a)002:679: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya ho //
NK030(a)002:680: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya phata //
NK030(a)002:682: rang bzhin gyis lha rnams kyi thugs kha nas //
NK030(a)002:683: phata nag po grangs med pa 'phros pas //
NK030(a)002:684: bdag gi sgo gsum gyi sdig pa sbyangs nas //
NK030(a)002:685: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par bsam //
NK030(a)002:686: de'i drin gyi lan du mchod pa ni /
NK030(a)002:687: a la u li ta li ta p+aa li dash+tam
NK030(a)002:688: go n+aa roo tri kha ram yo ni kha hi
NK030(a)002:689: ho / h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo /
NK030(a)002:690: zhes pas lha rnams la mchod pa'i tshe /
NK030(a)002:691: rang bzhin ting nge 'dzin gyi lha spros nas mchod
NK030(a)002:692: pas h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo zhes pas rang rang
NK030(a)002:693: la ba stim pa ni h+aum gis rigs lnga bstim
NK030(a)002:694: / ha yis ko ri ma bsti ma he yis phra men ma phata kyi sgo ma /
NK030(a)002:695: b+h+yo yis dbang bo bstim mo //
NK030(a)002:696: ram gyi me dpung gi dbus na bzhugs so //
NK030(a)002:697: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya ho /
NK030(a)002:698: sarba dush+ta na sa ma ya mu tra pra ba na tsakra h'u phata /
NK030(a)002:699: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka
NK030(a)002:700: ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tana sa ma ya ma s+t+wam
NK030(a)002:701: / a wa stam b+ha ya ka h'u /
NK030(a)002:702: badz+ra gu h+ye tri sha ha /
NK030(a)002:704: badz+ra gu h+ye bri sha ho sa ma ya ho /
NK030(a)002:705: badz+ra gu h+ya tri sha ho /
NK030(a)002:707: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tana sa
NK030(a)002:708: ma ya ma ra pra ban tsakra ba ga sha
NK030(a)002:712: he b+ha ga wan bu re sha ti s+t+wam pa ya ka h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:714: bdag gi dngos grub ma thob kyi bar rang bzhin
NK030(a)002:715: gyi dkyil 'khor dang ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK030(a)002:716: gnyis med du bzhugs par bsam /
NK030(a)002:717: skabs 'dir thod pa tshar gsum gyis //
NK030(a)002:719: khyung gshog gis zil gyis mnan pa bskyed rdzogs dang
NK030(a)002:720: mthun par byas na rung bar 'dir gtum chen gyi
NK030(a)002:721: bstod pa / bdag med phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing //
NK030(a)002:722: byams dang snying rje dgra zin mi mnga' yang //
NK030(a)002:723: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus la mi 'da' ba'i /
NK030(a)002:725: / 'jigs byed he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:726: srid gsum 'joms pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:727: mnyam nyid ngang gi khro la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:728: khro bo longs spyod mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:729: rdo rje 'du 'phro mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:730: mi gnas mi dmigs chos skur dag pa las //
NK030(a)002:731: bdud 'dul khro bo mchog gi skur ston pa //
NK030(a)002:732: thugs rjes gzigs ldan gdug pa thabs kyi 'dul //
NK030(a)002:733: bcom ldan khro rgyal gtso la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:734: khro mo dbang phyug sku la nyer gnas shing //
NK030(a)002:735: thabs dang shes rab 'brel pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)002:736: mkha' 'gro mi zad 'bar pa'i sprin 'phro ma //
NK030(a)002:737: gdug pa 'dul mdzad yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:738: nam mkha' lus can gar yang thog med cing /
NK030(a)002:740: / 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK030(a)002:741: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK030(a)002:742: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:744: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ba na tra ni ka re ya mi /
NK030(a)002:745: ma h+aa yo gi ni pra ti pu ho /
NK030(a)002:747: sems ma rdo rje ma'i phyag rgya bca' la /
NK030(a)002:748: bde bar gshegs pa khyed sku ci 'dra ba //
NK030(a)002:749: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:750: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas la /
NK030(a)002:752: / 'gro la phan phyir bdag gis spyad //
NK030(a)002:753: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK030(a)002:754: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong na //
NK030(a)002:755: rdo rje rgyal pos byin brlabs mdzad //
NK030(a)002:756: dus ngan thal ma'i lo ka 'dir //
NK030(a)002:757: sangs rgyas mdzad bka' bdag gis spyad //
NK030(a)002:759: bdag cag bsam pa 'a grub gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:760: phyag rgya'i mchod pa bya ba ni /
NK030(a)002:761: lha gang dang gang gi phyag rgya 'cha' ba'i tshe /
NK030(a)002:762: phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan par byas te /
NK030(a)002:763: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo las kyi phyag rgya /
NK030(a)002:764: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo chos kyi phyag rgya /
NK030(a)002:765: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK030(a)002:766: spyi bo bde ba chen po'i 'khor lo phyag rgya chen po zhes dran zhing mchod /
NK030(a)002:767: badz+ra he ru ka'i phyag rgya ni /
NK030(a)002:768: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK030(a)002:769: rtse dgu rtse lnga ti ra g.yas //
NK030(a)002:770: dril bu dung dmar 'jig rten g.yon //
NK030(a)002:771: dpal chen rdo rje thabs kyi rgya //
NK030(a)002:772: shes rab yum gyis phyag rgya ni //
NK030(a)002:773: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog mthing //
NK030(a)002:774: g.yas pa shes rab thabs la ba rten //
NK030(a)002:775: g.yon pas dung dmar gtso la stobs //
NK030(a)002:776: kro ti shwa ri dbyings kyi rgya //
NK030(a)002:777: shar gyi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni //
NK030(a)002:778: g.yas dkar g.yon ser dbus smug zhal /
NK030(a)002:780: / 'khor lo rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK030(a)002:781: dril bu dung dmar tri shul g.yon //
NK030(a)002:782: dpal chen bud+d+ha thabs kyi rgya //
NK030(a)002:783: shes rab yum gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK030(a)002:784: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog smug /
NK030(a)002:785: g.yas g.yon pa kro ti lho yi g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus ser po //
NK030(a)002:786: rin chen rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK030(a)002:787: dril bu dung dmar dgra s+t+wa g.yon //
NK030(a)002:788: dpal chen rad na shes rab yum gyi zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog ser //
NK030(a)002:789: g.yas g.yon kro ti nub kyi g.yas dkar g.yon ser
NK030(a)002:790: dbus dmar pad+ma rdo rje ti ra dril bu dung
NK030(a)002:792: dpal chenapad+ma shes ra ba zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog dmar //
NK030(a)002:793: g.yas g.yon kro ti byang gi g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ljang //
NK030(a)002:794: rgya gram rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK030(a)002:795: dril bu dung dmar thong gshol dpal chen karma shes rab yum zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog ljang //
NK030(a)002:796: g.yas g.yon kro ti 'bar ba'i mchod bzhes gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK030(a)002:797: go ri ban dmar zhing dbyug sngo //
NK030(a)002:798: tsoo ri mda' gzhu 'gengs ma ser //
NK030(a)002:799: pra mo chu srin rgyal mtshan 'chang //
NK030(a)002:800: be ta byi za rdo phyar nag /
NK030(a)002:803: sme sha mthing kha byi snying za //
NK030(a)002:805: 'bar ba'i mchod seng ha kha ro snol ser seng //
NK030(a)002:806: bya g+h+ri gnas ltag bsnol mar stag /
NK030(a)002:807: sri g+ha nag mo byis ldag wa //
NK030(a)002:808: shwa na 'dral lta gathinga ka spyang //
NK030(a)002:809: gri d+ha mgrin dmar khyung mgo rgod //
NK030(a)002:810: k+aang ka zhing phrag snar mgo ring //
NK030(a)002:811: kh+aa kha kha ro ban gri nag /
NK030(a)002:812: h+au lu lcags kyu mthing tshogs 'ug  /
NK030(a)002:813: 'bar ba'i mchod sgo bzhi rab rngam phyag rgya ni //
NK030(a)002:814: rta gdong dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK030(a)002:815: phag gdong ser mo mche zhags can //
NK030(a)002:816: nyi zla lcags sgrogs me 'bar ma //
NK030(a)002:817: thal byed dril khrol sna tshogs mdog /
NK030(a)002:819: / 'bar ba'i mchod 'jig rten 'das dang 'jig rten pa'i //
NK030(a)002:820: ma mo rnams kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK030(a)002:821: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK030(a)002:822: tshangs pa dmar ser pad+ma bsnams //
NK030(a)002:823: lha chen dkar ljang tri shul la //
NK030(a)002:825: gzhon nu dmar lo dung thung 'phen //
NK030(a)002:826: brgya byin dkar mo in+t+ra gdengs //
NK030(a)002:827: rdo rje ser mo tsan dan 'thung //
NK030(a)002:828: bdud rtsi dmar mo pad+ma bsnams //
NK030(a)002:829: zla ba dkar mo pun da ri //
NK030(a)002:830: be chen ljang nag dbyug tho 'chang //
NK030(a)002:831: srin mo dmar mo dung khrag 'thung //
NK030(a)002:832: za ba ljang nag ba su 'dren //
NK030(a)002:833: dga' ba dmar mo ka dar 'chang //
NK030(a)002:834: stobs chen dmar mo gshol 'dzin ma //
NK030(a)002:835: rdo rje ser mo spu gris gcod /
NK030(a)002:838: nor bsrungs dkar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK030(a)002:839: rlung lha sngon mo ba dan 'chang //
NK030(a)002:840: gcod byed ljang nag ral gri so //
NK030(a)002:841: me mo dmar mo gsal shing 'chang //
NK030(a)002:842: phag mo nag mo mche zhags can //
NK030(a)002:843: rgyal byed dmar mo zhing chung za //
NK030(a)002:844: sna chen dkar mo thod khrag 'thung //
NK030(a)002:845: chu lha dkar mo sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK030(a)002:846: rdo rje nag mo lcags kyu 'dzin /
NK030(a)002:847: rdo rje ser mo ra mgo zhags //
NK030(a)002:848: rdo rje dmar mo lcags sgrog sdom //
NK030(a)002:849: rdo rje ljang nag dril khrol dgyes /
NK030(a)002:851: / 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK030(a)002:852: mchod bzhes dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub gsol //
NK030(a)002:853: kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa 'di //
NK030(a)002:854: bde bar gshegs so khro rgyal gtso //
NK030(a)002:855: rgyal ba rgya mtsho ye shes kyis //
NK030(a)002:856: srid pa'i rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK030(a)002:857: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK030(a)002:858: sh+r+ai pa tra na ma sarba ta th+aa ga to b+h+yo /
NK030(a)002:860: sarba tat+tam ud ga te sba ra na hi mam ga ga na kham swa h+aa /
NK030(a)002:861: phyag rgya dang zhabs bsil gyis mchod pa ni /
NK030(a)002:863: yang dag don du dag mod kyang /
NK030(a)002:865: / 'gro ba yongs kyi don slad du //
NK030(a)002:866: phyag dang zhabs gnyis bsil nas kyang //
NK030(a)002:867: rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:868: +aa ha ra a ha ra sarba badz+ra bid+ya d+ha ra pu dzi te //
NK030(a)002:869: na ma sa man ta bud+d+ha na na ga ga na kham sa ma ye swa h+aa /
NK030(a)002:871: de nas spos la sogs pa'i mchod pa ni /
NK030(a)002:872: gdugs ma dkar mo rdo rjes mtshan pa'i spos bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:873: me tog ma ser mo me tog gi za ma tog bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:874: mar me ma dmar mo mar me'i gdu bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:875: dri ma ljang khu dri'i dung chos bsnams pa nam mkhar bsgom la /
NK030(a)002:877: pa ne pem pe nu su ra to /
NK030(a)002:879: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK030(a)002:881: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK030(a)002:883: sarba ma h+aa su ka sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK030(a)002:884: sh+ri badz+ra r+aa ga d+hu pe d+hu /
NK030(a)002:889: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:890: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa grub par mdzod /
NK030(a)002:892: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK030(a)002:894: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod pa chen po thams cad dag par mdzod /
NK030(a)002:896: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod pa chen po thams cad dag cing grub par mdzod /
NK030(a)002:897: lha mo rnams gtso bo la thim //
NK030(a)002:898: de nas sman gyis mchod pa ni /
NK030(a)002:899: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK030(a)002:900: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK030(a)002:901: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga'i dngos /
NK030(a)002:902: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK030(a)002:903: rgyud lnga sems can kun sgrol ba'i //
NK030(a)002:904: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK030(a)002:905: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK030(a)002:906: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen gyis //
NK030(a)002:907: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskang ba'i mchog /
NK030(a)002:908: ces che ba'i yon tan bsam la //
NK030(a)002:909: thog mar rtsa ba'i bla ma dang //
NK030(a)002:910: sgyu 'phrul gyi bla ma rnams kyi mtshan dngos su mchod la //
NK030(a)002:911: bdud rtsi g.yon pa'i 'theb srin gyis blangs la /
NK030(a)002:913: 'di ni sngon gyi dam tshig che //
NK030(a)002:914: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK030(a)002:915: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i mchog /
NK030(a)002:916: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid 'di //
NK030(a)002:917: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK030(a)002:918: thugs rje dgongs nas bzhes su gsol //
NK030(a)002:919: bzhes nas kun du dgyes mdzod la /
NK030(a)002:920: 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK030(a)002:921: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra ti tsa ho /
NK030(a)002:922: sh+r+ai wan kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK030(a)002:923: h+aum tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru ka  /
NK030(a)002:924: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khrag 'thung lnga rnams la //
NK030(a)002:925: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK030(a)002:926: thugs rjes cher dgongs dbang dang dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)002:927: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha h+ai /
NK030(a)002:928: dpal chen sku la gnyis med lhun sbyor ba'i /
NK030(a)002:929: kro d+hi shwa ri la sogs yum chen lnga rnams la /
NK030(a)002:930: rnam dag thugs rje mthing kha mchog rnams rdo rje gsang ba'i yum //
NK030(a)002:931: ko ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams la //
NK030(a)002:932: rnam dag thugs rje rdo rje mgo brnyan za byed mche gshog can //
NK030(a)002:933: seng ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams la //
NK030(a)002:934: rnam dag thugs rje sgo bzhi rab rngams rdo rje gdong mo'i tshogs //
NK030(a)002:935: rta gdong la sogs sgo ma bzhi rnam la /
NK030(a)002:936: rnam dag thugs dpal chen 'khor tshogs badz+ra a ra li //
NK030(a)002:937: mkha' 'gro shugs 'gro ma sring rgya mtsho la //
NK030(a)002:938: rnam dag thugs ci bgyis la sogs ging dang pho nya'i tshogs /
NK030(a)002:940: / 'bar ma la sogs bka' sdod tshogs rnams la //
NK030(a)002:941: rnam dag thugs sdom la gnas shing rig 'dzin grub pa'i sa /
NK030(a)002:942: lha dang lha min phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor la //
NK030(a)002:943: rnam dag thugs dam tshig dbang dang shes rgyud gab sbas pa'i //
NK030(a)002:944: nges pa'i lung ston rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK030(a)002:945: rnam dag thugs shes pa'i khyad par rim par dbang bskur ba'i //
NK030(a)002:946: rgyal theb spyan dang kar ma'i king rnams la //
NK030(a)002:947: rnam dag thugs 'jig rten 'di dang phyi ma gnyis ka ru //
NK030(a)002:948: dam tshig gzungs kyi 'brel pa'i rdo rje mched lcam la //
NK030(a)002:949: rnam dag thugs ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK030(a)002:950: lce'i rdo rje dam tshig la /
NK030(a)002:951: rdo rje can gyi h+aum sgom ste //
NK030(a)002:952: bdud rtsi lnga la sbyar ba'i sman /
NK030(a)002:953: myong na dngos grub gsum thob 'gyur //
NK030(a)002:960: dngos grub thob pas brtan par bya'o //
NK030(a)002:961: de na rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma 'bul ba ni /
NK030(a)002:964: 'dod yon gyi lha mo gtor ma'i gzugs nyid du gyur te /
NK030(a)002:965: gzugs kyi lha mo me long bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:966: sgra'i lha mo dmar mo pi wam can /
NK030(a)002:967: dri'i lha mo ljang khu dri dung chos can /
NK030(a)002:968: ro'i lha mo dmar mo zhal zas bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:969: reg bya'i lha mo ljang khu na bza' rdo rje rgya gram gyis mtshan pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:970: chos kyi lha mo dkar mo d+harma chos 'byung thog pa /
NK030(a)002:971: gtor ma'i gzugs kyi rnam par gyur /
NK030(a)002:972: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi zhal nas /
NK030(a)002:973: 'od kyi sbu gu byung gtor ma la gsol bar bsam zhing /
NK030(a)002:975: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK030(a)002:976: i dam d+hu pa pus pa d+hi pa gan+he /
NK030(a)002:977: b+ha ling ta pra ti dza ho //
NK030(a)002:978: sh+ri m+aa na kha kha kha hi kha hi /
NK030(a)002:980: gsang nan gyi mchod pa ni /
NK030(a)002:981: bla med mchog gi pa dam pa sbyar ba ni //
NK030(a)002:982: ye shes lnga'i 'od zer rnam par 'phro /
NK030(a)002:983: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i rab brgyan te //
NK030(a)002:984: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK030(a)002:985: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa h+ai /
NK030(a)002:987: ri rab chen po'i gling bzhi la //
NK030(a)002:988: gnas pa'i sems can ma lus kun /
NK030(a)002:989: ye shes me chen sgom byas te //
NK030(a)002:990: thams cad ma lus bsreg par bya'o //
NK030(a)002:991: srid gsum bsreg pa'i me yin te //
NK030(a)002:992: yid kyi ye shes me ru 'bar //
NK030(a)002:993: ram sbyor ba'i mchod pa ni /
NK030(a)002:994: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK030(a)002:995: pad+ma la ni rdo rje zhugs /
NK030(a)002:997: / 'khril ba'i mchod sbyin mnyam sbyor bas //
NK030(a)002:998: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya'o //
NK030(a)002:1001: a nu ra ga ya mi /
NK030(a)002:1002: a nu ra ga ya ho /
NK030(a)002:1004: bza' dang bcas dang btung dang sgo /
NK030(a)002:1005: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni /
NK030(a)002:1007: chos nyid la ni chos nyi rol /
NK030(a)002:1009: dzahh+aum bum hohsh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK030(a)002:1014: sh+r+ai m+aa na kha ram kha hi /
NK030(a)002:1015: gnyis pa he ru yi gnas bcu dang /
NK030(a)002:1016: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas /
NK030(a)002:1017: dpal chen khrag 'thung spyan drangs te /
NK030(a)002:1018: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK030(a)002:1019: zhing chen gsar snying tsit+tara bcas //
NK030(a)002:1020: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor skyil //
NK030(a)002:1022: ma lus gshegs nas bsnams su gsol /
NK030(a)002:1024: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tana /
NK030(a)002:1025: sa ma ya r+au tra m+aa ra ya /
NK030(a)002:1026: kha kha kh+aa h+ai hri d+ha ya si pa h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:1027: nga ni za byed chen po ste /
NK030(a)002:1028: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang //
NK030(a)002:1029: gdul ka ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK030(a)002:1030: sha rus la sogs za bar bya'o //
NK030(a)002:1032: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya ma h+aa m+aam sa /
NK030(a)002:1036: ma h+aa go ro tsa na /
NK030(a)002:1037: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti /
NK030(a)002:1038: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK030(a)002:1039: ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra tits+tsha ho /
NK030(a)002:1042: h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo /
NK030(a)002:1043: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang /
NK030(a)002:1044: rgod dang gshed dang 'jigs par byed pa dang //
NK030(a)002:1045: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba la sogs pa'i /
NK030(a)002:1046: sku'i dngos po shin tu bsgyur ba yin /
NK030(a)002:1047: gar bcas bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK030(a)002:1048: gar gyi dbang phyug gtso bo che /
NK030(a)002:1049: zla ba la sogs snying po can //
NK030(a)002:1050: mam sa la sogs ro mchog stsol //
NK030(a)002:1051: me tog la sogs tsan dan dri //
NK030(a)002:1052: bzang dgur dbul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1053: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i mchog /
NK030(a)002:1054: byin gyis brlabs shig rnal 'byor pa /
NK030(a)002:1055: bsgrub pa'i rdzas 'di thams cad la //
NK030(a)002:1056: h+aum dang phata kyis ldan par mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1058: gzigs pa rnams pa sna tshogs 'gyur ba'i rgyas thob la //
NK030(a)002:1059: rnams pa sna tshogs 'o byed 'khyud pa'i rmongs mdzad de //
NK030(a)002:1060: rnam pa sna tshogs bde ba'i mchog bstan kun gsol la //
NK030(a)002:1061: rnam pa sna tshogs ngo mtshar bstan du gsol //
NK030(a)002:1062: rgyas ston rmongs byas rnams su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1063: bde mchog ngo mtshar bde la bzhugs //
NK030(a)002:1064: h+aum a la la ho snang bar mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1065: rnal 'byor bde mchog sgyu mas sprul //
NK030(a)002:1066: dam tshig bdag la bzhugs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1067: nyon mongs kun las rgyal bar mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1068: ma lus pa dag bsnams su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1069: nyon mongs thams cad gsal bar mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1070: hi dbang phyug sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs /
NK030(a)002:1071: e h+ya i hi tshur byon 'khor dang bcas /
NK030(a)002:1072: dzahh+aum bam hohspyana 'dren ma lus gshegs so gsol /
NK030(a)002:1073: ka la ki la ha ha dga' ba'i gzhad mos khengs //
NK030(a)002:1074: bde spyod bde drangs a ho su ka k+shi pa ka /
NK030(a)002:1075: ti ta shi sha slob ma bzhugs shig snang bar mdzod /
NK030(a)002:1076: rol zhig dgongs shig 'dod pa'i bdag nyid ti ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK030(a)002:1077: d+ha ra d+ha ra ha ra ha ra /
NK030(a)002:1078: zo cig ngo mtshar mchog tu stobs so //
NK030(a)002:1080: bdud rtsi dmar chen snying po lnga /
NK030(a)002:1081: mam sa la sogs tshe 'phel mchog /
NK030(a)002:1082: ma rtsa me rtsa rak+sha ta ru ti re ma ta /
NK030(a)002:1083: nye bar sgrub pa'i snying po sgrub rdzas rnams //
NK030(a)002:1084: dri med gzi ldan mchog gi mchod pa dam pa sbyar ba 'di //
NK030(a)002:1085: ye shes rgya mtsho thams cad dgyes shing rol du gsol //
NK030(a)002:1086: de rnams kyis mchod cing 'phrin las bcol ba'o //
NK030(a)002:1087: mnyes byed stongs pas lhag pa'i bde ba 'dod pa'i gzugs ston pa /
NK030(a)002:1089: / 'dul ba'i dbang gis gshin rje stong pas lhag par rab tu ston //
NK030(a)002:1090: dkyil 'khor kun gyi mchog tu de bzhin gshegs kun 'grub par mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1091: thams cad dag par mos pas ngo mthong stobs kyis non par mnon /
NK030(a)002:1093: dbang phyug thams cad shig shig rab tu shig /
NK030(a)002:1094: rab kyi rtsa la gnon pa'i stobs kyi ngo mthong dbang phyug non /
NK030(a)002:1095: sbyor chen h+au lu hu lu mi gsum pa las gsum gru drangs //
NK030(a)002:1096: rab kyi rtsal gyis non pa'i stobs kyi ngo mthong mthu chen non //
NK030(a)002:1097: mnyam sbyor ru tra ma tra snying las dpal mo drongs shig rab drongs shig /
NK030(a)002:1098: rab kyi rtsal gyis non pa'i stobs kyis ngo mthong tshangs pa non /
NK030(a)002:1099: sbyor chen tshangs pa drongs shig rab drongs shig /
NK030(a)002:1100: sma ra tha rab kyi rtsal gyis non pa'i stobs kyi ngo mthong dga' dbang non //
NK030(a)002:1101: mnyam sbyor kun gyis bdag la dga' drongs shig a la la ho /
NK030(a)002:1102: gdug cing khro rgyal rab tu gtum pas sems can bsgral ba'i phyir /
NK030(a)002:1103: bsgrub zhugs a la la ho /
NK030(a)002:1104: sum b+ha ni sum b+ha h+aum /
NK030(a)002:1105: madza'o mi la bya'am mi bya ba /
NK030(a)002:1106: yongs su rtogs pa de dag ming kyang sla //
NK030(a)002:1107: de 'dra'i 'adza'o sgyu ma yin pas med kyang sla /
NK030(a)002:1108: de 'dra'i sgrol ba sgyu ma yin pa de la dpa' zhes su zhig zer /
NK030(a)002:1115: ko la ko la ko la /
NK030(a)002:1118: zhes gnod sbyin gyi skad kyi bstod /
NK030(a)002:1119: rnam dag sgrib spangs srid gsum skyon bral zhing //
NK030(a)002:1120: ston ka zla gsal dri med zhal mnga' ba //
NK030(a)002:1121: bcom ldan bde gshegs rdo rje dkyil 'khor dbyings //
NK030(a)002:1122: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK030(a)002:1123: shes rab lha mo rigs kyi yum rnams dang /
NK030(a)002:1124: phyag brnyan gtum chen rngam pa'i tshogs la sogs /
NK030(a)002:1125: bsod nams ye shes tshogs ni zhing rab rdzogs /
NK030(a)002:1126: dgyes pa gar gyi mchod pa sbyar ba 'di bzhes shig /
NK030(a)002:1127: a la la ste dgyes par mdzod /
NK030(a)002:1128: ces par rol mo'i khyad par bcu sbyar la 'bul /
NK030(a)002:1132: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK030(a)002:1136: ho spros pa med pa'i dbyings rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag pa na /
NK030(a)002:1137: dus gsum du gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom
NK030(a)002:1138: ldan 'das rnam par thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK030(a)002:1139: kyi bye brag dang ldan pa /
NK030(a)002:1140: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs te /
NK030(a)002:1141: rigs lnga'i bde bar gshegs pa'i rigs mchog gzungs kyi
NK030(a)002:1142: yum gyi dbyings na rtag tu rnam par bzhugs pa
NK030(a)002:1143: / 'phags pa'i tshogs phun sum tshogs pa dang bcas
NK030(a)002:1144: pa thugs rje'i dbang gis shin tu khros shing ye
NK030(a)002:1145: shes chen po'i rol pa rmad du byung ba'i drag
NK030(a)002:1146: / shul / bla na med pa'i thabs rgya ma tsho dang ldan pa'i rgyal po /
NK030(a)002:1147: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK030(a)002:1149: yum kro d+hi shwa ri ma dang gnyis su med pa'i rol pa'i byin rlabs las byung ba /
NK030(a)002:1150: rigs lnga'i dpa' chen po yab yum goo ri'i tshogs /
NK030(a)002:1151: seng ha'i 'khor phyi yi grub pa mo dang /
NK030(a)002:1153: ye shes dang las las skyes pa thams cad mkhyen pa dang byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK030(a)002:1157: pho nya mo dang ci bgyis dang //
NK030(a)002:1159: phyogs bcu dus gsum rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK030(a)002:1161: dgongs pa rnal 'byor gyi don la thugs rtse gcig
NK030(a)002:1162: tu dgongs shing gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i don
NK030(a)002:1163: gzhung du mdzad pa thams cad mkhyen pa dang byin
NK030(a)002:1164: gyis brlabs pa dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK030(a)002:1165: gzhan yang rnal 'byor gyi mchod yon dam pa phud kyi khyad par gyi mchog 'di las /
NK030(a)002:1166: chos nyid las chos nyid byung ste /
NK030(a)002:1167: 'byung ba chen po kun rdzob kyi mtshan nyid rtsam las bsdus nas /
NK030(a)002:1168: deng sprul pa la sprul pa rol zhing rnal 'byor gsang ba mchog gi mchod pa dang /
NK030(a)002:1169: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i tshul du sbyar ba 'di /
NK030(a)002:1170: bdag nyid chen po 'khor dang bcas pa khyed rnams la dbang mi 'tshal ba'i slad du /
NK030(a)002:1171: phud dang gtsang mar dpags te /
NK030(a)002:1172: dga' mgu gus pa'i sems kyis mchod pa'i lha mo ltar /
NK030(a)002:1173: 'dod 'jos rtogs pa'i tshul du gar ye shes kyi spyi gtsug la blangs te /
NK030(a)002:1174: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rin po che'i gzhal yas khang
NK030(a)002:1175: chos kyi dbyings kyi mthas klas pa byur bur bkang
NK030(a)002:1177: thugs chen po'i dbang gis gnyis su med pa'i bde ba chen po dgyes pa'i lhun du dgongs te /
NK030(a)002:1178: ye shes chu zla lta bur sgyu ma la sgyu ma rol zhing dgongs /
NK030(a)002:1179: sku gsung thugs kyi longs spyod mi zad pa'i gter chen po bzhes su gsol /
NK030(a)002:1180: deng yon bdag dang bdag cag rnams kyi sa dang
NK030(a)002:1181: po gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa chen po'i sgor
NK030(a)002:1183: dam tshig gnyan po mngon par nos pa las //
NK030(a)002:1184: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig cha gsum su gyur ba /
NK030(a)002:1185: lha nye bar ma sgom sgoms pa snying po dag par ma bzlas pa /
NK030(a)002:1186: sbyor sgrol mang po'i bar skum pa //
NK030(a)002:1187: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcag pa /
NK030(a)002:1188: dge ba can gyi thugs dkrugs pa //
NK030(a)002:1189: mchod pa lo zla las 'das pa /
NK030(a)002:1190: dam rdzas dang du len pa rngo ma thogs pa //
NK030(a)002:1191: bsnyen pa la yun thung pa /
NK030(a)002:1193: ting nge 'dzin thangs lhod du gyur ba //
NK030(a)002:1194: le lo dang snyoms las gyis dbang du gyur ba /
NK030(a)002:1195: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzad spyod dam pa klong du ma gyur ba /
NK030(a)002:1196: sems can gyi rang bzhin du gyur pa /
NK030(a)002:1197: snga slad du dam tshig gi chags nyams su gyur pa ci 'chis pa thams cad /
NK030(a)002:1198: dus 'dir shin tu gnong shing 'gyod pa'i sems kyis mthol bshags shing mchis na /
NK030(a)002:1199: dbyings nyid nam mkha' dang 'dra ba'i ngang gi sku bzod pa chen po dang du bzhes te /
NK030(a)002:1200: tshangs pa mchog gi yid bzhin du thob par mdzad du gsol lo //
NK030(a)002:1201: dngos grub tu gsol ba ni thogs pa med pa'i shes rab //
NK030(a)002:1206: dpal chen po'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub kyi bla ma man chad nas //
NK030(a)002:1207: dngos grub kyi skal ba dang rgyu gang lags pa /
NK030(a)002:1208: dus phyi ma las sdad mi 'tshal bar //
NK030(a)002:1209: dus 'di nyid du thob par stsal du gsol /
NK030(a)002:1211: / 'phrin las dang snyan snyung du gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK030(a)002:1212: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa la sdang bar sems pa'i dgra /
NK030(a)002:1214: sdug pa'i dbal du gyur pa /
NK030(a)002:1218: so so'i rmi lam ngan pa /
NK030(a)002:1221: mi shis pa'i rkyen de dag thams cad bzlog cing /
NK030(a)002:1222: ming yang mi grags cing zhi ba chen por mdzad du gsol //
NK030(a)002:1223: gal te zhi bas 'dul du ma btub na /
NK030(a)002:1224: drag po'i 'phrin las kyi dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK030(a)002:1226: gzir zhing gnan pa la sogs ste /
NK030(a)002:1228: / 'phrin las drag shul rnam pa bzhis //
NK030(a)002:1229: ji ltar 'dul zhing 'tshams pa bzhin du mdzad nas /
NK030(a)002:1230: ming yang mi grags cing zhi ba chen por mdzad du gsol //
NK030(a)002:1231: bdag cag dam tshig 'di sngon du bzhugs pa rnams /
NK030(a)002:1232: gcad gtub lus la 'byung bar mi 'gyur zhing //
NK030(a)002:1233: grib mas phog pa'i sdug bsngal shin tu mi bzod pa //
NK030(a)002:1234: sku yi phyogs tsam mthong ba'i mod la 'tsho ba dang /
NK030(a)002:1235: gzi mdangs lus la phog pas nyi ma'i 'od zer stong phrag gi //
NK030(a)002:1236: 'od bzhin 'jig rten khams 'dir byung pa dang /
NK030(a)002:1237: lus ngag yid gsum tshe 'dir rdo rje rab snang zhing //
NK030(a)002:1238: re smon thams cad dus 'di nyid du thob par stsal du gsol //
NK030(a)002:1240: de ltar bskyed pa'i lha rnams snang la rang bzhin
NK030(a)002:1241: med pa dbang po'i gzhu dang 'dra ba la yid
NK030(a)002:1244: rdzogs pa'i rim pa gsum bstan pa yang skabs 'dir shes par bya'o //
NK030(a)002:1246: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shu d+d+he badz+ra dz+nya na tsakra /
NK030(a)002:1247: b+h+rum dza badz+ra sh+r+ai heru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri dza /
NK030(a)002:1248: zhes brjod pas gzhal yas khang mdun du phye la /
NK030(a)002:1249: lha thams cad kyi thugs khar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK030(a)002:1250: gyi steng du rgyu'i he ru ka lta bu'i ye
NK030(a)002:1252: de'i thugs kar zla ba la gnas pa'i rdo rje
NK030(a)002:1253: rtse lnga pa rang gi mdog dang mthun pa'i lte
NK030(a)002:1254: bar / rang gi sa bon gyis mtshan pa /
NK030(a)002:1255: de'i 'khor yug tu rang gi nye skong dang snying
NK030(a)002:1256: po rtsa sngags kyis bskor ba g.yas phyogs su 'khor
NK030(a)002:1258: rang gi zhal nas thon yum gyi zhal du zhugs thugs khar thim /
NK030(a)002:1259: bdag dang bsgrub bya'i sdig pa dang sgrib pa dang sdug bsngal thams cad zhi /
NK030(a)002:1261: 'gro ba thams cad dbang du bsdus /
NK030(a)002:1262: bgegs dang log par 'dren pa tshar bcad /
NK030(a)002:1263: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi byin brlabs 'jug par bsam la bzlas /
NK030(a)002:1264: ngag tu ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK030(a)002:1265: h+aum kun gzhi skye ba med pa'i klong gdal nas //
NK030(a)002:1266: stong gsum thams cad dur khrod gzhal yas khang //
NK030(a)002:1267: rang 'byung yid kyi rig par rang shar bas //
NK030(a)002:1268: rgyud drug thams cad khrag 'thung rol pa'i sku //
NK030(a)002:1269: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi sde gdal bas //
NK030(a)002:1270: sgra skad thams cad bzlas brjod sngags kyi tshig /
NK030(a)002:1271: dran rtogs thams cad khrag 'thung rol pa'i thugs /
NK030(a)002:1273: / 'di yang gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor dam pa ste //
NK030(a)002:1274: blo chung theg dman rnams kyi spyod yul min //
NK030(a)002:1275: rnal 'byor chen po rnams kyi nan tan bya'o //
NK030(a)002:1276: ru lu ni ye shes rnam pa lnga //
NK030(a)002:1277: ru lu gong ma ko ri khro mo brgyad //
NK030(a)002:1278: ru lu 'og ma seng ha phra men brgyad //
NK030(a)002:1279: h+aum ni dpal gyi sgo ma bzhi /
NK030(a)002:1280: b+h+yo ni dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad /
NK030(a)002:1281: h+aum khro bo chen po bcu /
NK030(a)002:1282: ru lu 'bru brgyad glu blangs pas //
NK030(a)002:1283: sngon gyi rgyal ba glu yi bsgrub //
NK030(a)002:1285: rnal 'byor dbang phyug glu yis bsgrubs //
NK030(a)002:1286: bstan pa rgya mtsho glu yis spel //
NK030(a)002:1287: srid pa'i bu mo glu yis brten //
NK030(a)002:1288: bdud dang srin po glu yis btul //
NK030(a)002:1289: dus gsum rgyal ba glu yis mnyes //
NK030(a)002:1290: dngos grub brlabs chen glu yis 'bebs //
NK030(a)002:1291: rnal 'byor chen po glu blangs ngo //
NK030(a)002:1292: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK030(a)002:1293: h+aum gtum chen dus mtha' me ltar 'bar /
NK030(a)002:1296: khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK030(a)002:1297: mche ba zangs dmag za byed che //
NK030(a)002:1299: h+aum rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug stong ldir //
NK030(a)002:1300: gtum chen ri rab 'bum bsnyil skad //
NK030(a)002:1301: a a ha la'i ga da rgyang can //
NK030(a)002:1302: spyug pa'i mthor rlung gsang ba che /
NK030(a)002:1304: h+aum khro bo shes rab 'od po che //
NK030(a)002:1305: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun du gsal /
NK030(a)002:1308: sna tshogs ye shes thig le che ho //
NK030(a)002:1309: h+aum khro bo'i rgyal po sprin chen po //
NK030(a)002:1310: khros pa'i rgyal po char ltar 'bebs //
NK030(a)002:1312: sna tshogs khros pas thig le che ho //
NK030(a)002:1313: h+aum bdud kun gyi ni bdud chen po //
NK030(a)002:1314: bdud kyi bdud de bdud rnams 'joms /
NK030(a)002:1318: / 'jigs byed chen po thig le che ho //
NK030(a)002:1319: h+aum rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK030(a)002:1320: rdo rje chu bo bdud chen po //
NK030(a)002:1321: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che //
NK030(a)002:1322: rdo rje rlung de mthor rlung che ho //
NK030(a)002:1325: tshogs kyi yo byad rnams tshang bar bsags la //
NK030(a)002:1327: gtor ma ltar 'dod yon du byin brlabs /
NK030(a)002:1328: b+ha ling ta'i sngags brjod mi dgos /
NK030(a)002:1330: dbang phyug chen po yab yum dang //
NK030(a)002:1331: byang chub rdo rje lcam dral dang //
NK030(a)002:1332: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' yas dang //
NK030(a)002:1333: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs chen dang //
NK030(a)002:1334: lha dang lha min rnal 'byor dang //
NK030(a)002:1336: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK030(a)002:1337: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1339: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK030(a)002:1348: sarba badz+ra ta ki ni nan /
NK030(a)002:1349: hri ta ya h+aum h+aum h+aum phata phata phata /
NK030(a)002:1351: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK030(a)002:1352: sarba dush+ta na sa ma ya /
NK030(a)002:1353: mu tra pra ban tsakra h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:1354: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan /
NK030(a)002:1355: dzah h+aum bam ho ru lu ru lu /
NK030(a)002:1361: sh+r+aii he ru ka e h+ye hi tri sha ho /
NK030(a)002:1363: hrim hrim h+r+aim zhes brjod pas mdun gyi nam mkha' la sprin phung bzhin byon par bsam /
NK030(a)002:1365: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa sbyar ba ni /
NK030(a)002:1366: ye shes lnga'i 'od zer rnam par 'phro /
NK030(a)002:1367: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK030(a)002:1368: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1369: +aahh+aum su ta u pa b+h+yahka ma la badz+ra amri ta ha ra na /
NK030(a)002:1371: b+ha ga w+aan dzah+aum bam ho /
NK030(a)002:1374: sarba ma h+aa su ka sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK030(a)002:1377: de nas tshogs gsum spros tee /
NK030(a)002:1379: sgeg pa dpal ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK030(a)002:1380: rgod dang gshed dang 'jigs par byed pa dang //
NK030(a)002:1381: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba la sogs pa'i //
NK030(a)002:1382: sku'i dngos po shin tu bsgyur ba yin //
NK030(a)002:1383: gar byas sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK030(a)002:1384: gar gyi dbang phyug gtso bo che //
NK030(a)002:1385: zla ba la sogs snying po che //
NK030(a)002:1386: mam sa la sogs ro mchog stsol //
NK030(a)002:1387: me tog la sogs tsan dan dri //
NK030(a)002:1388: bzang dgur 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1389: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i tshogs //
NK030(a)002:1390: byin gyis rlobs shig rnal 'byor pa //
NK030(a)002:1391: bsgrub pa'i rdzas 'di thams cad la /
NK030(a)002:1392: h+aum dang phata kyi ldan par mdzod /
NK030(a)002:1394: tshe rabs thog med tshun chad nas /
NK030(a)002:1395: da lta'i lus ni blangs pa yan chad du //
NK030(a)002:1396: lus kyi sdig byas sdig pa ngan du spyad /
NK030(a)002:1397: ngag gi tshig 'khyal smras pa ngan du brjod //
NK030(a)002:1398: sems kyi blo nor legs par bsam la sogs /
NK030(a)002:1400: / 'dod khro gti mug dbang gi nongs bgyis pa //
NK030(a)002:1401: bkram pa'i lha tshogs khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK030(a)002:1402: ye shes lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK030(a)002:1403: de'i 'khor du rtogs pa'i lha srin rnams /
NK030(a)002:1404: mi yi skyon mthong tsam la rnams par rtog /
NK030(a)002:1405: nongs gyis 'gal 'khrul mchis na mthol zhing bshags //
NK030(a)002:1406: mthol bshags bzhes la tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK030(a)002:1408: b+y+aa ri ku lam sha ba ro d+ha ro /
NK030(a)002:1410: ba no gad na kha trong ka ga rbo /
NK030(a)002:1411: dza la da n+aa la ba sur ti ba ta ka sho bo sha la /
NK030(a)002:1412: a sam na pad+ma rtsan dre ni /
NK030(a)002:1413: ka ma h+aum ta ta ri /
NK030(a)002:1414: rak+ta tsit+ta krmo dza la pa tam ban d+he he ru badz+ra ma sa ran nan /
NK030(a)002:1415: ba mu kha tig na dash+taka ri lam lta ba 'khrul dang dam nyams pa thams cad bskang ngo //
NK030(a)002:1417: tha ma la ka p+aa la mtshan ldan gyi nang du zhal zas bsdus te /
NK030(a)002:1418: e ram em ram zhes brjod pas snod la dal gru gsum mthing nag me dpung 'bar bar gyur /
NK030(a)002:1419: dz+wa la ram dz+wa la ram /
NK030(a)002:1420: zhes bcu khro bo mthing nag mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs par bsam /
NK030(a)002:1421: ba h+aum be ta zhes brjod pas khro bo rnams
NK030(a)002:1422: rab tu khros thabs su las la chas par gyur
NK030(a)002:1424: sde brgyad kyis dgra bgegs gyi rgyab brten mi byed bar dgongs /
NK030(a)002:1425: pho nya btang la ngag du /
NK030(a)002:1427: zhes sgo ba'i sngags dang phyag rgyas tri yam dzah n+ri yam dza /
NK030(a)002:1429: lcags kyi sdig pa mgo dgu pa kha brgyad pas snying dkar nag mtshams nas bzung /
NK030(a)002:1430: ngag tu badz+ra ki li ki li ya h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:1432: rang gi thugs kha nas khro bo spros nas /
NK030(a)002:1434: phur pa ki la ya zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas dgra sta ltag par 'phyar ba /
NK030(a)002:1435: g.yon phur pa snying khar gzir ba /
NK030(a)002:1436: lte ba man chad lcags kyi phur pa zur gsum pa /
NK030(a)002:1437: dur khrod kyi chas brgyad dang ldan pa /
NK030(a)002:1438: me 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis brlabs cing //
NK030(a)002:1439: bdag he ru kar nga rgyal ba dang /
NK030(a)002:1440: phur pa ki la yar gsal ba dang //
NK030(a)002:1441: ling dgra bgegs su gsal ba dang /
NK030(a)002:1442: gsum pa de dang ldan pas gdab ste /
NK030(a)002:1443: ngag tu g+ha ta ya brjod cing phur bskor byas la snying dkar gdab la /
NK030(a)002:1444: rnam par shes pa 'og min du spar la //
NK030(a)002:1445: bo d+hi tsit+ta dz+nya na sid+d+hi ku tu h+aum /
NK030(a)002:1446: zhes brjod pas phur pa snying khar bsdus la /
NK030(a)002:1448: bee d+aur sngon po rin chen ri rab la //
NK030(a)002:1449: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer gdal ba ltar /
NK030(a)002:1450: sems dpa' sngon po 'od kyi dkyil 'khor can //
NK030(a)002:1451: dpal ldan gzi brjid 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK030(a)002:1453: / 'od dpung stug po sprin ltar 'khrigs pa yi /
NK030(a)002:1455: / 'jigs byed rngam stabs rkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NK030(a)002:1456: za byed bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar 'dra te //
NK030(a)002:1457: gdug pa thams cad rdo rje'i zhal du 'dren //
NK030(a)002:1458: mi zad mche bas brgyan pa'i zhal gdangs shing //
NK030(a)002:1459: khams gsum za bar byed pa'i skan sgra can //
NK030(a)002:1460: nyi zla 'bar ba'i spyan gyi gdang mig gis /
NK030(a)002:1461: bgegs dpung sreg par mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:1462: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK030(a)002:1463: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri kha hi /
NK030(a)002:1464: zhes lha tshangs pa'i sngags kyis btab la /
NK030(a)002:1465: de'i lhag ma longs spyad par bya'o //
NK030(a)002:1466: de nas lhag ma bya ste gtor ma shod du phab /
NK030(a)002:1468: gtor mar me dmar skya gcig btang /
NK030(a)002:1469: de nas gtor gzhong e b+h+rum zhes pas /
NK030(a)002:1470: phyi khyams gru gsum pa'i nang gzhal yas khang du bsam /
NK030(a)002:1471: der rtsa ba'i lha bskyed la /
NK030(a)002:1473: gtor ma bdud rtsir gyur par bsam //
NK030(a)002:1474: de nas lhag ma'i lha snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK030(a)002:1475: h+aum las kyi rdo rje byed par dbang bskur ba'i //
NK030(a)002:1476: mkha' 'gro ging dang dbang phyug ma mo'i tshogs //
NK030(a)002:1477: lhag ma'i kha chu dam las gtogs pa rnams //
NK030(a)002:1478: dam tshig tshul bzhin mchod kyi da tshur byon //
NK030(a)002:1480: lhag ma dang kha chu'i dam tshig la rtog pa'i mkha' 'gro ma sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK030(a)002:1482: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK030(a)002:1484: 'khor dang bcas pa rnams sngon gyi thugs dam las ma 'da' bar gshegs shig /
NK030(a)002:1487: e a ra la hrim hrim /
NK030(a)002:1488: spyan drangs pa ni lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK030(a)002:1489: d+aa ki ni d+aa ki ni /
NK030(a)002:1496: to sha ya to sha ya /
NK030(a)002:1499: sarba badz+ra d+aa ki n+ai n+aam /
NK030(a)002:1500: hri ta yam h+aum dzah dzahh+aum bam ho /
NK030(a)002:1503: bdag dang rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK030(a)002:1504: chos skyong ba'i rgyal po dang /
NK030(a)002:1505: dkon mchog gsum gyi sku dgra la sogs pa thams cad sgrol zhig bzhes shig /
NK030(a)002:1506: sangs rgyas kyi zhing bde ba can du gnas spor gcig gdan 'bul zhing dbang bsdu ba ni /
NK030(a)002:1507: rta gdong gi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK030(a)002:1508: pad+ma ba da b+ha mu ka /
NK030(a)002:1517: sarba badz+ra d+aa ki n+ai n+aam hri ta yan /
NK030(a)002:1520: zhes dbang du bsdus zil gyis mnan du'ang rung ngo //
NK030(a)002:1521: de nas rigs lngar phye la mchod de /
NK030(a)002:1522: badz+ra d+aa ki ni pra tits+tsha mam ba ling ta h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:1523: bud+ha d+h+aa ki ni pra tits+tsha mam b+ha ling+ta phata /
NK030(a)002:1524: rat+na t+aa ki ni pra tits+tsha mam b+ha ling+ta tram phata /
NK030(a)002:1525: pad+ma da ki ni pra tits+tsha mam b+ha ling+ta h+r+aihphata /
NK030(a)002:1526: karma ta ki ni pra tits+tsha mam b+ha ling+ta a phata /
NK030(a)002:1528: de nas kha chus gdab pa ni //
NK030(a)002:1529: thod phreng gi phyag rgyas bcings la //
NK030(a)002:1530: gu ru kro d+ha rat+na sa ma ya p+r+ai sha
NK030(a)002:1531: su rba bud+d+ha k+she tra p+aa la k+sho b+ha ka
NK030(a)002:1532: ra h'u phata / zhes brjod la kha chus gdab bo //
NK030(a)002:1533: de nas mkha' 'gro ma mchod de //
NK030(a)002:1534: h+aum rnam dag chos nyid zhi ba las //
NK030(a)002:1535: thugs rje chen po'i sprul pa byung //
NK030(a)002:1536: thabs chen zla gsang thig le las //
NK030(a)002:1537: yal gam can rnams 'du bar mdzod /
NK030(a)002:1540: grub pa tshogs kyi bdag mo rnams //
NK030(a)002:1541: re ba bskang phyir gnas pa rnams //
NK030(a)002:1542: mngon sum snang ba shar bar mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1543: h+aum rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK030(a)002:1544: yi dwags stan la yang dag zhon //
NK030(a)002:1545: gdug pa'i sems kyis sdigs byed cing //
NK030(a)002:1546: dpa' bo brjid pa'i gzugs 'dzin ma //
NK030(a)002:1547: skal ldan rang gi lag char ldan //
NK030(a)002:1548: sha khrag dang ni sgyu ma dang //
NK030(a)002:1549: rkang dang tshil bu za zhing byon //
NK030(a)002:1550: dga' bar byed dang gsod par byed /
NK030(a)002:1552: / 'bar byed ma dang gzir byed ma /
NK030(a)002:1554: / 'joms byed ma dang bung bu'i mgo /
NK030(a)002:1555: chags byed ma dang chags bral ma /
NK030(a)002:1558: sna tshogs lus dang bsrung ba ma //
NK030(a)002:1559: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bsrungs bar byed //
NK030(a)002:1560: gnod sbyin mo dang yang dag 'phrog /
NK030(a)002:1561: bya rog gdong de mi dug zhing /
NK030(a)002:1564: lag na gri dang mkhar gzhong thogs //
NK030(a)002:1565: gzhad dang 'ug pa'i gdong rings ma //
NK030(a)002:1566: khros pas khyi dang phag gi gdong //
NK030(a)002:1567: gsus po che dang lto 'chang po //
NK030(a)002:1568: rnga mong bung bu'i gdong 'dzin ma //
NK030(a)002:1569: khros pas ra dang byi la'i gdong //
NK030(a)002:1570: sgyu ma'i mgo nas za byed cing //
NK030(a)002:1571: keng rus dkar po 'dzin pa ste //
NK030(a)002:1572: khros pas rus pa'i 'phreng bas klubs //
NK030(a)002:1573: gsus po che la bum pa 'dzin //
NK030(a)002:1574: phan tshun 'thab par brtson par byed //
NK030(a)002:1575: lce spyang gis ni 'khor gyis bsnams /
NK030(a)002:1580: / 'khor bcas ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1581: shar nyid nas ni bum sna ste //
NK030(a)002:1582: lho ru rnam par 'joms par mo //
NK030(a)002:1583: nub nas mda' shar 'gri ba ste //
NK030(a)002:1585: mdor na ye shes las grub pa'i //
NK030(a)002:1586: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK030(a)002:1587: don gyis sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK030(a)002:1588: bsgrub pa po la phan gdags phyir //
NK030(a)002:1589: bran gyi tshul du khas blangs te //
NK030(a)002:1590: gnas 'dir rtse gcig gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1591: gnas 'dir rtse gcig gshegs nas kyang //
NK030(a)002:1592: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK030(a)002:1593: bcol ba'i 'phrin las grub par mdzod /
NK030(a)002:1594: mkha' 'gro sum bcu rtsa gnyis ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta la kha hi /
NK030(a)002:1595: ma h+aa rak+ta la kh+aa hi //
NK030(a)002:1596: ma h+aa b+ha li ta la kha hi //
NK030(a)002:1597: bcom ldan dpal chen he ru la //
NK030(a)002:1598: ging chen ka ra'i tshogs kyi bskor ba ni /
NK030(a)002:1599: dpa' bo tshogs kyi lam rnams kun gyi lam rnams kun 'byed pa /
NK030(a)002:1600: khro bo chen po badz+ra ging ka ra //
NK030(a)002:1601: khro mo chen mo khams gsum dbugs bsdud ma //
NK030(a)002:1602: ta na g+ha na'i 'phrin las dus la babs //
NK030(a)002:1603: rdo rje gnod sbyin rdo rje srin po dang //
NK030(a)002:1604: rdo rje 'byung po rdo rje shwa na dang //
NK030(a)002:1605: rdo rje gshin rje rdo rje ro langs dang //
NK030(a)002:1606: rdo rje 'chi bdag rdo rje dus mtshams dang //
NK030(a)002:1607: dbang bsdu lcags kyu 'dren par chen mo dang /
NK030(a)002:1608: khams gsum g.yab mos 'dud pa chen mo dang //
NK030(a)002:1609: gar gyi glog ltar chen mo dang //
NK030(a)002:1610: snod stong len par byed pa chen mo dang //
NK030(a)002:1611: rna brnyan phra med zer ba chen mo dang //
NK030(a)002:1612: khams gsum snying rjes gsod pa chen mo dang //
NK030(a)002:1613: tshogs kyi phyag tshang byed pa chen mo ste la sogs ste //
NK030(a)002:1614: rdo rje byi sku pho mo 'khor bcas la //
NK030(a)002:1615: khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging chen bco brgyad rnams //
NK030(a)002:1616: ta na ga na'i tshogs gyi gnas chen 'dir //
NK030(a)002:1617: sngon gyi tha tshig bzhin du 'dir gshegs shig /
NK030(a)002:1618: bdud rtsi dmar chen longs spyod 'di bzhes la //
NK030(a)002:1619: dgyes pa gar gyi rol zhing 'phrin las mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1620: ging ka ra ha ha ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK030(a)002:1621: ging chen bco brgyad ma h+aa pa na tsa a mri ta la kha hi /
NK030(a)002:1622: ma h+aa rak+ta ma h+aa b+ha ling ta bcom ldan dpal chen he ru la //
NK030(a)002:1623: dbang phyug tshogs kyi bskor ba ni //
NK030(a)002:1624: grub pa'i ma tshogs rnal 'byor ma //
NK030(a)002:1625: snying rje byams pa'i spyod yul can //
NK030(a)002:1626: tshangs pa la sogs nyi shu brgyad /
NK030(a)002:1628: / 'jig rten rnams kyi sring mo ni //
NK030(a)002:1629: lag par blo snying nang khrol thogs //
NK030(a)002:1630: mkha' la khrag ba rlangs snyim par 'dzin //
NK030(a)002:1631: spu gri so la skra yangs ma //
NK030(a)002:1632: mche ba gtsigs shing 'bri tshug lta //
NK030(a)002:1634: bsod pa'i las rnams kun la brtson //
NK030(a)002:1635: rgyal mo dang ni blon mo dang //
NK030(a)002:1636: bran mo dang ni yang bran mo //
NK030(a)002:1637: g.yog dang yang g.yog 'khor dang bcas //
NK030(a)002:1638: ma mo chen mo khyed rnams kyang /
NK030(a)002:1641: ye shes thob par bya ba'i phyir //
NK030(a)002:1642: lhag ma za bar dam bcas shing /
NK030(a)002:1644: / 'grub pa rnams kyis grogs bya zhes //
NK030(a)002:1645: ji ltar khas blangs dam re bcas //
NK030(a)002:1646: dam bcas bzhin du he ru ka'i //
NK030(a)002:1648: de sngar khyed kyi gzugs mchog rnams //
NK030(a)002:1649: mngon par ston la grub mchog 'bul //
NK030(a)002:1650: ji srid grub mchog ma lus shing //
NK030(a)002:1651: khyed rnams mngon du ma gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:1652: bar du ta na'i gnas chen 'dir /
NK030(a)002:1654: / 'dug la las rnams grub mdzod cig /
NK030(a)002:1655: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad ma h+aa pa na tsa a mri ta la kha hi /
NK030(a)002:1656: ma h+aa rak+ta ma h+aa ba ling ta bcom ldan dpal chen he ru la /
NK030(a)002:1657: ma bdun tshogs kyi bskor ba ni //
NK030(a)002:1658: rgya mtsho chen mo'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)002:1659: dpal ldan shugs sgrol gtso mo ste //
