NK030(a)002:1660: ri rab brnyil ba'i rngam stobs can //
NK030(a)002:1661: kha nas me 'bar rgya mtsho skems //
NK030(a)002:1662: rdo rje kun grags gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1667: kun tu bzang mo gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1669: nam mkha' stong la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK030(a)002:1670: bdud dpung dgra rnams kun 'dul ma //
NK030(a)002:1671: rdo rje grags snyems gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1672: dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas /
NK030(a)002:1673: khro mo gtum chen za byed ma //
NK030(a)002:1674: pho nya mo ste drug bcu'i tshogs //
NK030(a)002:1675: sha chen khrag la longs spyod cing //
NK030(a)002:1676: gdug pa ma lus kun 'dul ma //
NK030(a)002:1677: rdo rje chen mo ye shes mchog  /
NK030(a)002:1678: 'khor bcas ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1679: khrag gi rgya mtsho dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)002:1682: rdo rje 'dod chags gshegs su gsol /
NK030(a)002:1685: zhag pa stong gi gdengs ldan ma /
NK030(a)002:1688: rdo rje gsal 'phro gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1689: dbang phyug chen mo'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK030(a)002:1692: dam tshig nyams rnams sgrol bar byed //
NK030(a)002:1693: rdo rje g.yu sgron gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1694: ma mo chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK030(a)002:1695: kun kyang nag mo ral pa can //
NK030(a)002:1696: kun kyang kha nas khrag 'dzag ma /
NK030(a)002:1697: kun kyang mig nas me 'bar ma /
NK030(a)002:1698: ri rab brnyil ba'i rngam stobs can /
NK030(a)002:1699: 'khor bcas ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1700: rnams lnga dmar gyis mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK030(a)002:1701: bdag gi bcol ba'i las rnams 'grub par mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1702: ma mo chen mo bdun la ma h+aa pany+tsa amri
NK030(a)002:1703: ta la ma h+aa rak+ta ma h+aa b+ha ling ta
NK030(a)002:1704: 'phrin las bcol / bcom ldan dpal chen he ru ka /
NK030(a)002:1705: sring mo bzhi yis bskor ba ni /
NK030(a)002:1707: shar gyi 'gyogs ma gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1708: mkha' la khyung lding gshin rje'i sring //
NK030(a)002:1710: dmar mo g.yag thod klu'i sring //
NK030(a)002:1711: nub kyi 'gyogs ma gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1712: nag mo ser chen gnod sbyin sring //
NK030(a)002:1713: byang gi mgyogs ma gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1714: sring mo chen mo khyed rnams kyang /
NK030(a)002:1715: shin tu gdungs pa'i dam tshig can //
NK030(a)002:1716: zhi dang khro bo'i las mdzad ma //
NK030(a)002:1717: gser gyi sprul pa mang po'i khri steng nas //
NK030(a)002:1718: dam tshig yal gam can la ba rtse dgongs ma /
NK030(a)002:1720: / 'khor bcas ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1721: rnam lnga dmar gyis mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK030(a)002:1722: bdag gi bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1723: sring mo bzhi la ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta la ma h+aa rak+ta ma ha b+ha ling ta  /
NK030(a)002:1727: ho bcom ldan 'das dpal chen sh+r+ai he ru ka'i 'khor phyi yi grub pa mo dang /
NK030(a)002:1728: nang rnal 'byor ma ye shes dang las la skyes pa thams cad mkhyen pa dang /
NK030(a)002:1729: byin gyis brlabs pa dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK030(a)002:1730: rnal 'byor gyi mchod yon dam pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i tshul du sbyar ba 'di /
NK030(a)002:1731: brdul dang phyag dar dang dri ma kha chu la
NK030(a)002:1732: sogs te so so'i dam tshig brtul zhugs kyis so
NK030(a)002:1733: so nas ji ltar dgyes pa bzhin phul /
NK030(a)002:1734: dgyes pa rnams ni phul la bsnams su gsol //
NK030(a)002:1735: lhag ma kha chu la dgyes pa rnams ni so
NK030(a)002:1736: so'i dam tshig bzhin du gsol nas mnyes zhing tshim
NK030(a)002:1737: par gyur cig / bdag cag gi gsang ba'i slad du gsang ba mchog gi bka' nos pa las //
NK030(a)002:1738: dam tshig rtsa ba dang yan lag dag las tshor
NK030(a)002:1739: ba dang ma tshor bar nyams pa ci mchis rnams
NK030(a)002:1740: / shin tu gnong zhing 'gyod pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags shing mchis na /
NK030(a)002:1741: bzod pa bzhes ste tshangs pa dam pa yid bzhin thob par mdzad du gsol /
NK030(a)002:1743: ya hi gats+tsha zhes lhag ma'i lha slar rang gnas su gshegs /
NK030(a)002:1744: h+aum zhes brjod pas gtor gzhong gi lha rnams rang gi thugs khar bsdu /
NK030(a)002:1745: b+h+yo sngon gyis bskal pa dang po la /
NK030(a)002:1746: 'og min chos gyi pho brang du //
NK030(a)002:1747: bcom ldan dpal chen gar gyis dbang phyug des //
NK030(a)002:1748: srid pa'i ma mo dam la btag pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)002:1749: ko ri la sogs gnas kyi ma mo brgyad //
NK030(a)002:1750: sing ha la sogs yul gyi phra men brgyad //
NK030(a)002:1751: rta gdong la sogs sgo ma bzhi rnams kyi //
NK030(a)002:1752: so so'i gzugs mchog dam pa bstan nas kyang //
NK030(a)002:1753: bka'i gtor ma blangs bar ma chad dam //
NK030(a)002:1754: bcol ba'i las rnams bya bar ma chad dam //
NK030(a)002:1755: sngon tshe zhal bzhes dam las ma mda' bar //
NK030(a)002:1756: rnam lnga dmar gyi mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK030(a)002:1757: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i 'phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1758: b+h+yo dus skabs de'i 'og rol du /
NK030(a)002:1759: rgya gar rdo rje gdan gyi gtsug lag tu //
NK030(a)002:1760: slob dpon chen po dga' rab rdo rje yi //
NK030(a)002:1761: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK030(a)002:1762: mkha' 'gro chen mo sum bcu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK030(a)002:1763: mgon po chen po bdud bcu rtsa gnyis kyi //
NK030(a)002:1764: so so'i gzugs mchog dam bka'i gtor ma bcol ba'i
NK030(a)002:1765: 'phrin las sngon tshe zhal bzhes rnam lnga dmar gyi
NK030(a)002:1766: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i b+h+yo dus skabs de'i 'og rol
NK030(a)002:1767: du / lho brag mkhar chu dpal gyi dben gnas su //
NK030(a)002:1768: slob dpon chen po nam mkha'i snying po yis //
NK030(a)002:1769: rdo rje phur pa'i dkyil 'khor zhal phye nas //
NK030(a)002:1770: gnam lcags phur pa brag la btab pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)002:1771: ma bdun sring bzhi 'khor dang bcas rnams kyis //
NK030(a)002:1772: so so'i gzugs bka'i gtor ma bcol ba'i sngon tshe
NK030(a)002:1773: rnam lnga dmar b+h+yo dus skabs de'i 'og rol du
NK030(a)002:1774: / spa gro stag tshang seng ge'i dben gnas su //
NK030(a)002:1775: slob dpon chen po dpal gyi seng ge yis //
NK030(a)002:1776: yang dag lha dgu'i dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK030(a)002:1777: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad 'khor bcas kyis //
NK030(a)002:1778: so so'i gzugs bka' yi bcol pa'i sngon tshe rnam
NK030(a)002:1779: lnga rnal 'byor b+h+yo dus skabs de'i 'og rol du
NK030(a)002:1780: / yar lung gangs kyi phug ring chen mo ru //
NK030(a)002:1781: slob dpon chen po dz+nya na ku m+aa ras //
NK030(a)002:1782: phun sum tshogs pa'i dkyil 'khor zhal phye nas //
NK030(a)002:1783: lce spyangs la sogs 'khor dang bcas rnams gyis //
NK030(a)002:1784: so so'i gzugs bka' yi bcol pa'i sngon tshe rnam
NK030(a)002:1785: lnga rnal 'byor b+h+yo dus skabs de'i 'og rol tu
NK030(a)002:1786: / brag dmar bsam yas chu rgyun ni seng du /
NK030(a)002:1787: slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis /
NK030(a)002:1788: man ngag lta ba'i rdzong 'phrang bshad pa'i tshe //
NK030(a)002:1789: bod khams skyong pa'i brtan ma bcu gnyis kyis //
NK030(a)002:1790: rang rang srog gi snying po phul nas kyang /
NK030(a)002:1791: so so'i gzugs mchog dam bstan nas kyang //
NK030(a)002:1792: bka' yi bcol pa'i sngon tshe rnam lnga rnal 'byor b+h+yo shar phyogs ma bdun bka'i gtor ma longs //
NK030(a)002:1793: khyod kyis zhi ba'i 'phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1794: lho'i ma bdun bka'i gtor ma longs /
NK030(a)002:1795: khyed kyis rgyas pa'i 'phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1796: nub kyi ma bdun bka'i gtor ma longs /
NK030(a)002:1797: khyod kyis dbang gi 'phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1798: byang gi ma bdun bka'i khyed kyis drag po'i 'phrin sngon tshe zhal bzhes dam las ma 'da' bar //
NK030(a)002:1799: rnam lnga dmar gyis mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK030(a)002:1800: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i 'phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1801: badz+ra kro d+ha mah+aa sh+ri he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:1802: ho nag mo bzhin mi sdug gi bu mo chen mo bzhi dang //
NK030(a)002:1803: dmar mo khro gnyer can gyi bu mo gnod sbyin ma chen mo bzhi dang //
NK030(a)002:1804: dkar mo mdangs can gyi bu mo sman btsun ma chen mo bzhi dang /
NK030(a)002:1805: bod khams skyong ba'i brtan ma bcu gnyis 'khor dang bcas pa /
NK030(a)002:1806: dpal chen po'i bka' pha babs blangs pa dang /
NK030(a)002:1807: sgrub pa po'i stong grogs la deng mchod pa'i gnas 'dir gshegs shig /
NK030(a)002:1809: hring hring ta ki ni h+aum dza zhes spyan drangs /
NK030(a)002:1811: h+aum bka'i tshogs dang bcas nyid du //
NK030(a)002:1812: khrag 'thung de bzhin nam mkha'i sku //
NK030(a)002:1814: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs skyong ma rnams //
NK030(a)002:1815: bdag nyid chen mo rdo rje kun grags ma //
NK030(a)002:1816: dpal ldan ha ri rdo rje ya ma skyong //
NK030(a)002:1817: gangs dkar sha med rdo rje kun tu bzang /
NK030(a)002:1819: / 'brog chen 'khor 'dul rdo rje bgegs kyi gtso //
NK030(a)002:1820: bdud mo chen mo mched bzhi yang //
NK030(a)002:1821: lhab lhub mang po rgyan dang bcas //
NK030(a)002:1822: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas /
NK030(a)002:1825: gangs kyi yum chen rdo rje g.yu bun ma //
NK030(a)002:1826: kha rag khyung btsun rdo rje dpal gyi yum //
NK030(a)002:1827: gter chen mkha' lding rdo rje klu mo skyong //
NK030(a)002:1828: sma ri rab 'byam rdo rje bgegs kyi gtso //
NK030(a)002:1829: gnod sbyin chen mo mched bzhi yang //
NK030(a)002:1830: lhab lhub bran 'dir gshegs bskong btsun de mo rdo rje bod khams skyong //
NK030(a)002:1831: btsan la la rol rdo rje sman btsun ma //
NK030(a)002:1832: u chos rdo rje dbyar mo sil //
NK030(a)002:1833: g.yu yi dril bu rdo rje gzugs legs ma //
NK030(a)002:1834: sman btsun chen mo khyed bzhi yang /
NK030(a)002:1835: lhab lhub mang po'i bran 'dir gsheg bstan skyong chen mo khyed rnams kyang /
NK030(a)002:1836: a su ra ba'i brag phug tu /
NK030(a)002:1838: rigs lnga dpal chen spyan snga ru //
NK030(a)002:1839: zhing chen mchog gi rdzas bkram nas /
NK030(a)002:1840: rnams lnga dmar gyi mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK030(a)002:1841: lag tu rdo rje byin na sa ni //
NK030(a)002:1842: thar pa thob pa'i ming yang rtags //
NK030(a)002:1843: rdo rje 'chang gi gral du bzhag //
NK030(a)002:1844: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK030(a)002:1849: snying gi dkyil nas khrag phyung ste /
NK030(a)002:1850: sgrol ging mang pos las byas nas /
NK030(a)002:1853: de bas ngos kyi bka' nyon la //
NK030(a)002:1854: rnam lnga dmar gyi mchod pa 'di bzhes la /
NK030(a)002:1855: bod khams rtag tu bde ba dang /
NK030(a)002:1856: nad dang rims nad med par mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1857: sngon gyi thugs dam brtser dgongs la //
NK030(a)002:1858: bdag gi bcol ba'i 'phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK030(a)002:1863: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK030(a)002:1864: brtan ma bcu gnyis zhal du ma h+aa pany+tsa kha h+ai /
NK030(a)002:1866: ma h+aa b+ha ling ta kha hi /
NK030(a)002:1871: tre rat+na tre lo kya sam ha ra na h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:1872: rgyal ba mchod pas mnyes gyur gcig /
NK030(a)002:1873: dam can thugs dam bskong gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:1874: pha ma la sogs 'gro drug la //
NK030(a)002:1875: tshad med gtor ma 'di bsngosa pas //
NK030(a)002:1876: longs spyod ldan zhing tshogs rdzogs nas //
NK030(a)002:1877: thams cad myur du sangs rgyas shog /
NK030(a)002:1878: sarba pre ta ni a mri ta h+aum /
NK030(a)002:1879: zhes gtor ma byin par bsngo /
NK030(a)002:1880: de nas gtor gzhong rnams bshal /
NK030(a)002:1881: 'phrin las rnam bzhi'ii bro bya ba ni /
NK030(a)002:1882: sor mo rnams lu gu rgyud du byas la 'di skad do //
NK030(a)002:1883: h+aum sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs /
NK030(a)002:1884: gti mug bde gshegs 'khor bcas rnams /
NK030(a)002:1887: shin tu rmongs pa'i sems can rnams //
NK030(a)002:1888: zhi ba chen po thugs rje yis //
NK030(a)002:1889: zhi bar ma gyur gang yang med //
NK030(a)002:1890: zhi mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:1891: zhi bar gyur cig shan ting ku ru ye swa h+aa /
NK030(a)002:1893: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku nga rgyal rat+na 'khor bcas rnams /
NK030(a)002:1895: / 'jig rten khams ni shin tu drag po'i tshe dang dngos grub rgyas mdzad ma //
NK030(a)002:1896: rgyas par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK030(a)002:1897: rgyas mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:1898: rgyas par gyur cig push+tinga ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK030(a)002:1899: h+aum sangs rgyas kun gyi sku 'dod chags pad+ma 'khor
NK030(a)002:1900: 'jig rten khams ni shin tu chags pa'i sems can
NK030(a)002:1901: rnams // yid tsam gyis ni dbang du bsdus //
NK030(a)002:1902: dbang du ma gyur gcig kyang med //
NK030(a)002:1903: dbang mdzad lha la dbang du bsdus shig pa shang
NK030(a)002:1904: h+aum sangs rgyas kun gyi sku zhe sdang rdo rje
NK030(a)002:1905: 'khor bcas rnams / 'jig rten khams ni shin tu gdug pa'i sems can rnams /
NK030(a)002:1906: yud tsam gyis ni bsdus bsdus nas /
NK030(a)002:1907: bsdus su ma gyur brlag mdzad lha la dbang du
NK030(a)002:1908: bsdus cig ma ra ya ma ra ya swa h+aa
NK030(a)002:1911: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK030(a)002:1913: dkyil 'khor gsal gdab mchod pa rnams kyis mchod cing bstod pa ci shes pas bstod /
NK030(a)002:1914: badz+ra t+aa ki ni'i sngags brjod /
NK030(a)002:1916: mtshams kyi khro bo rnams gtso bo la bsdu /
NK030(a)002:1917: dbang po rnams rigs lngar bsdus te /
NK030(a)002:1918: phyogs bzhi'i gtso bo bzhi dang dbus su brgyad 'khril /
NK030(a)002:1919: tha mar lnga lnga 'khril sgo ma rigs bzhi la bsdus so //
NK030(a)002:1920: sing ha ma brgyad yum bzhi la bsdus so //
NK030(a)002:1921: khro mo brgyad yab la bsdus so //
NK030(a)002:1922: rigs lnga khrag 'thung gi yab gtso bo la bsdus /
NK030(a)002:1923: yum kun kro ti la bsdus /
NK030(a)002:1925: yab ye shes sems dpa' la bsdus /
NK030(a)002:1926: rdo rje bum pa'i h+aum la bsdus so /
NK030(a)002:1931: zla tshes thig le la bsdus /
NK030(a)002:1932: thig le mi dmigs par gyur /
NK030(a)002:1933: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK030(a)002:1935: slar dpal chen por bskyed la /
NK030(a)002:1936: go bgo ba ni sbyi bor ham bsam /
NK030(a)002:1938: rgya gram gyi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK030(a)002:1939: badz+ra k+aa ba tsi rak+sha rak+sha ham zhes go bgo /
NK030(a)002:1940: rdo rje rgya gram gyis go chas lus kheb par dmigs la /
NK030(a)002:1941: khro bo shin tu mi zad pas bsrung bar bsam /
NK030(a)002:1943: t+yam zhes brjod cing 'dzub mo gnyis la h+aum bsam ste lte bar snol bas /
NK030(a)002:1944: khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin dang /
NK030(a)002:1945: khro bo mi 'chi thabs sbyor gnyis kyis /
NK030(a)002:1946: lte bar zhabs bsnol nas lus bsrungs bar bsam /
NK030(a)002:1952: khro bo gnyis kyi sngar bzhin bsrung /
NK030(a)002:1953: thod skam phyag rgya byas la /
NK030(a)002:1955: badz+ra ka p+aa la ma le a b+hi shiny+tsa tram tram tram /
NK030(a)002:1956: zhes mgo'i gnas lngar gtum go /
NK030(a)002:1957: dar dpyangs kyi phyag rgya bcings la /
NK030(a)002:1958: badz+ra ar+ya lam b+ho d+ha ra ma le a b+hi
NK030(a)002:1959: shiny+tsa h+r+aih h+r+aih h+r+aih zhes brjod pas dar mthing ka
NK030(a)002:1960: g.yas dang / dmar po g.yon 'chang bar bsam la /
NK030(a)002:1962: zhes lan gsum thal mo btab la dbang thob pa'i nga rgyal gzung pa'o //
NK030(a)002:1963: he ru ka'i yi ge brgya pas lhag chad bskang /
NK030(a)002:1964: de nas so so'i lag tu me tog thogs rol mo bzung nas /
NK030(a)002:1965: che ba'i che mchog ston mchog bla na med //
NK030(a)002:1966: chos rje nyi ma rgyal ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)002:1967: bdud dang bgegs tshogs gnod pa'i dgra zhi nas //
NK030(a)002:1968: rtag tu dpal gnas nyin mtshan bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)002:1969: chos nyid bden pa'i chos mchog bla na med //
NK030(a)002:1970: dam chos bdud rtsi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)002:1971: nyes pa'i skyon bral dge tshogs rnam par 'phel //
NK030(a)002:1972: rtag tu dpal gnas dge 'dun yon tan rin chen dpal 'bar ba //
NK030(a)002:1973: rgyal sras phan mdzad bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)002:1974: nyon mongs dug lnga gdung pa'i dgra zhi nas //
NK030(a)002:1975: rtag tu dpal gnas nyin mtshan bkra shis shog /
NK030(a)002:1976: tshangs dang lha dbang srung ma'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)002:1977: phan mdzad lha yi bkra shis gnas gyur te //
NK030(a)002:1978: bde legs bsam pa yid bzhin 'grub pa dang //
NK030(a)002:1979: tshe ring nad med bde skyid ldan par shog  /
NK030(a)002:1980: 'jug spyod lam gyii rnal 'byor ni gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK030(a)002:1981: de nas sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa'i mngon rtogs dang las byang ngo //
NK030(a)002:1982: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor 'bring bo'i mngon rtogs la /
NK030(a)002:1983: ting nge 'dzin rnams gsum nas rten gzhal yas khang /
NK030(a)002:1984: brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor la lnga bcu rtsa brgyad
NK030(a)002:1985: sgom pa yan chad dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang mthun
NK030(a)002:1988: lha rnams phyi ma'i zur bzhi dang /
NK030(a)002:1989: dbang mo nyer brgyad kyi sgo ma bzhi'i bzhugs gnas kyi rgyab bzhi dang /
NK030(a)002:1990: steng 'og gnyis ste bcur bskyed pa'o /
NK030(a)002:1991: yang gzhal yas khang gi phyi rol /
NK030(a)002:1992: dur khrod kyi phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og gnyis dang bcur bskyed pa ste /
NK030(a)002:1993: badz+ra kro ta h+aum ka ra h+aum las /
NK030(a)002:1994: h+aum ka ra sngo skya mda' gzhu bsnams pa steng du bskyed /
NK030(a)002:1996: rnam rgyal dkar po kha tam dang /
NK030(a)002:1997: tri shul bsnams pa shar du bskyed /
NK030(a)002:1999: shar lhor dbyugs pa sngon po dbyug pa dang me dpung bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:2001: lhor gshin rje gshed mthing ka /
NK030(a)002:2002: be con dang dgra sta bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:2003: a ar+ya a tsa la h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2004: lho nub tu mi g.yo mgon po ljang dmar /
NK030(a)002:2005: spu gri dang zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:2007: nub tu rta mgrin dmar po ral gri dang sbrul zhags bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:2010: gzhan gyis mi thub pa sngon po ban d+ha dang rnga yab bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:2011: a mri ta kun+ta li h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2012: byang du bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang khu /
NK030(a)002:2013: rgya gram dang dril bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:2014: tre lo k+sha pi dza ya h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2016: khams gsum rnam rgyal ser po 'khor lo dang mche ba 'dzin pa /
NK030(a)002:2018: 'og tu stobs po che dud kha tho ba dang gtun shing bsnams /
NK030(a)002:2019: khro bo de rnams dur khrod kyi chas brgyad dang gar dgu yis brgyan pa'o //
NK030(a)002:2020: de ltar lha drug bcu rtsa brgyad po de dag la sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis brlabs /
NK030(a)002:2021: ye shes lnga'i dbang bskur snyan gsan dbab //
NK030(a)002:2022: spyan drangs pa la sogs bsnyen pa yan chad gong dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang mtshungs so //
NK030(a)002:2023: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i mngon rtogs la ting nge 'dzin rnam gsum nas /
NK030(a)002:2024: rten gzhal yas khang yan chad dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang mthun la /
NK030(a)002:2025: gzhal yas khang gi 'og gzhi 'khor lo sngon po rtsibs bzhi lte ba lnga'i dbus lnga /
NK030(a)002:2026: 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi pa re /
NK030(a)002:2030: blo 'bur dang bcas pa phyogs ma log pa /
NK030(a)002:2031: phyi'i lha rnams sgo dang bcas pa phyogs mdog /
NK030(a)002:2032: de nas lha bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)002:2033: dbus lte ba'i 'khor rtsibs bzhi ser po'i dbus su /
NK030(a)002:2034: bdud bzhi 'am brgyad dam nyi ma'i steng du badz+ra he ru ka sngon po /
NK030(a)002:2035: zhal gsum phyag drug yum dang bcas pa /
NK030(a)002:2036: rtsibs bzhi la rang rang gi gdan la rdo rje
NK030(a)002:2037: he ru ka'i rigs chung gi khro bo yab yum
NK030(a)002:2038: brgyad bskyed / shar rtsibs kyi dbus kyi 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi'i dbus /
NK030(a)002:2039: dri za khyu mchog nyi ma'i steng du /
NK030(a)002:2040: bud+d+ha he ru ka dkar po zhal gsum phyag drug yum dang bcas pa //
NK030(a)002:2041: rtsibs bzhi la rang rang gi gdan la b+hud+d+ha he
NK030(a)002:2042: ru ka'i rigs chung gi khro bo yab yum bskyed
NK030(a)002:2043: / lho rtsibs kyi 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi'i dbus su /
NK030(a)002:2044: gshin rje ma he nyi ma'i steng du /
NK030(a)002:2045: rat+na he ru ka ser po zhal gsum phyag drug yum dang bcas pa /
NK030(a)002:2046: rtsibs bzhi rang rang gi gdan la /
NK030(a)002:2047: rat+na he ru ka'i rigs chung gi khro bo yab yum brgyad bskyed /
NK030(a)002:2048: nub rtsibs kyi 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi'i dbus su klu gzugs nyi ma'i steng du /
NK030(a)002:2049: pad+ma he ru ka dmar po zhal gsum phyag drug yum dang bcas pa /
NK030(a)002:2050: rtsibs bzhi la rang rang gi gdan la /
NK030(a)002:2051: pad+ma he ru ka'i rigs chung gi khro bo yab yum brgyad bskyed /
NK030(a)002:2052: byang rtsibs kyi 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi'i dbus su /
NK030(a)002:2053: gnod sbyin brgyad sngags brgyad nyi ma'i steng du /
NK030(a)002:2054: karma he ru ka ljang khu zhal gsum phyag drug yum dang bcas pa /
NK030(a)002:2055: rtsibs bzhi la rang rang gi gdan la /
NK030(a)002:2056: karma he ru ka'i rigs chung gi khro bo yab yum brgyad bskyed do //
NK030(a)002:2057: phyi'i 'khor lo'i rtsibs mchan bzhi gru chad bzhi dang brgyad la /
NK030(a)002:2058: goo ri ma la sogs gnas kyi lha mo brgyad bskyed /
NK030(a)002:2059: lha snams nang ma'i phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad la phra men ma brgyad bskyed /
NK030(a)002:2060: blo 'bur bzhi la sgo ma bzhi /
NK030(a)002:2061: lha rnams phyi ma la dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad bskyed /
NK030(a)002:2062: sku mdog phyag mtshan ni gong dang mthun no //
NK030(a)002:2063: khro bo yab yum nyi shu bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)002:2064: badz+ra kro ta h+aum ka ra h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2065: h+aum las steng du h+aum ka ra sngo skya mda' gzhu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:2066: rang 'od kyi yum dang bcas pa bskyed /
NK030(a)002:2067: bi dza ya h+aum h+aum las /
NK030(a)002:2068: shar du rnam par rgyal ba dkar po kha t+aam dang tri shul bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:2069: rang 'od kyi yum dang bcas bskyed /
NK030(a)002:2071: ni lan da na tra h+aum h+aum las shar lhor
NK030(a)002:2072: dbyug pa sngon po dbyug pa dang me dpung bsnams
NK030(a)002:2073: pa / ya man ta ka h+aum h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2074: lho gshin rje gshed mthing kha be con dang dgra sta /
NK030(a)002:2075: lho nub ar+ya a tsa la h+aum h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2076: zhes mi g.yo mgon po sku mdog ljang dmar zhal
NK030(a)002:2077: gsum phyag drug spu gri dang zhags pa bsnams pa
NK030(a)002:2078: / ha ya g+hi wa h+aum h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2079: rta mgrin dmar po zhal gsum phyag drug ral gri dang sbrul zhags bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:2080: a pa ra dzi ta h+aum h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2081: nub byang gzhan gyis mi thub pa sngon po /
NK030(a)002:2082: bad+ha dang rnga yab bsnams pa'o //
NK030(a)002:2083: ar mri ta kun da li h+aum h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2084: byang du bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang khu /
NK030(a)002:2085: rgya gram dang dril bu bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:2086: tre lo k+sha bi dza ya h+aum h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2088: khams gsum rnam rgyal ser po 'khor lo dang mche ba bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:2089: ma h+aa ba la h+aum h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2090: 'og tu stobs po che dud kha tho ba dang gtun shing bsnams pa /
NK030(a)002:2091: khro bo de rnams dur khrod kyis chas brgyad dang /
NK030(a)002:2093: rang 'od kyis yum rnams la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)002:2094: yum rnams kyis g.yas pas gtso bo la 'khyud pa /
NK030(a)002:2095: g.yon dung dmar gtso bo la stobs pa /
NK030(a)002:2096: me dpung gi klong na bzhugs pa bskyed do //
NK030(a)002:2097: de ni sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i dkyil 'khor brgyas pa'i mngon rtogs so //
NK030(a)002:2098: de ltar lha brgya bco brgyad po de dag la sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa nas /
NK030(a)002:2099: bsnyen pa'i bar yan chad gong khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa'i skabs ltar ro //
NK030(a)002:2100: khro bo'i tshom bu gcig pa'i sngon rtogs la /
NK030(a)002:2102: rten gzhal yas khang yan chad dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang mthun la /
NK030(a)002:2103: 'khor lo'i dbus su bdud bzhi nyi ma'i gdan la /
NK030(a)002:2104: badz+ra he ru ka yab yum la rtsibs bzhi rang rang gi gdan la /
NK030(a)002:2105: badz+ra he ru ka'i rigs chung gi he ru ka yab yum brgyad /
NK030(a)002:2108: khro bo yab yum nyi shu ste /
NK030(a)002:2109: bdun bcu don brgyad bskyed do //
NK030(a)002:2110: de la sku gsung thugs byin rlabs nas bsnyen pa yan chod dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang mthun no //
NK030(a)002:2111: tshom bu gsum pa'i mngon rtogs la /
NK030(a)002:2112: ting nge 'dzin rnam gsum nas rten gzhan yas khang yan chad dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang mthun /
NK030(a)002:2113: 'khor lo'i lte ba'i dbus su 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi'i dbus su /
NK030(a)002:2114: bdud bzhi seng ge nyi zla'i gdan la /
NK030(a)002:2115: badz+ra he ru ka sngon po zhal gsum phyag drug yab yum la /
NK030(a)002:2116: rtsibs bzhi la rang rang gi gdan la /
NK030(a)002:2117: badz+ra he ru ka'i rigs chung gi he ru ka yab yum brgyad /
NK030(a)002:2118: shar rtsibs kyi dkyil 'khor rtsibs bzhi'i dbus su /
NK030(a)002:2119: dri za dang ma he'i nyi ma'i gdan la /
NK030(a)002:2120: bud+d+ha he ru ka dkar po zhal gsum phyag drug yum dang bcas pa /
NK030(a)002:2121: rtsibs bzhi la rang rang gi gdan la /
NK030(a)002:2122: bud+d+ha he ru ka'i rigs chung gi he ru ka yab yum brgyad /
NK030(a)002:2123: nub rtsibs kyi dbus su gshin rje dang stag gi gdan la /
NK030(a)002:2124: pad+ma he ru ka zhal gsum phyag drug yab yum dmar po /
NK030(a)002:2125: rtsibs bzhi rang rang gi gdan la pad+ma he ru
NK030(a)002:2126: ka'i rigs chung gi khro bo yab yum brgyad de
NK030(a)002:2127: / pho brang gi lha sum bcu /
NK030(a)002:2130: khro bo yab yum nyi shu ste /
NK030(a)002:2131: dgu bcu go brgyad bskyed la /
NK030(a)002:2132: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa nas /
NK030(a)002:2133: bsnyen pa yan chad gong dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang mthun no //
NK030(a)002:2134: tshom bu lnga pa'i dkyil 'khor kyi mngon rtogs la /
NK030(a)002:2136: rten gzhal yas khang yan chad gong dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang mthun la /
NK030(a)002:2137: 'khor lo sngon po rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang lnga'i steng du /
NK030(a)002:2138: 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi'i dbus dang rtsibs bzhi la /
NK030(a)002:2139: badz+ra he ru ka yab yum la sogs pa'i pho brang gi lha lnga bcu /
NK030(a)002:2140: lha mo nyi shu dbang mo nyer brgyad /
NK030(a)002:2141: khro bo yab yum nyi shu ste /
NK030(a)002:2142: brgya dang bco brgyad bskyed la /
NK030(a)002:2143: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa la sogs /
NK030(a)002:2144: bsnyen pa yan chad gong dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang mthun no //
NK030(a)002:2145: gsum pa mdun bskyed la drug ste /
NK030(a)002:2146: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang /
NK030(a)002:2152: de dag ji ltar bskyed pa'i tshul ni /
NK030(a)002:2153: gong bum bskyed dang mthun la /
NK030(a)002:2154: bar skabs su tshig kha bsgyur ro //
NK030(a)002:2155: gnyis pa rab gnas kyi sngon 'gro dngos ni /
NK030(a)002:2156: sku gzugs la sogs rab gnas kyi rten thams cad la ba byung lnga dang /
NK030(a)002:2157: mar khu shing shun lngas phyis te /
NK030(a)002:2158: de nas thod pa'i 'phreng ba thogs la /
NK030(a)002:2159: ho mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid
NK030(a)002:2160: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs
NK030(a)002:2161: 'khor rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang bcas pa thams cad
NK030(a)002:2162: / bdag rdo rje che ge mo la gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:2163: deng yon bdag che ge mo la sogs pa'i mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad /
NK030(a)002:2164: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho gnas nas bsgral zhing lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyir /
NK030(a)002:2165: bdag rdo rje che ge mos mdo' sgyu sems gsum
NK030(a)002:2166: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs la rab tu
NK030(a)002:2168: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bdag la mthu bstan du gsol //
NK030(a)002:2171: rab gnas ye shes dang ldan par mdzad du gsol //
NK030(a)002:2173: gnang ba thob par bsam mo //
NK030(a)002:2174: gnyis pa rab gnas kyi rten lhar bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)002:2175: shu nya ta nyer gcig brjod /
NK030(a)002:2176: chos thams cad stong pa nyid du gsal bar bsgom /
NK030(a)002:2177: de nas bdag gi thugs ka nas h+aum las byung
NK030(a)002:2178: ba'i ye ge lnga byung nas khro bo'i 'byung rim
NK030(a)002:2179: bskyed / b+h+rum las gzhal yas khang rgyan dang ldan par bskyed /
NK030(a)002:2180: gdan stengs su sku rnams kyang stong pa nyid kyi ye shes su gsal ba las /
NK030(a)002:2181: bdag yab yum sbyor ba byas pa'i byang chub sems
NK030(a)002:2182: las lha gang yin pa'i yig 'bru bton nas bkod
NK030(a)002:2183: de / gnyis su med par gsal ba las /
NK030(a)002:2184: cho ga gsum gyi lha rnams dam pa rgyan bzhin bskyed /
NK030(a)002:2186: byin gyis brlabs par bsam la /
NK030(a)002:2187: h+aum chos dbyings mnyams pa chen po la //
NK030(a)002:2188: ye shes gsal bar gnas pa dang //
NK030(a)002:2189: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyis //
NK030(a)002:2190: skye med chos la dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)002:2191: shunya ta dz+nya na nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:2192: dag cing gsal ba'i rang bzhin ste /
NK030(a)002:2193: skyon med sems nyid rin po che /
NK030(a)002:2194: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis /
NK030(a)002:2195: srid pa gsum la dbang bsgyur shog /
NK030(a)002:2196: a da sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK030(a)002:2197: s+w+aa khams gsum re bskong rgyal po ste /
NK030(a)002:2198: yid bzhin re bskongs gter gyis mchog /
NK030(a)002:2199: mnyam pa nyid kyis ye shes kyis /
NK030(a)002:2200: 'gro ba'i re bskongs rgyal por shog /
NK030(a)002:2201: sa man ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:2202: skye 'gag med pa'i dngos grub ste //
NK030(a)002:2203: nyes pa'i skyon bral dri med pa //
NK030(a)002:2204: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK030(a)002:2205: srid gsum nyes mig bral bar shog /
NK030(a)002:2206: pra t+ya be k+sha na dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham //
NK030(a)002:2207: dbyiings kyi dkyil 'khor mthar phyin cing /
NK030(a)002:2208: grub pa las kyi bye brag las /
NK030(a)002:2209: bya ba nan tan ye shes kyis /
NK030(a)002:2210: skye 'gro dbyings su sgrol bar shog /
NK030(a)002:2211: kri t+yam nush+tha dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK030(a)002:2212: na mo 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs la //
NK030(a)002:2213: rigs lnga'i dbu brgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)002:2214: deng yon gyi bdag po dang bdag dang mtha' yas
NK030(a)002:2215: pa'i sems can thams cad kyis rigs lnga ye shes
NK030(a)002:2216: lnga'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig bde gshegs
NK030(a)002:2218: mi shig rdo rje rgyal ba'i gtso //
NK030(a)002:2219: sngags dang phyag rgya lngan pa yis //
NK030(a)002:2220: rdo rje sku yi gtso bor shog /
NK030(a)002:2221: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK030(a)002:2222: +aah bde gshegs gsung gi ngo bo las //
NK030(a)002:2223: mi shigs rdo rje chos kyi dbyings //
NK030(a)002:2224: sngags dang phyag rgya ldan pa yis //
NK030(a)002:2225: rdo rje gsung gi ngo bor shog /
NK030(a)002:2226: sarba ta th+aa ga ta wak+ka badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:2227: h+aum bde gshegs thugs kyi ngo bo las /
NK030(a)002:2228: mi shig rdo rje chos kyi dbyings /
NK030(a)002:2229: sngags dang phyag rgya ldan pa yis //
NK030(a)002:2230: rdo rje thugs kyi gtso bor shog /
NK030(a)002:2231: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:2232: swa mi 'gyur ba'i zhing khams na /
NK030(a)002:2236: cir yang 'gyur ba'i ye shes kyis //
NK030(a)002:2237: rang dbang thabs kyis bsgyur bar shog /
NK030(a)002:2238: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au tsa badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:2239: h+aa thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i /
NK030(a)002:2242: las dang dngos grub kun snang ba //
NK030(a)002:2243: ma lus nyams pa sbyor bar shog /
NK030(a)002:2244: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu ra ga badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:2245: na mo khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams la /
NK030(a)002:2246: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lngas byin gyis
NK030(a)002:2247: rlabs pas sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las mi
NK030(a)002:2248: zad pa brgyan gyi 'khor lo dang ldan par gyur
NK030(a)002:2249: cig / gsum pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing bstim pa ni /
NK030(a)002:2251: dam can gyi spyan 'dren skabs 'dir byed do //
NK030(a)002:2253: h+aum ye shes rab snang sangs rgyas kun gyis gnas /
NK030(a)002:2254: 'khor lo dur khrod da la rab rib can /
NK030(a)002:2255: rnam bzhi dbyibs tshul sgo dgu sgo rtser ldan /
NK030(a)002:2256: rang bzhin lhun grub de la bzhes su gsol /
NK030(a)002:2257: tshad med rnams bzhi rang snang rang byung ba /
NK030(a)002:2258: rdo rje rat+na pad+ma rgya gram rtsegs //
NK030(a)002:2259: rgyu mthun gling bzhir 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa /
NK030(a)002:2260: bla med dal la bzhi po gshegs su gsol /
NK030(a)002:2261: bcom ldan sprul sku'i mdzad pa las byung ba /
NK030(a)002:2262: lha las bab pa'i dal la gshegs su gsol /
NK030(a)002:2263: pad+ma can gyis mdzad pa las byung ba /
NK030(a)002:2264: byang chub chen po'i dal la gshegs su gsol /
NK030(a)002:2265: chos kyi 'khor lo'i mdzad pa las byung ba //
NK030(a)002:2266: gser mdog 'od can da la gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:2267: bkra shis sgo mang mdzad pa las byung ba //
NK030(a)002:2268: sgo ma bzhi po'i dal la gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:2269: shar nas byams ldan mthar legs g.yung drung rdzogs //
NK030(a)002:2270: lho nas yid bzhin lhun grub ka ni ka /
NK030(a)002:2271: byang nas khams gsum smad drag bde ba rgyas /
NK030(a)002:2272: nub nas pad+ma bsam 'das rin chen rtsegs /
NK030(a)002:2273: byin gnas dal la brgyad po gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:2274: la la byin brlabs rata na skur snang yang /
NK030(a)002:2275: nub byang rgyal po'i mig nad zhi mdzad pa //
NK030(a)002:2276: thugs rje'i dal la rnam gnyis gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:2277: dregs pa'i rgyal po dur khrod brgyad kyi rten //
NK030(a)002:2278: ma mo'i gnas dang sid+d+hi kun gyi gzhi //
NK030(a)002:2279: bde byed brten dang ri bo ta la sogs //
NK030(a)002:2280: sgrub pa'i dal la brgyad po gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:2281: mkha' sogs 'byung dang 'byung 'gyur ma lus pa //
NK030(a)002:2282: rang byung ye shes snang ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK030(a)002:2283: gdul bya cir snang 'dul ba don mdzad pa //
NK030(a)002:2284: yid kyi dal la brgyad po gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:2285: de dag rnams kyang theg pa so so yi //
NK030(a)002:2286: tha dad rnams la mthun par skur bzhengs pa'i //
NK030(a)002:2287: sprul pa'i dal la ji rnyed bzhugs su gsol /
NK030(a)002:2289: / 'gro ba'i don phyir spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:2291: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan /
NK030(a)002:2293: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2294: e a ra i hreng hreng /
NK030(a)002:2295: phyogs bcu dal la'i tshogs ni spyan drangs so //
NK030(a)002:2296: thabs chen ma 'dres rnam thar cir snang yang //
NK030(a)002:2297: dus bzhi'i rgyal po rang rig nyid du 'dus /
NK030(a)002:2298: da la rnams gsum rang rig ming gi phyir //
NK030(a)002:2299: snying po byang chub mthar ni ba rtan par bzhugs //
NK030(a)002:2300: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra /
NK030(a)002:2301: sems can don phyir nan tan mdzad //
NK030(a)002:2302: chos sku mu mtha' dpag mi rigs //
NK030(a)002:2303: thabs mkhas phyag rgya rgyu 'bras rdzogs //
NK030(a)002:2304: rang byung rol pa rang snang yang //
NK030(a)002:2305: dus gsum rgyal ba bzhugs gnas khang //
NK030(a)002:2306: rang bzhi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2307: thugs kyi byin rlabs cir yang snang //
NK030(a)002:2308: sna tshogs thabs kyi 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK030(a)002:2309: sprul pa'i dal la brgyad po dang //
NK030(a)002:2310: bla med dal la rnam bzhi po //
NK030(a)002:2311: byin rlabs rol pa'i dal la brgyad //
NK030(a)002:2312: thugs rje'i da la la la sogs pa //
NK030(a)002:2313: sgo gsum dang bas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2314: dmigs med chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2315: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2316: cir yang sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2317: mngon par byang chub sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2318: khams gsum zhing du spyor la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2319: bdag med phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing //
NK030(a)002:2320: byams dang snying rje'i dgra zin mi mnga' yang //
NK030(a)002:2321: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus la mi 'da' ba'i /
NK030(a)002:2323: / 'jigs byed he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2324: srid gsum 'joms pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2325: mnyams nyid ngang gis khro la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2326: khro bo longs spyod mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2327: rdo rje 'du 'phro mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2328: mig gnas mi dmigs chos sku dag pa la //
NK030(a)002:2329: bdud 'dul khro bo mchog gi skur ston pa //
NK030(a)002:2330: thugs rjes gzir ldan gdugs pa thabs kyi 'dul //
NK030(a)002:2331: bcom ldan khro rgyal gtso la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2332: khro bo dbang phyug sku la nyer gnas shing //
NK030(a)002:2333: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i dkyil 'khor na //
NK030(a)002:2334: mkha' 'gro mi zad 'bar ba'i sprin 'phro ma //
NK030(a)002:2335: gdug pa 'dul mdzad yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2336: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing /
NK030(a)002:2338: / 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK030(a)002:2339: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK030(a)002:2340: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK030(a)002:2343: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las dang /
NK030(a)002:2344: zhing khams dag pa zad mi shes pa'i bden pa dang /
NK030(a)002:2345: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK030(a)002:2346: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK030(a)002:2347: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la phyag dang pu tsa 'bul bas /
NK030(a)002:2348: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams dang gnyis su med pa'i don /
NK030(a)002:2350: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2353: kun tu bzang po'i p+au tsa 'bul /
NK030(a)002:2354: bdag dpal chen po'i mchod pa la longs spyod pa'i skal ba dang ldan ste /
NK030(a)002:2355: deng yon bdag la sogs pa'i sems thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2356: bzhi pa dbang po'i skyon gsal ba la /
NK030(a)002:2357: gser gyi thur ma thogs la /
NK030(a)002:2358: rin chen rgyu las byas pa yis //
NK030(a)002:2359: gser gyis thur mas spyan phyes pas //
NK030(a)002:2360: dbang po rnams kyi skyon bsal nas //
NK030(a)002:2361: ye shes spyan mnga' thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2362: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK030(a)002:2363: bden pa gser gyis thur mas lha rnams kyi spyan phyes pas /
NK030(a)002:2364: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can rnams ye shes kyi spyan dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2365: snyan bzhar thogs la rin chen rgyu las byas pa yis //
NK030(a)002:2366: gser gyi snyan bzhar snyan gsal bas //
NK030(a)002:2367: dbang bo rnams kyis skyon gsal nas //
NK030(a)002:2368: ye shes snyan rnams thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2370: lha rnams kyis snyan phyis pas /
NK030(a)002:2371: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad ye shes kyi snyan dang ldan bar gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2373: rin chen rgyu las byas pa yis //
NK030(a)002:2374: gser gyi rmang tsher shangs kyi spu gtogs pas //
NK030(a)002:2375: shangs kyi dbang po'i skyon rnams bsal ba yis //
NK030(a)002:2376: sems kyi rnam grangs ma lus thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2378: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi shangs gsal bas /
NK030(a)002:2380: sems can thams cad kyi dri ma sel bar gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2382: gser gyis rgyu las byas pa yis //
NK030(a)002:2383: ljags kyi dri ma gzhar ba yis //
NK030(a)002:2384: gsung rab sor sor 'chad par shog /
NK030(a)002:2386: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi dri ma bsal bas /
NK030(a)002:2387: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis chos 'chad par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2389: rat+na'i rgyu las byas pa yis /
NK030(a)002:2390: tshems kyi shing bu 'di yis ni /
NK030(a)002:2391: tshems kyi dri ma bsal ba dang /
NK030(a)002:2392: mnyam par bzhag pa thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2394: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis dri ma bsal ba dang /
NK030(a)002:2395: mnyam par bzhag pa thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2396: dung gi so mang thogs la /
NK030(a)002:2397: rat+na'i rgyu la byas pa yis //
NK030(a)002:2398: dung gi so mang dbu skra bsil //
NK030(a)002:2399: dbu skra lcang lo'i skyon bsal nas //
NK030(a)002:2400: nyon mongs dri ma dag par shog /
NK030(a)002:2401: bden pa dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyis dbu skra shad pas /
NK030(a)002:2402: bdag dang yon bdag sems can thams cad kyi dri ma dag par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2403: gser gyi chen pa thogs la /
NK030(a)002:2404: rat+na'i rgyu las byas pa yis /
NK030(a)002:2405: gser gyi chen pa btab pa yis //
NK030(a)002:2406: dbu skra zhal gyi spu bregs pas //
NK030(a)002:2407: nyon mongs zung rngu bral bar shog /
NK030(a)002:2408: bden pa dkyil 'khor kyi lha rnams kyi dbu skra gser gyi spu gris bsal bas /
NK030(a)002:2409: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyi
NK030(a)002:2410: nyon mongs pa'i zung rngu dang bral bar gyur cig
NK030(a)002:2412: bde gshegs sku la me long 'di bstan pas /
NK030(a)002:2413: bdag dang sems thams cad kyis /
NK030(a)002:2414: chos rnams gzugs brnyan ltar rtogs nas /
NK030(a)002:2415: 'gro bas lta ba'i 'os su 'gyur bar shog /
NK030(a)002:2417: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la me long phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2418: chos thams cad gzugs brnyan lta bur rtogs te /
NK030(a)002:2419: brjod du med pa'i don bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2420: lnga pa chus khrus gsol ba la /
NK030(a)002:2421: shun gyi chu khrus gsol la /
NK030(a)002:2422: don dam bcud kyi thig le chen po 'di /
NK030(a)002:2423: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2424: lhan gcig skyes pa'i sgrib pa kun dag nas //
NK030(a)002:2425: a a sgrib pa kun dag nas /
NK030(a)002:2426: byang chub sems kyi rlan dang ldan par shog /
NK030(a)002:2427: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta dz+nya na bi shud+d+he h+aum h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2429: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus shun gyis sku khrus gsol ba'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK030(a)002:2430: bdag dang yon bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems thams
NK030(a)002:2431: cad kyis lhan gcig skyes pa'i sgrib pa yongs su
NK030(a)002:2432: dag nas bde chen byang chub kyi sems kyi rlan
NK030(a)002:2433: dang ldan pa'i sgo nas 'gro ba'i don byed par
NK030(a)002:2434: gyur cig / thal chen gyis chus khrus gsol ba /
NK030(a)002:2435: lhag pa'i thal bas 'phrin las rdzogs pa'i chus /
NK030(a)002:2437: / 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK030(a)002:2438: bdag gzhan gnyis 'dzin sgrib pa kun dag nas //
NK030(a)002:2439: gnyis su med pa'i don dang ldan par shog /
NK030(a)002:2440: badz+ra b+hi sa smi ti dz+ny+aa na bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2442: thal chen gyis chus khrus gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2443: kun tu brtags pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK030(a)002:2444: gnyis su med pa'i don dang ldan pa'i sgo nas 'gro ba'i don byed par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2446: skye med byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin te //
NK030(a)002:2447: dkar la dag pa gnyis med ye shes chus /
NK030(a)002:2449: / 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2450: rdo rje rigs kyis sid+hi thog par shog /
NK030(a)002:2451: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta dz+nya na bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2453: me long lta bu'i ye shes gsal ba la /
NK030(a)002:2454: rtogs pa med pa'i don rtogs nas /
NK030(a)002:2455: rdo rje rig kyi byang chub sems kyi khrus gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2456: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyi
NK030(a)002:2457: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i
NK030(a)002:2458: ye shes chen po thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2460: dri chen gsang ba'i rdzas chen dam rdzas mchog /
NK030(a)002:2461: skye shi med pa rdo rje'i rang bzhin chus /
NK030(a)002:2463: / 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK030(a)002:2464: de bzhin rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2465: badz+ra +aa yuh dz+nya na b+hi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2467: dri chen stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi /
NK030(a)002:2468: ye nas yod med stong pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK030(a)002:2469: de bzhin rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2470: mam sa'i chus khrus byed la /
NK030(a)002:2471: khams gsum pa'i rgyud drug sems can rnams //
NK030(a)002:2472: dug gsum bsgral ba'i sha chen bcud kyis chus /
NK030(a)002:2474: / 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK030(a)002:2475: rat+na rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2476: ma h+aa mam sa dz+nya bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2477: bden pa sha chen chu yis khrus gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2478: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis //
NK030(a)002:2479: nga dang bdag 'dzin med rtogs nas //
NK030(a)002:2480: rat+na rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2482: pad+ma ra k+ta gsang ba dbang gi rdzas /
NK030(a)002:2483: chags par med pa'i gsal la dngas pa'i chus /
NK030(a)002:2485: / 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol bas //
NK030(a)002:2486: pad+ma rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2487: ma h+aa pad+ma rak+ta ti la ka bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2490: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK030(a)002:2491: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid don rtogs nas //
NK030(a)002:2492: pad+ma rigs kyi sid+hi thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2494: dri chu kun gyis gsos byed las kyi rigs //
NK030(a)002:2495: thams cad khrus byed bdud rtsi chen po'i chu /
NK030(a)002:2497: / 'jigs byed sku la khrus chab 'di gsol bas //
NK030(a)002:2498: las kyi rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2499: badz+ra ma h+aa ma ma ku ku dz+nya na b+hi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2501: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK030(a)002:2502: bdag gzhan dngos grub don rtogs nas /
NK030(a)002:2503: las kyi rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2505: yang dag nyid du dag mod kyang /
NK030(a)002:2507: / 'jig rten srid zhu'i tshul gyis ni //
NK030(a)002:2508: phyag dang zhabs ni bsil mdzod la /
NK030(a)002:2510: / 'di nyid du ni bzhugs su gsol //
NK030(a)002:2511: phyag dang zhabs bsil gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2512: phyi nang gi dri ma thams cad dag pa'i don rtogs par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2513: sarba ta th+aa ga ta swa b+ha wa b+hi shud d+he h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2515: thugs rje lhun grub khrag 'thung dkyil 'khor lo /
NK030(a)002:2516: sku la srid zhu gus phyir ras kyis sku phyis pas /
NK030(a)002:2517: las dang nyon mongs bag chags kun byang nas /
NK030(a)002:2518: spyod lam rnam par dag pa'i sku thob shog /
NK030(a)002:2520: ras kyi sku phyis pas gzugs 'dzin las byung ba'i
NK030(a)002:2521: las dang nyon mongs pa'i dri ma dag nas spyod
NK030(a)002:2522: lam rnam par dag pa'i sgo thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2523: drug pa mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK030(a)002:2524: lha mo bzhi bsnol gyi sngags brjod pas khrag la /
NK030(a)002:2525: yon tan lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku mchog la /
NK030(a)002:2526: khrag gi mdzes pa'i me tog 'di phul bas //
NK030(a)002:2527: log lta'i nyon mongs tha ba kun bral nas //
NK030(a)002:2528: lta bas mi ngom mdzes pa'i sku thob shog /
NK030(a)002:2531: khrag gi me tog gis mchod pa phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2533: sems can thams cad tha ba bral te tshogs thams
NK030(a)002:2534: cad yongs su rdzogs nas lta bas mi ngoms pa'i
NK030(a)002:2535: sku thob ste / sems can thams cad yongs su dag par byed par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2537: mchog tu rnam par dag pa'i sku mnga' ba'i /
NK030(a)002:2539: / 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la 'di phul bas //
NK030(a)002:2540: dam tshig sdom pa'i nyes pa kun bral nas //
NK030(a)002:2541: ye shes thugs rje ma lus 'dzin par shog /
NK030(a)002:2543: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la tshil chen gyi mchod pa phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2544: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad theg pa so so'i dri ma las grol ste /
NK030(a)002:2545: dam tshig rnam par dag nas /
NK030(a)002:2546: thugs rje chen pos phyogs lung bston pa'i phung po yongs su 'dzin pa' sku thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2548: mchog tu rnam par dag pa'i sku mnga' yis /
NK030(a)002:2549: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la mun pa snang byed 'di phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2550: ma rig 'thibs po'i mun pa kun bral nas /
NK030(a)002:2551: sangs rgyas spyan mnga' yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK030(a)002:2554: mar ma'i mchod pa phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2555: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad lhan
NK030(a)002:2556: cig gnas pa'i ma rig las byung ba'i rab rib
NK030(a)002:2558: sangs rgyas kyi spyan lnga thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2560: snyigs ma lnga nyid 'bras bu yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK030(a)002:2561: sangs rgyas sku la dri chab 'di phul bas //
NK030(a)002:2562: mya ngan zu ngu'i duhkha kun bral nas /
NK030(a)002:2564: / 'od zer ma lus 'gyed pa'i sku thob shog /
NK030(a)002:2566: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la dri chab 'di phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2567: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad /
NK030(a)002:2568: mya ngan zu ngu gdung ba kun bral nas /
NK030(a)002:2569: 'od zer mtha' yas 'gyed pa thob par shog /
NK030(a)002:2571: ye shes sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa yis /
NK030(a)002:2572: 'jigs byed sku la bdud rtsi 'di phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2573: dug lnga'i gdod nas sems su dag gyur pa'i /
NK030(a)002:2574: ye shes sku lnga lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK030(a)002:2577: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la bdud rtsi sman gyi p+au tsa phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2578: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad dug lnga ma spangs gnas su dag nas /
NK030(a)002:2579: ye shes sku lnga lhun gyis grub par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2581: chos rnams longs spyod yongs su rdzogs pa yis /
NK030(a)002:2582: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la gtor ma 'di phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2583: rdzas su spyod pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas /
NK030(a)002:2584: gsang ba'i longs spyod yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK030(a)002:2586: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2587: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad rdzas su spyod pa'i gdung pa thams cad bral nas /
NK030(a)002:2588: gsang ba'i spyod pa yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2589: rak+ta tshar gsum tshig brjod la /
NK030(a)002:2591: rak+ta tshar gsum gyi p+au tsa phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2592: bdag dang yon bdag sogs byang chub sems kyi sems dbyer med par rtogs nas /
NK030(a)002:2593: sems nyid dbye ba med pa thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2595: ye shes spyod yul yongs su dag pa yis /
NK030(a)002:2597: / 'jigs byed sku la ta na 'di phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2598: khams gsum dug gsum dag gyur ste //
NK030(a)002:2599: sku gsung thugs kyi sid+d+hi lhun gyis grub /
NK030(a)002:2600: ri rab chen po brjid pa'i don rtogs shog /
NK030(a)002:2602: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la ta na'i mchod pa phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2603: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyi dug gsum yongs su dag nas /
NK030(a)002:2604: sku gsum gyi 'khor yongs su 'a grub par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2605: gzhung gi sbyor mchod byas la /
NK030(a)002:2606: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med pa yis /
NK030(a)002:2607: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la g+ha na 'di phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2608: phyi nang byang chub sems su rnam dag ste /
NK030(a)002:2609: mtha' yas snying por 'jug pa thob par shog  /
NK030(a)002:2610: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la thabs dang shes rab g+ha na sbyor ba'i mchod pa phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2611: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis
NK030(a)002:2612: thabs dang shes rab kyi spyod pas snod bcud thig
NK030(a)002:2613: le chen po yongs su dag ste /
NK030(a)002:2614: mtha' yas lhun gyis grub pa'i ting nge 'dzin thob par spyod yul yongs su dag ste /
NK030(a)002:2615: mthong ba med pa mthong ba la sogs pa'i thabs yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2616: glu ye shes kyi pu tsa phul la /
NK030(a)002:2619: glu ye shes kyi pu tsa phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2620: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad che
NK030(a)002:2621: ba'i yon tan tham cad mngon par mthong bas kun
NK030(a)002:2622: gyis bkur ba'i gnas su gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2627: bro gar ye shes kyi p+au tsa phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2629: sems can thams cad thabs la mkhas pa'i rdzu 'phrul
NK030(a)002:2630: gyi bya ba mang pos bdag dang gzhan gyi don
NK030(a)002:2631: thams cad lhun gyis grub par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2633: rnam dag sgrib spangs bardzoda la /
NK030(a)002:2636: rol mo ye shes kyi p+au tsa phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2637: bdag dang yon bdag tshangs pa'i gsung gi chos sgra chen po thos nas /
NK030(a)002:2638: rgyun mi 'chad pa'i don brda' 'phrod par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2639: bdun pa che ba'i yon tan mnga' gsol ba la bco lnga las /
NK030(a)002:2640: dang po dpal chas brgyad kyi ni /
NK030(a)002:2641: thod phreng skam po dbul ba /
NK030(a)002:2642: gsang ba ye shes lnga'i bdag /
NK030(a)002:2643: rigs mchog lnga dang ldan pa yis //
NK030(a)002:2644: khams gsum dbang po mnga' gsol bas //
NK030(a)002:2645: thod 'phreng thugs rjee chen po'i gzugs //
NK030(a)002:2647: mi brjed gzungs dang ting 'dzin gyis /
NK030(a)002:2649: / 'jigs byed sku la mnga' gsol lo //
NK030(a)002:2651: cod pan chos mchog sbrul chun la /
NK030(a)002:2652: ye shes sbrul gyis chas brgyad ni /
NK030(a)002:2653: zhe sdang gnas su dag pa'i rtags /
NK030(a)002:2654: 'jigs byed sku la sbrul chun 'di phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2655: dbyings phyug gsum dang ldan par shog /
NK030(a)002:2656: na ga ra tsa h+au lu hu lu a b+hi shi ny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2658: g.yang gzhi khyab pa'i thugs rje de /
NK030(a)002:2659: 'gro drug yongs su khyab pa yis //
NK030(a)002:2660: nga rgyal dag nas thabs la mkhas pa yis /
NK030(a)002:2662: badz+ra tig+na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2664: ko rlon chos sku brjid pa che //
NK030(a)002:2665: gti mug gnas su dag pa'i rtags /
NK030(a)002:2667: / 'jigs byed sku la ko rlon 'di phul bas //
NK030(a)002:2668: stobs bcu yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK030(a)002:2669: da ra pa sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2671: dpa' bo stag gi sham thabs ni /
NK030(a)002:2672: phrag dog gnas su dag pa'i rtags /
NK030(a)002:2673: 'jigs byed sku la stag lpags 'di phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2674: phas kyi rgol ba thams cad tshar gcod shog /
NK030(a)002:2675: bya kri dza ra ma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2677: zhag gi zo ris mtshan pa ni //
NK030(a)002:2678: he ru ka'i gnas bcu dang //
NK030(a)002:2679: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK030(a)002:2680: sangs rgyas kun dang bcings pa'i phyir /
NK030(a)002:2682: / 'jigs byed kun la mnga' dbul bya //
NK030(a)002:2683: ma h+aa b+ho d+hi tsit+ta sid+d+hi ku ru a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2684: zhag gi zo ris kyi mnga' gsol phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2685: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad dang /
NK030(a)002:2686: thugs dam gcig pa'i skal pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2688: rak+ta'i thig le brgyan pa ni //
NK030(a)002:2689: he ru ka'i gnas bcu dang //
NK030(a)002:2690: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK030(a)002:2691: d+aak+ki kun dang gcig pa'i phyir //
NK030(a)002:2692: rak+ta'i thig le mtshan pa ni /
NK030(a)002:2694: / 'jigs byed sku la mnga' dbul bya //
NK030(a)002:2695: rak+ta ti la kha kha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2697: rak+ta'i thig les mnga' dbul bas /
NK030(a)002:2698: d+aak+ki kun dang thugs dam gcig par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2700: lhag ma'i thal bas mtshan pa ni /
NK030(a)002:2701: he ru ka'i gnas bcu dang /
NK030(a)002:2702: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas /
NK030(a)002:2703: ging chen kun la brgyan pa ni /
NK030(a)002:2704: 'jigs byed sku la mnga' dbul bya /
NK030(a)002:2705: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2707: thal chen gyis mnga' dbul bas /
NK030(a)002:2708: sgrol byed kyi ging thams cad dang /
NK030(a)002:2709: thugs dam gcig pa gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2711: chags sdang snyoms pa dregs pa khyo shugs dang //
NK030(a)002:2712: rang bzhin 'od gsal zhing chen zhi ba'i gdan /
NK030(a)002:2714: / 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la gdan phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2715: 'bras bu'i chos rnams yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK030(a)002:2716: ma h+aa sur+ya ti ra dza a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK030(a)002:2717: dur dang de las sems can dang nyi zla la sogs pa'i gdan du bsam la /
NK030(a)002:2718: dur khrod dregs pa pho mo dang //
NK030(a)002:2719: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK030(a)002:2720: gtum po dom dang nyi zla'i gdan //
NK030(a)002:2721: zhabs bzhi bdud bzhi 'dul ba'i rtags //
NK030(a)002:2722: dreg pa gdan gyis mnga' gsol lo /
NK030(a)002:2724: dregs pa gdan gyis mnga' gsol bas //
NK030(a)002:2726: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2727: khro bo chen po yon tan gyi sgo nas mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK030(a)002:2731: dpal chen he ru ka'i lha rnams sku mdog gi mnga' gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2732: gting dpag dka' ba'i chos nyid dang /
NK030(a)002:2734: 'dul dka' drag po'i 'phrin las dang gsum /
NK030(a)002:2736: ma slad pa'i ye shes dpag dka' ba'i chos nyid dang /
NK030(a)002:2737: cir yang 'gyur ba'i 'phrin las gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i 'phrin las /
NK030(a)002:2738: thabs la mkhas pa'i mdzad spyod /
NK030(a)002:2739: khyad par 'phags pa'i che ba dang gsum /
NK030(a)002:2740: thabs dang shes rab kyi 'brel pa /
NK030(a)002:2741: gang yang ma spangs pa'i lta ba /
NK030(a)002:2742: ma chad pa'i mdzad spyod gsum /
NK030(a)002:2743: gang yang mi 'dor ba'i mdzad spyod /
NK030(a)002:2744: cir yang ston pa'i phrin las /
NK030(a)002:2745: thams cad mi 'gags par snang ba'i rol mo rnams bdag dang yon bdag dang /
NK030(a)002:2746: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK030(a)002:2747: srid gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur gcig  /
NK030(a)002:2749: dbu gsum gsal bar byas pas /
NK030(a)002:2751: he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la dbu gsum gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2752: rnam par thar pa'i sgo gsum dang /
NK030(a)002:2753: dgu phrugs su lhun gyis grub ste /
NK030(a)002:2754: khams gsum sa dgu'i don mdzad pa /
NK030(a)002:2755: slob ma che ge la sogs pa khams gsum gyis sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2756: yi ge lnga'i mum spros bsdus pas /
NK030(a)002:2760: dpal he ru ka la sogs pa la /
NK030(a)002:2761: phyag drug bco brgyad kyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2762: ye shes chen po drug dang /
NK030(a)002:2763: stong pa bco brgyad kyis 'bras bus bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2766: zhabs bzhi'i brgyad kyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2768: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyis bdud bzhi zil gyis
NK030(a)002:2769: non pa'i 'bras bu bdag dang sems can thams cad
NK030(a)002:2771: dza'i 'phro 'du las ral pa mthon mthing lcang lo bsam la /
NK030(a)002:2772: bden pa che ge'i lha la ral pas mnga' gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2774: mthar mi ltung ba'i lta ba gsum bdag dang yon
NK030(a)002:2775: bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur
NK030(a)002:2777: am 'phro 'dus lce glog dmar lta bu bsam la /
NK030(a)002:2778: bden pa khyab byed ljags kyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2779: sgra'i yan lag bsam mi khyab /
NK030(a)002:2780: gdul bya smin par byed pa yi //
NK030(a)002:2781: bdag dang yon bdag sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2783: mche ba dkar bo bsam la /
NK030(a)002:2785: dpal he ru ka'i lha la mche ba'i mnga' gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2786: skye shi rtsa ba gcod pa'i sgrib pa thams cad zad par byed pa'i 'bras bus /
NK030(a)002:2788: sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2789: ma las spyan me dpung 'bar bar bskyed la /
NK030(a)002:2791: dpal chen po la spyan gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2792: chos nyid mi 'gyur ba'i spyan dang /
NK030(a)002:2793: thugs rjes khyab pa'i spyan dang /
NK030(a)002:2794: ye shes ma g.yos pa'i spyan dang don rnams pa /
NK030(a)002:2795: lhun gyis grub bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2797: ral pa khams nag tu bskyed la /
NK030(a)002:2799: dpal chen po la ral pa'i mnga' gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2802: mthar ma lhung ba'i lta ba gsum /
NK030(a)002:2803: yon bdag sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2804: ra las smin ma dmar ser 'khyug pa bsam /
NK030(a)002:2808: thabs mkhas pas gdul bya chud mi gson pa /
NK030(a)002:2809: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2810: ka las sma ra ser po me stag 'phro ba bsam /
NK030(a)002:2812: khro bo dang phra men ma la sogs pa dang /
NK030(a)002:2813: sprul pa mang pos don mdzad kyang /
NK030(a)002:2814: rigs pa'i ye shes ma g.yos pa'i don bdag dang
NK030(a)002:2815: yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis thob par
NK030(a)002:2816: gyur cig / h+aum drug brgyad phyag mtshan gsal bas /
NK030(a)002:2818: dbyings dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa yi /
NK030(a)002:2819: dug gsum dbang du bsdud cing /
NK030(a)002:2820: rig pa gsung gi brda' sprod pa dang /
NK030(a)002:2821: 'khor ba ma spangs pa spyad pa'i don /
NK030(a)002:2822: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2823: re'i 'phro 'dus rin po che'i mgur chu bsam /
NK030(a)002:2825: che ge'i lha rnams la rin po che'i mgur chus mnga' gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2826: gsung lnga'i yon tan mthar phyin nas /
NK030(a)002:2827: chos thams cad kyi don ma 'dres par ston zhing /
NK030(a)002:2828: gdul bya thams cad chud mi gson pa'i don /
NK030(a)002:2829: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2831: rol pa nyi shu dang ldan par bskyed la /
NK030(a)002:2833: dpal chen po la rol pa chen po chos kyi 'brug dang /
NK030(a)002:2844: blang dor med par gsol ba dang /
NK030(a)002:2848: mi g.yo ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK030(a)002:2850: snang srid kyis phyag rgya gsal ba'i bden pa dang /
NK030(a)002:2851: chos kyi ro mnyam pa snang /
NK030(a)002:2852: snang ba ma g.yos pa zung du 'jug pa dang /
NK030(a)002:2853: de ltar yon tan gyi rol pa nyi shu dang ldan pa'i dbang /
NK030(a)002:2854: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2856: yon tan gyis che ba nyi shu dang ldan par
NK030(a)002:2857: bskyed la bden pa gnyen po med pas che ba
NK030(a)002:2858: dang / 'gran zla med pa'i che ba dang khyad par 'phags pas che ba dang /
NK030(a)002:2863: thams cad du ma pham pas /
NK030(a)002:2867: thams cad kyi gos pa med pas /
NK030(a)002:2874: mche bas mnan pas che ba dang /
NK030(a)002:2875: de ltar che ba nyi shu yon tan bdag dang /
NK030(a)002:2876: rnal 'byor pa sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2877: pa'i 'phro 'du las brjid nyi shu dang ldan par bsam /
NK030(a)002:2879: dpal chen po la brjid che nyi shus mnga' gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2880: sku che yan lag rags pa brjid che /
NK030(a)002:2881: grangs mang brgyan du mtshams pas brjid che /
NK030(a)002:2882: bskur 'os gtso bor mthong bas khyad par bzhugs yid
NK030(a)002:2883: dang 'thad pas gdangs che stong gsum gang bas tshig
NK030(a)002:2884: nyung the tshom chod pas bdag la nye tsher ston
NK030(a)002:2885: pas khyad par yon tan mtho bas spangs pas re
NK030(a)002:2886: dog med pas gsal bas mtha' gnyis spangs pas thugs
NK030(a)002:2887: rje thugs dam rdzogs pas ma rmongs thabs kyis 'dul
NK030(a)002:2888: ba med pas zad mi shes pas gcig la 'dod
NK030(a)002:2889: dgur dbang sgyur bas brjid gnod sbyor pham par mdzad
NK030(a)002:2890: pas thabs mkhas skyon gyis ma gos pa mi snying
NK030(a)002:2891: nyams bag rol bas dgos 'dod lhun gyis grub pas
NK030(a)002:2892: brjid pa che ba bdag dang yon bdag dang sems
NK030(a)002:2893: can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2895: rngams nyi shu ldan par bsam /
NK030(a)002:2897: dpal chen po la rngam nyi shu mnga' gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2898: sku phrag pa yangs pa rngoms /
NK030(a)002:2899: lung bstan pa rgya mtsho'i rngom /
NK030(a)002:2900: thugs chos nyid nam mkha'i rngom /
NK030(a)002:2901: snang ba thams cad ri rab ltar cir yang 'gyur ba'i gar stabs ltar rngom /
NK030(a)002:2902: zil gyis non pas khyad par du byung ba rngom /
NK030(a)002:2903: mtshams rngam stobs su zad par sdum pa'i zhal gyi rngom /
NK030(a)002:2904: cir yang 'gyur ba'i ljags skye shi rtsad gcod kyi rngam /
NK030(a)002:2905: go bar bsgrogs pa'i dbyangs ting 'dzin nam mkha'i skar tshogs ltar rngom /
NK030(a)002:2906: 'phrin las rgya mtsho'i rlabs ltar rngom /
NK030(a)002:2907: yon tan sa gzhi'i skye khrungs ltar rngom /
NK030(a)002:2908: gnas kyi 'phro 'du dur khrod ltar gnon pas zhing
NK030(a)002:2909: gi khyad par bla na med par rngom pa dang
NK030(a)002:2910: / spyod pa'i khyad par thams cad 'grub la me sbyor bas rngom pa dang /
NK030(a)002:2911: rngom nyi shu dbang bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2913: cho 'phrul nyi shu dang ldan par bsam la /
NK030(a)002:2919: thugs rje'i rang bzhin gyis dang /
NK030(a)002:2932: gang ltar mdzes pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK030(a)002:2934: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2935: e'i 'phro 'dus dpal gyi chas brgyad du bsam la /
NK030(a)002:2937: dpal chen po la zhal gsum gdangs pa'i zhal /
NK030(a)002:2946: de ltar chas brgyad kyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK030(a)002:2947: chas brgyad kyi dbang bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig  /
NK030(a)002:2948: 'dir khro bo'i smon lam cha lnga gdab /
NK030(a)002:2953: che ge mo'i tshogs kyi p+au tsa phul bas /
NK030(a)002:2954: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs yongs su rdzogs pas /
NK030(a)002:2955: bdag dang yon bdag dang sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2956: brgyad pa yon bdag gis me tog thogs la /
NK030(a)002:2957: gu rus g.yon du yungs dkar /
NK030(a)002:2959: na mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i ta th+aa thams cad
NK030(a)002:2960: kyis sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las zhing khams
NK030(a)002:2961: dag pa zad mi shes pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i
NK030(a)002:2963: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK030(a)002:2964: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyi 'dus pa chen po'i lha rnams la dbang bskur /
NK030(a)002:2967: thun mong gi p+au tsa lnga dbul /
NK030(a)002:2974: rol mo ye shes kyi p+au tsa 'bul /
NK030(a)002:2975: dbang gi chas brgyad kyis mnga' gsol /
NK030(a)002:2976: smon lam btab pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK030(a)002:2977: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams kyis /
NK030(a)002:2978: sku gsung thugs mnyes pa'i 'bras bu'i dbang /
NK030(a)002:2979: slob ma bdag cag dang khams gsum gyis sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:2983: sa ma ya tish+tha lhan zhes bzhugs su gsol bar bya'o /
NK030(a)002:2985: dgu pa yon bdag gis bskor ba bya /
NK030(a)002:2986: slob dpon gyis smon lam btab ste /
NK030(a)002:2987: ho chos nyid byang chub sems kyi bden pa dang /
NK030(a)002:2988: chos thams cad sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las mi zad pa brgyan gyis 'khor lo /
NK030(a)002:2989: sangs rgyas pa'i bden pa dang /
NK030(a)002:2990: de bzhin gshegs pa'i 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs rje chen po'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK030(a)002:2991: de ring slob ma che ge mos dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams bskyed nas /
NK030(a)002:2992: sku dang brgyan cha rdzogs par bzhes su gsol ba dang /
NK030(a)002:2993: yo byad phun gsum tshogs par bsags /
NK030(a)002:2994: sgo gsum dka' ba brdos te /
NK030(a)002:2995: rab gnas gzhung bzhin byas nas /
NK030(a)002:2996: brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba'i byin rlabs kyi yon bdag dang /
NK030(a)002:2999: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK030(a)002:3000: srid pa gsum gyi sems can thams cad /
NK030(a)002:3001: dkyil 'khor 'di dang nam yang mi 'bral zhing /
NK030(a)002:3002: de dag gi phung po dang khams dang skye mched thams cad dkyil 'khor 'di'i ngo bor gyur nas /
NK030(a)002:3003: lhun gyis grub par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:3005: bkra shis zhal spro bar bya'o //
NK030(a)002:3012: rgyun gyis ting nge 'dzin la gnas par bya'o //
NK030(a)002:3013: b+h+yo h+aum ka ra zhes khro bo yi ge brgya pas gshegs /
NK030(a)002:3016: 'dus pa mdo'i khro bo'i dbang gis skabs gnyis kar sbyar ro /
NK030(a)002:3017: spyi don bdun pa sbyin bsreg ni /
NK030(a)002:3018: gong zhi ba'i dbang bskur gi skabs su yod pa 'dir blangs la /
NK030(a)002:3019: sbyin bsreg lag len rgyas par byed do /
NK030(a)002:3020: mdo' dbang gi skabs su'ang sbyor /
NK030(a)002:3021: de bdun po gcig tu dril ba las /
NK030(a)002:3022: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa de song nas /
NK030(a)002:3023: gnyis pa 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa la gnyis ste /
NK030(a)002:3024: slob dpon 'jug cing dbang len pa dang /
NK030(a)002:3025: slob ma dkyil 'khor du bzhugs cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK030(a)002:3027: slob dpon dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa dang /
NK030(a)002:3031: kun byas dbyug rig pas 'jug ces gsungs pas /
NK030(a)002:3034: bcu gcig pa nas bla ma zhes bya ste /
NK030(a)002:3035: mtshan gsum dang ldan pa de nyid khrus byas la /
NK030(a)002:3036: chas gos lnga po kun dang ldan par byas la /
NK030(a)002:3037: dkyil 'khor gyis shar sgor gus pas 'dug la /
NK030(a)002:3038: dur khrod kyi me tog 'phreng bas snyim pa bkang zhing thugs kar thal mo sbyar nas /
NK030(a)002:3039: 'jigs byed chen po khro bo'i lha rnams mngon sum du byas nas /
NK030(a)002:3040: rigs pa'i me tog dor pa ni /
NK030(a)002:3041: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya h+aum zhes pa dang /
NK030(a)002:3042: khro la khros bas zhi mdzad pa /
NK030(a)002:3044: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK030(a)002:3047: de dkyil 'khor du me tog dor bas /
NK030(a)002:3048: lha rnams sngon gyis thugs dam rjes su dran pas /
NK030(a)002:3049: sku gsung thugs kyi gnas nas yi ge 'bru gsum gyi 'od 'phros te /
NK030(a)002:3050: bdag gis lus ngag yid gsum la thim pas /
NK030(a)002:3051: sgo tha mal du 'dzin pa'i rtog pa sbyangs nas /
NK030(a)002:3052: sku gsung thugs kyi gzi brjid dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK030(a)002:3053: de nas bzod par gsol te /
NK030(a)002:3054: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i /
NK030(a)002:3056: bdag gi slob ma bzhugs par bgyi /
NK030(a)002:3057: bzod pa mdzad de dgongs su gsol /
NK030(a)002:3058: zhes brjod de me tog blangs la dbu la bcings /
NK030(a)002:3059: lha dang bdag dbyer med par dgyes nas /
NK030(a)002:3061: slob ma dkyil 'khor du chug la /
NK030(a)002:3062: dbang bskur cig ces pa'i gnang bar thob par bsam pa ni /
NK030(a)002:3063: slob dpon bdag bcug pa ces bya'o //
NK030(a)002:3064: rgyas par spro na slob ma dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa bzhin 'jug go /
NK030(a)002:3065: gnyis pa dbang len pa ni /
NK030(a)002:3066: slob ma la dbang bskur ba bzhin phyi nang gsang gsum gyi dbang len no //
NK030(a)002:3067: gnyis pa slob ma dkyil 'khor du bzhug cing dbang bskur ba la gnyis ste /
NK030(a)002:3071: de nas slob ma bzhugs par bya /
NK030(a)002:3074: khrus dgab dri dang lus 'bul dang /
NK030(a)002:3077: de nyid dbog dang chu nan dang //
NK030(a)002:3078: bsgrags dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK030(a)002:3079: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang //
NK030(a)002:3080: spyan dbye dkyil 'khor legs bstan dang //
NK030(a)002:3081: tshogs mchod yon dang ces gsung pas //
NK030(a)002:3084: dri chus bkru bar gsungs kyang /
NK030(a)002:3086: las bum gyi chus slob ma rnams khrus dag par bya'o /
NK030(a)002:3087: gnyis pa gdong g.yogs bcing ba ni /
NK030(a)002:3088: ras sam dar dmar pos slob ma'i gdong bkab ste rin po che'i me tog gtad do //
NK030(a)002:3089: gsum pa ci la dga' dri ba ni /
NK030(a)002:3091: khyod ni 'dod pa ci lta bu /
NK030(a)002:3092: bu khyod dga' ba ci la dga' /
NK030(a)002:3096: bdag ni skal ldan bde chen la //
NK030(a)002:3097: rab dgyes 'phrul la bdag dga' ste //
NK030(a)002:3098: bla med byang chub bsgrub bya'i phyir //
NK030(a)002:3099: skal ba bzang po thob par 'tshal /
NK030(a)002:3101: de nas gral byed pa ni /
NK030(a)002:3102: slob ma mang na gu ru'i phyag gi rdo rje rtse mo /
NK030(a)002:3103: gral dang po'i slob bu'i lag du byin la /
NK030(a)002:3104: gzhan rnams lag pa gcig la gcig dril la drangs /
NK030(a)002:3105: nyung na re re nas drangs ste /
NK030(a)002:3106: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du /
NK030(a)002:3107: byang chub rdo rje'i lam la drangs nas ni /
NK030(a)002:3108: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dang dngos grub rnams /
NK030(a)002:3109: dwangs ba'i yid kyi rab tu blangs bar bgyi /
NK030(a)002:3111: goms pa gsum nang du bcug la /
NK030(a)002:3113: dbang stegs pad+ma 'dab brgyad pa re bri ba'am /
NK030(a)002:3114: bsgom pa'i steng du bzhag go /
NK030(a)002:3117: spyi bor thal mo sbyar la /
NK030(a)002:3118: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa rnams la lus 'bul bar bagyi'o //
NK030(a)002:3119: sarba b+hud+d+ha p+au tsa sas+tha na ya ad ma ni /
NK030(a)002:3122: thal mo smin mtshams su sbyar la /
NK030(a)002:3123: da ltar gyis sangs rgyas bla ma rnams la lus 'bul bar bagyi'o //
NK030(a)002:3124: a tsar+ya p+au tsa sas+tha na ya a ma nam /
NK030(a)002:3127: thal mo snying khar sbyar la /
NK030(a)002:3128: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad la lus 'bul bar bya'o //
NK030(a)002:3129: sa ga la sa ta pu tsa sas+tha /
NK030(a)002:3133: lnga pa bgegs bskrad pa ni /
NK030(a)002:3134: slob bu'i klad pa dung khang gi nang du /
NK030(a)002:3135: b+h+rum las gzhal yas khang zla kham /
NK030(a)002:3136: sgo gcig pa'i dbus su h+aum mthing skya /
NK030(a)002:3137: sgo khyud la h+aum ljang nag bsam /
NK030(a)002:3138: de las 'od 'phros pa snod bcud kun la khyab
NK030(a)002:3139: ste slar 'dus pas 'gra ba'i tshe bsod nams kyi
NK030(a)002:3140: bcud thams cad bsdus nas h+aum gnyis la thim 'od
NK030(a)002:3142: badz+ra kro ta h+aum ka ra h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:3143: ces zla gam gyi dbus su /
NK030(a)002:3145: h+aum ka ra sngo skya rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams pa bskyed /
NK030(a)002:3146: badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa la h+aum phata /
NK030(a)002:3148: mi g.yo mgon po ljang nag ral gri dang sdigs mdzub can bskyed la /
NK030(a)002:3149: khro bo gnyis 'od du zhu nas bu'i lus la thim pas /
NK030(a)002:3150: bskal pa'i bar du skye 'jigs med pa rdo rje lta bur gyur bar bsam mo //
NK030(a)002:3151: de nas gu rus yungs dkar gtor zhing /
NK030(a)002:3153: khro bo'i sprul pa grangs med pa spros pas /
NK030(a)002:3155: 'ur 'ur dang chem chem la sogs byung te /
NK030(a)002:3156: khams gsum thams cad khro bo'i sprul pas dbyings nas
NK030(a)002:3157: bgegs thams cad stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i pha
NK030(a)002:3160: phyogs mtshams thams cad khro bo dang rdo rje'i gur du gyur bar bsam mo /
NK030(a)002:3161: drug pa lhar bskyed pa ni /
NK030(a)002:3162: bu'i sems nyid h+aum ring po las /
NK030(a)002:3163: skad gcig gi dpal chen po he ru ka'i skur dran rdzogs su dkrongs kyi bskyed /
NK030(a)002:3164: de'i gnas gsum du +aahh+aum gsum la spros bsdus sku
NK030(a)002:3165: gsung thugs kyi rdo rje gsum du brlabs la gnas
NK030(a)002:3166: gsum du rdo rjes gtug go /
NK030(a)002:3167: bu'i sbyi bor ham ljang khu zhu ba las badz+ra
NK030(a)002:3168: karma rak+sha ham brjod pas rgya gram gyi go khrab
NK030(a)002:3169: kyis lus mgo mjug khyab par bsam la /
NK030(a)002:3170: de nas g.yas pa'i mdzub mo h+aum las /
NK030(a)002:3171: rdo rje gnod sbyin mthing nag mche zhags can dang /
NK030(a)002:3172: g.yon pa'i mdzub mo h+aum las /
NK030(a)002:3173: mi 'chi thal sbyor dmar po ral gri dang sdigs mdzub can bskyed la /
NK030(a)002:3174: badz+ra k+aa ba tsi rak+sha rak+sha h+aum h+aum /
NK030(a)002:3175: ces brjod cing 'dzub mo gnyis lte bar bsnol bas /
NK030(a)002:3176: khro bo gnyis zhabs phyir bltas ste rting pa sprad nas bzhugs par bsgom /
NK030(a)002:3177: de nas bcu drug mdor grangs pas /
NK030(a)002:3178: khro bo gnyis zhabs la rdo rje lu gu rgyud /
NK030(a)002:3179: bring gis byung nas gdams par bsam zhing /
NK030(a)002:3180: bcu drug mdo yang khro bo gnyis kyi bsrungs bar bsgoms /
NK030(a)002:3181: de bzhin du de nas snying kha dang /
NK030(a)002:3185: spyi gtsug dang bdun du bsrung ngo //
NK030(a)002:3186: de nas rdo rje lu gu rgyud g.yas g.yon nas
NK030(a)002:3187: cod pan gyi tshul du 'phyang pa'i sna la'ang khro
NK030(a)002:3188: bo gnyis kyi bar chad bsrung bar bsam mo //
NK030(a)002:3189: bdun pa dam tshig sbyin pa ni /
NK030(a)002:3191: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK030(a)002:3192: a la la ste mnyes par mdzod //
NK030(a)002:3193: a la la ste dam tshig bskongs /
NK030(a)002:3194: a la la ste dngos grub bstsol //
NK030(a)002:3195: dpal ldan rdo rje sku 'chang ba //
NK030(a)002:3196: mi phyed rdo rje sku rang bzhin //
NK030(a)002:3197: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas ni /
NK030(a)002:3198: rdo rje sku ru mdzad du gsol //
NK030(a)002:3200: dbang phyug gis ban d+har bdud rtsi cung zad blug la /
NK030(a)002:3202: sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin yig 'bru gsum gsal bar bsgom zhing /
NK030(a)002:3203: badz+ra a mri ta h+aum h+r+aih th+aa /
NK030(a)002:3204: lan gsum gyis bdud rtsir brlabs nas /
NK030(a)002:3205: phyag ga yas rdo rje dang bcas pa'i srin lag gi bdud rtsi gnas gsum du bzhag la /
NK030(a)002:3207: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig gsum du bsam la /
NK030(a)002:3208: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:3211: dpal ldan rdo rje gsung 'chang ba /
NK030(a)002:3212: mi phyed rdo rje gsung rang bzhin /
NK030(a)002:3213: deng bdag byin gyis rlabs nas ni //
NK030(a)002:3214: rdo rje'i gsung du mdzad du gsol //
NK030(a)002:3216: sarba ta th+aa ga ta wa ka badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham brjod /
NK030(a)002:3218: dpal ldan rdo rje thugs 'chang ba //
NK030(a)002:3219: mi phyed rdo rje thugs rang bzhi na //
NK030(a)002:3220: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas ni //
NK030(a)002:3221: rdo rje thugs su mdzad du gsol //
NK030(a)002:3223: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:3224: ces dam tshig thob par slob mas bsam mo /
NK030(a)002:3225: brgyad pa dam tshig 'bog pa ni /
NK030(a)002:3226: dbang phyug gis rdo rjes slob ma'i snying khar bzhag la /
NK030(a)002:3227: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba 'dis //
NK030(a)002:3228: dam nyams ma 'dres med pa la //
NK030(a)002:3229: nam yang smra bar ma byed cig /
NK030(a)002:3230: theg pa chen po ston byed pa'i /
NK030(a)002:3231: nga la brnyas dang smad mi rung //
NK030(a)002:3232: sku gsung thugs la rtags gnas shing //
NK030(a)002:3233: ma lus sems can don gyis shig /
NK030(a)002:3235: dgu pa chu nan bya ba ni /
NK030(a)002:3236: slob bu de gsang sngags la mi bzlog par rigs
NK030(a)002:3237: nges shing brtan par bya ba'i phyir nan tan bya
NK030(a)002:3239: dang po nyes skyon brjod pa'i chu nan bya ba ni /
NK030(a)002:3240: tsan+dana dkar dmar sbyar ba'i chu rdo rje gnod sbyin du bskyed la /
NK030(a)002:3241: badz+ra yak+sha h+aum zhes brgya rtsa brgyad dang bcas pas 'od du zhu bar bsam nas /
NK030(a)002:3242: thar lam 'dren pa'i bla ma dang //
NK030(a)002:3243: byang chub 'dren pa'i spun rnams la //
NK030(a)002:3244: sgo gsum zol med bskur ba dang //
NK030(a)002:3245: gsang ba'i yid kyis bsrung bya zhing //
NK030(a)002:3246: he ru ka la rtag gnas na //
NK030(a)002:3247: mtha' yas sems can bu bzhin skyongs //
NK030(a)002:3248: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyams sbyor ba'i //
NK030(a)002:3249: sdom pa la ni gang 'das pa //
NK030(a)002:3250: lha rnams dang ni mi rnams dang //
NK030(a)002:3251: bsgrub pa po dang rnal 'byor rnams //
NK030(a)002:3252: de kun 'khros nas khrag chen po //
NK030(a)002:3253: nyams pa'i snying nas drangs ste 'thung //
NK030(a)002:3254: sa ma ya i dan te na ra ka na /
NK030(a)002:3255: ces chu rdo rje blangs la /
NK030(a)002:3256: slob bu'i lce la lan gsum bzhag ste snying la thims pas /
NK030(a)002:3257: dam nyams na chu'i rdul phra rag thams cad h+aum du gyur pa las /
NK030(a)002:3258: khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin gyis rang bzhin lcags
NK030(a)002:3259: kyi sdig pa mgo dgu pa'i rnam pa grangs med
NK030(a)002:3260: par gyur nas / 'dir tshe srog gis bar chad byed la /
NK030(a)002:3261: phyi ma rdo rje dmyal bar skye bar byed pa'o //
NK030(a)002:3262: gnyis pa yon tan brjod pa'i chu nan ni /
NK030(a)002:3263: bdud rtsi sbyar ba'i chu he ru kar bskyed pa 'od du zhu bar bsam nas 'di skad du /
NK030(a)002:3264: de ltar bas na bu khyod kyis /
NK030(a)002:3265: dam tshig 'di rnams bsrungs bar gyis /
NK030(a)002:3266: dam tshig bsrungs na dngos grub pas /
NK030(a)002:3267: rdo rje bdud rtsi'i chu 'thung zhig /
NK030(a)002:3268: badz+ra u ta ga h+aum h+r+ai th+aa /
NK030(a)002:3269: ces rdo rje lce la lan gsum bzhag ste /
NK030(a)002:3271: dam ma nyams na chu de h+aum las ye shes sems dpar gyur nas /
NK030(a)002:3273: tshe gcig gis sangs rgyas par byed pa'o //
NK030(a)002:3274: bcu pa dam tshigs bsgrags ba ni /
NK030(a)002:3275: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i ye shes gang /
NK030(a)002:3276: ding 'dir dngos grub mchog du gsungs /
NK030(a)002:3277: dam tshig che ba'i chen po mchog /
NK030(a)002:3278: bye brag med pas deng nas spyod //
NK030(a)002:3279: dge dang mi dge'i chos rnams la //
NK030(a)002:3280: lhag par rten par mi bya ste //
NK030(a)002:3281: mnyam nyid rig pa'i klong zhugs nas //
NK030(a)002:3282: ci la'ang thog pa med par sbyod //
NK030(a)002:3283: zhes brjod cing de'i don legs par bshad do //
NK030(a)002:3284: bcu gcig pa me tog dor ba ni /
NK030(a)002:3285: bu rnams rim par dal gyi shar sgo nas thal
NK030(a)002:3286: mo sbyar ba'i bar du me tog khyad par can
NK030(a)002:3287: thogs la / dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du /
NK030(a)002:3288: gsang mchog rdzas kyi me tog dor nas kyang /
NK030(a)002:3289: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rnams /
NK030(a)002:3290: skal ldan rnal 'byor bdag cag rnams la stsol /
NK030(a)002:3293: gang la phog pa'i rigs kyi lhar bzung /
