NK030(a)002:5149: bu khyod bsgrol dang thabs lam 'di //
NK030(a)002:5150: rgyal ba yongs kyis sbas pa yin //
NK030(a)002:5151: thabs chen gsang ba'i theg pa ru //
NK030(a)002:5152: gtsang sbras 'ching ba sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK030(a)002:5153: dri sha chu yi bza' btung dang //
NK030(a)002:5154: nga yi b+ha ga'i ye shes bzhi /
NK030(a)002:5157: sems chu btung par khyod nus sam /
NK030(a)002:5161: bdag ni gang yang mi nus med //
NK030(a)002:5162: de dag bdag gis sbyad par bgyi //
NK030(a)002:5163: ci ltar sad phyir bdag la stsol //
NK030(a)002:5166: rig ma'i lag nas bzung ste /
NK030(a)002:5167: slob ma la gtod pa ni /
NK030(a)002:5168: skye med chos dbyings rig pa 'byung pa'i yum //
NK030(a)002:5169: mtshan ldan rig ma mchog gi brgyan //
NK030(a)002:5170: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med rol pa las //
NK030(a)002:5171: lhag pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor spro /
NK030(a)002:5173: / 'phags mchog bde bsgrub 'bras bu kun mnyes so //
NK030(a)002:5174: gnyis med don spyod chos nyid dag pa'i brgyan //
NK030(a)002:5175: dgyes pa'i ro mchog bde chen dbang thob shog /
NK030(a)002:5176: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa gu he pra dz+ny+aa shwa ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK030(a)002:5178: de nas 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis bde ba rgyas pa dang /
NK030(a)002:5179: bde ba dbab pa'i thabs gtum mo sbar ba dang /
NK030(a)002:5180: rtsa rlung thig le bsgom pa'i thabs rnams bslabs pa dang /
NK030(a)002:5181: sha chen gyi tshod ma dang /
NK030(a)002:5182: dri chen gyi bza' ba dang /
NK030(a)002:5184: nye'u shing gi khu ba btung ba dang /
NK030(a)002:5187: dri zhim pos byug la rgyan gyis brgyan /
NK030(a)002:5188: lus sems stong pa nyid las /
NK030(a)002:5189: khro mor bsgom gnas lngar khro mo lnga 'god /
NK030(a)002:5190: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi 'god /
NK030(a)002:5191: nam mkha' bam las pad+ma 'dab brgyad pa e mthing khas mtshan pa 'od dang ldan pa bskyed /
NK030(a)002:5192: slob bu bud+d+ha he ru kar bsgoms la /
NK030(a)002:5194: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi bskyed la /
NK030(a)002:5195: gsang ba h+aum las rdo rje dmar po rtse lnga
NK030(a)002:5196: pa bsgoms pa'i rwa la yab kyi 'bru lnga dang
NK030(a)002:5197: / dbus kyi rtsa gsum las 'bru gsum mdor phata sgom /
NK030(a)002:5198: dri zhim po sbrang gis sbyar ba'i ril bu mur zhing /
NK030(a)002:5199: pad+ma la bltas te yongs su rgyas nas /
NK030(a)002:5200: phyag rgya bzhis rol du gzhug /
NK030(a)002:5202: spyi bo nas 'khor lo bzhi la rim bzhin dbab cing /
NK030(a)002:5203: dga' ba bzhi'i ye shes bskyed la //
NK030(a)002:5204: rang rig ye shes kyi ngo bo /
NK030(a)002:5205: lhag pa byang chub sems kyi ngo bo rdo rje'i
NK030(a)002:5206: nor bu rtser phebs pa'i dus na gzung zhing bskyil
NK030(a)002:5207: ste / de yang rlung bum pa can gzung ba dang /
NK030(a)002:5208: yig 'bru'i sbyor bas gzung ba dang /
NK030(a)002:5209: lus kyi 'phrul 'khor gyis bzung ba la sogs pas /
NK030(a)002:5210: thig le bzung ba'i dus na gzung 'dzin gyi rtog
NK030(a)002:5211: pa thams cad dang bral ba'i lhan gcig skyes pa'i
NK030(a)002:5212: ye shes bde stong dbyer med kyi chos nyid 'od
NK030(a)002:5213: gsal dri ma med pa'i don /
NK030(a)002:5214: ci bzhin ye mnyam chen po'i dgongs pa gnyis med
NK030(a)002:5215: thig le nyag gcig gi rtogs pa ci lta ba
NK030(a)002:5216: bzhin nyams su myong zhing ngo shes par gyur to
NK030(a)002:5217: // gnyis ka'i lag pa nas gzung nas //
NK030(a)002:5218: bu khyod 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las //
NK030(a)002:5219: sgrol zhing thar nas skad cig gis //
NK030(a)002:5220: rdo rje nam mkha'i ye shes che //
NK030(a)002:5221: bla ma chen po'i sar gnas su //
NK030(a)002:5222: thams cad rigs kyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK030(a)002:5223: gcig pu sa bzung mnga' mnyes nas //
NK030(a)002:5224: bde khyab chen po'i 'phrin las las //
NK030(a)002:5225: khams gsum sras su bzung bar byos //
NK030(a)002:5229: rang byung gi ye shes 'char ba dang /
NK030(a)002:5231: bdun pa ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK030(a)002:5233: mngal gyis yi dwags su btung ba dang /
NK030(a)002:5234: mthar thug gi 'bras bu mi 'byung pa'o //
NK030(a)002:5235: gsum pa bde ba chen po'i dbang la'ang bdun las /
NK030(a)002:5237: don dam gyis shes bya sbyang ba dang /
NK030(a)002:5238: dug gis dug sbyang ba'i ched do //
NK030(a)002:5240: 'dod chags kyi ro bden pa gnyis med kyi ye
NK030(a)002:5241: shes rang la gnas pa thob bya nyid rgyu rkyen
NK030(a)002:5244: gnyis med kyi ye shes skye 'jig med kyi /
NK030(a)002:5245: gzung 'dzin spangs par rang bral bas /
NK030(a)002:5246: bde ba dang ldan pa zhes bya la /
NK030(a)002:5247: de gang la snang bas na /
NK030(a)002:5253: rten can dang rten med gnyis dang mtshon byed dang mtshon bya gnyis /
NK030(a)002:5255: dngos po lhan gcig skyes pa'i ye shes dang rang bzhin gyis gnyis su shes par bya'o //
NK030(a)002:5257: phyag rgya ma lo bcu gnyis ma bkug gcing khrus bya /
NK030(a)002:5259: bza' btung longs spyod man+dala dang bcas pa bla ma la 'bul /
NK030(a)002:5260: de nas ji ltar 'os pa'i yum la dbang bskur la sbyor ba bya ste /
NK030(a)002:5261: gzungs ma'i don dam pa'i lte ba na /
NK030(a)002:5262: zla ba tshes pa lta bu'i nang na byang chub
NK030(a)002:5263: sems kyi thig le dkar po yungs dkar tsam zhig
NK030(a)002:5264: rang bzhin gyis gnas pa la ting 'dzin gyis dmigs
NK030(a)002:5265: te gsang ba'i rdo rje ye shes kyi ro can
NK030(a)002:5266: dang / b+ha ga'i theg le dang /
NK030(a)002:5268: yab kyi lhag pa'i b+ho d+hi theg le dang mkha' la gnas pa de basre'o //
NK030(a)002:5270: pad+ma'i khyams na b+ho d+hi yod pa 'theb srin kyis blangs la /
NK030(a)002:5271: gzungs ma'i lce thog tu bskur ro //
NK030(a)002:5272: de nas yab yum gnyis ka sa //
NK030(a)002:5273: bdag bskyed khro ba'i dkyil 'khor snying po brjod la
NK030(a)002:5274: rdzogs pa'i tshul du lus dkyil bskyed sa man dzas
NK030(a)002:5275: snyan gsan dbab / e h+ya his sbyan drangs /
NK030(a)002:5276: dzah+aum bam hognyis su med par bstim la /
NK030(a)002:5277: mchod bstod bsnyen pa ci rigs pa bya /
NK030(a)002:5278: mdun bskyed kyang gong bzhin du bsnyen pa yan chad byas la /
NK030(a)002:5280: de nas slob bu'i gung mo g.yas pa dang gzungs ma'i gung mo g.yon rat+na phreng bas bcings te /
NK030(a)002:5281: de'i mdo nas slob dpon gyis bzung ste /
NK030(a)002:5282: bde ba chen po chos kyi sku //
NK030(a)002:5283: shes rab thabs kyi rdzogs par 'gyur /
NK030(a)002:5285: / 'di dang skye ba thams cad du //
NK030(a)002:5286: dngos grub gter bas 'di mi spongs /
NK030(a)002:5287: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK030(a)002:5288: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas khyod las byung //
NK030(a)002:5289: spangs na rdo rje dbyings phyug rtsal //
NK030(a)002:5290: dgug dang bsgom pa ma shes na //
NK030(a)002:5291: rdo rje bskal ba mtha' klas pa //
NK030(a)002:5292: chos sku thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK030(a)002:5293: de'i don rgyas par bshad do //
NK030(a)002:5295: dga' ba bzhi'i dbang gdam ngag 'bog ste /
NK030(a)002:5300: thog ma gzungs ma mthong bas bde ba g.yos pas dga' ba'o //
NK030(a)002:5301: de nas gzungs ma byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK030(a)002:5302: srin lag sbrel ba la sogs pa byas pas bde ba skyes pa mchog dga' 'o /
NK030(a)002:5304: / 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyi cha byed pa dga' bral lo //
NK030(a)002:5305: gzung ma dang rang lus rngul zhing bems kyis song ba ni /
NK030(a)002:5306: lhan gcig skyes pa'i dga' ba'o //
NK030(a)002:5308: rang dang gzung ma gnyis ka la 'khor lo bzhi sgoms te /
NK030(a)002:5309: bde ba chen po'i tsa kra ni dga' ba /
NK030(a)002:5310: longs spyod kyi tsa kra ni mchog dga' /
NK030(a)002:5312: sprul pa'i tsakra ni lhan skyes so //
NK030(a)002:5314: gu h+ya badz+ra rtsa ba ni dga' ba /
NK030(a)002:5315: rdo rje'i sked pa ni mchog dga' /
NK030(a)002:5316: rdo rje'i bum pa ni dga' bral /
NK030(a)002:5319: de rnams re re la yang /
NK030(a)002:5320: thig le bzhi bzhi rtsis pas bcu drug ste /
NK030(a)002:5323: bcu gsang ba'i sa bcur shes par bya'o //
NK030(a)002:5324: de ltar gdam ngag phog nas bus sbyor ba la snyoms par 'jug ste /
NK030(a)002:5325: rdo rje h+aum gcig bkod de spro bsdu la rdo rje rtse lnga pa gcig tu gyur /
NK030(a)002:5328: rtse mo'i bu gar phata nag po b+ha ga la phatahnaga po gcig bsam /
NK030(a)002:5329: de la spro bsdus pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa /
NK030(a)002:5330: de'i dbus su e mthing ga gru gsum pa de'i steng du h+aum dmar po gcig bsgoms /
NK030(a)002:5331: de nas gzungs ma la 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyi cha rnams bya /
NK030(a)002:5333: rdo rje phyed tsam pad+mara bsdams te /
NK030(a)002:5335: sra bas myong ba 'byung ba sa /
NK030(a)002:5336: rdul cung zad gsher ba chu /
NK030(a)002:5338: de nas shes pa zhib tu bltas pas bde ba g.yos pa rlung ngo //
NK030(a)002:5339: de nas bde ba bzlog ste /
NK030(a)002:5343: dang po ni bde ba g.yo ba tsam na /
NK030(a)002:5344: rdo rje e tsam gcig pha tshad la phyung la lto ba rgal tshig la sbyar /
NK030(a)002:5347: ting nge 'dzin gyis bzlog pa ni /
NK030(a)002:5348: bde ba g.yos tsam na bstod kyi dbugs bsdams la /
NK030(a)002:5349: ro rkyang gnyis kyis rtsa sna dbus gyi kun d+har 'brel nas yod pa'i /
NK030(a)002:5350: ro rkyang nas dbugs zhugs pa las /
NK030(a)002:5351: kun d+har lhags pa'i b+ho d+hi gyen la 'khyil gyis ldog nas dkar chil gyis ldog par bsam mo /
NK030(a)002:5353: rdo rje'i rtsa ba nas phar sor gnyis kyis thub tshad du mnan la ldog /
NK030(a)002:5354: sprul pa'i 'khor lo nas gyen la de ltar ldog /
NK030(a)002:5355: rdo rje'i rtsa ba nas sked pa dang /
NK030(a)002:5356: rtse mo nas rim par ldog /
NK030(a)002:5358: rdo rje'i rtsa bar dga' ba'i thig le bzhi'i theg le gsum pa nas /
NK030(a)002:5359: rdo rje sked ba'i mchog dag'i thig le gnyis pa ni /
NK030(a)002:5361: de rdo rje rtse mo lhan gcig skyes pa gnas su zla ba dang /
NK030(a)002:5362: nyi ma'i theg le rdo rje dang /
NK030(a)002:5363: pad+ma rang rang gi kha nas ma shor bar zin tsa na /
NK030(a)002:5364: rang rig pa'i don dam nyams su myong ba de kun tu 'od kyi sa'o //
NK030(a)002:5365: de'i dus su rgyu'i zung 'jug nyi zla 'dres pas /
NK030(a)002:5366: 'bras bu'i zung 'jug ye shes rang snang gi lha dang /
NK030(a)002:5367: lha mor snang bzhin du rang bzhin med pa'o //
NK030(a)002:5368: de tsam na zhen pa med pa pad+ma can gyi sa'o //
NK030(a)002:5369: de la smon lam gyi dbang gis gzugs sku gnyis 'byung ba ni /
NK030(a)002:5370: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa'o //
NK030(a)002:5371: de ni theg pa 'og ma dang sgo bstun pa'o //
NK030(a)002:5372: de nas rgyu 'bras ldog pa'i theg pa ni /
NK030(a)002:5373: nyi zla thig le rang gi gnas su rtse mo na tshur ldog pas //
NK030(a)002:5375: rdo rje'i rtsa bar phyin pa ni /
NK030(a)002:5377: de nas sprul pa'i tsa krar phyin pa ni pad+ma can no //
NK030(a)002:5378: thig le rang gnas su phyin pa la dgye /
NK030(a)002:5379: rang bzhin lhun grub gyi dkyil 'khor mthong ba ni /
NK030(a)002:5380: tshogs chen gyi sa mngon du byas pa yin no //
NK030(a)002:5381: gal te b+ho d+hi shor na /
NK030(a)002:5382: byang sems h'u dmar po sha rtag tu bsam la /
NK030(a)002:5383: mtheb srin gyis blang la khong du mid do //
NK030(a)002:5385: sbyor lam gyis mi rtogs pa'i bde ba skyes pa'i dus su /
NK030(a)002:5386: de la blo 'jog na gzungs ma mi dgos /
NK030(a)002:5387: mi rtag par blo gnas nas mi rtog pa sangs na yang dbang don de la blo gtad pas /
NK030(a)002:5389: de ltar sgom pa'i don la gnas par bya'o //
NK030(a)002:5391: pha rol tu phyin pa sngon du 'byin /
NK030(a)002:5393: bdun pa skyon ni de las bzlog pa nyid do //
NK030(a)002:5394: de ltar phyin nang zab mo'i dbang rnams la bye
NK030(a)002:5395: brag tu dbang gi rnams grangs sum cu so bdun
NK030(a)002:5397: de las mang ba 'dir sangs rgyas gsang bas ma bkral la /
NK030(a)002:5398: nyung na gzhung nas bshad pa'i dbang mi tshang ba'i phyir te /
NK030(a)002:5399: man ngag gi gzhung 'di nyid la legs par sbyad pas shes so //
NK030(a)002:5400: spyi don tha ma 'jug bsdu ba ni rjes kyi bya ba las /
NK030(a)002:5401: dang po dbang gi yon tan brjod pa ni /
NK030(a)002:5402: bla mas gsang bum phyag tu bzhes la 'di skad do //
NK030(a)002:5403: phyag rgya dbu rgyan snying po dang //
NK030(a)002:5404: gtso bo rus pa'i phreng ba dang //
NK030(a)002:5405: gzi mdangs rgyal mtshan zhing gi gdugs //
NK030(a)002:5407: lha dang phyag mtshan brgyan chas dang //
NK030(a)002:5408: sgrub rdzas gsang ba'i dbang gsum mo //
NK030(a)002:5411: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK030(a)002:5412: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK030(a)002:5413: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK030(a)002:5414: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK030(a)002:5415: na mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa
NK030(a)002:5416: thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las
NK030(a)002:5417: kyi zhing khams dag pa zad mi shes pa brgyan
NK030(a)002:5418: gyi 'khor lo'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK030(a)002:5419: 'jigs byed chen po khro bo'i lha tshogs rnams kyi bka' bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs gyis /
NK030(a)002:5420: bdag rdo rje che ge mos rigs kyi bu 'di
NK030(a)002:5421: rnams sgyu 'phrul dra ba khrag 'thung khro bo'i dbang
NK030(a)002:5422: lnga yongs su rdzogs par bskur bas /
NK030(a)002:5423: dus 'di nas bzung ste rgyal ba rnams kyi sras kyis dam par dgongs shing /
NK030(a)002:5424: ngan song gsum gyi duh kha thams cad dang bral nas /
NK030(a)002:5425: mtho ris bde ba thams cad dang ldan nas /
NK030(a)002:5426: thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa'i bdag po rgyal
NK030(a)002:5427: ba sku lnga'i go 'phang bsgrod de yi ge 'khor
NK030(a)002:5428: lo tshogs chen kyi sa la lhun gyis gnas par
NK030(a)002:5429: gyur cig / gzhan yang dbang bskur chen po 'di'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK030(a)002:5430: yul phyogs 'di dang rgyal khams thams cad du yang /
NK030(a)002:5431: dus kyi 'khrugs pa zhi ba dang /
NK030(a)002:5432: mtshon gyi bskal pa nyams pa dang /
NK030(a)002:5433: mi nad dang phyugs nad rgyun chad pa dang /
NK030(a)002:5434: char chu dus su phebs pa dang /
NK030(a)002:5435: lo phyug rtag tu legs te /
NK030(a)002:5436: sems cad thams cad bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK030(a)002:5438: de nas gnyis pa dbang bsab par bya ste /
NK030(a)002:5440: nam mkha' la bzhugs pa'i lha tshogs gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa thams cad 'od du zhu nas /
NK030(a)002:5441: rdo rje slob dpon bdag nyid la thim pas /
NK030(a)002:5442: sku gsung thugs kyi gzi byin bkrag dang gzi mdangs su ldan ste /
NK030(a)002:5443: sngon bas kyang mthu che bar bsam pa ni /
NK030(a)002:5444: dbang bsab zhes bya ba rdo rje slob dpon nyid la shin du gces pa yin no //
NK030(a)002:5445: de nas gsum pa smon lam gdab ste /
NK030(a)002:5446: slob dpon gyis khri las babs te /
NK030(a)002:5447: rdo rje dril bu thogs shing /
NK030(a)002:5448: yum gyis mar me thogs nas //
NK030(a)002:5449: mched lcam thams cad thal mo sbyar nas /
NK030(a)002:5452: bsam rdzogs lhun grub phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba dang //
NK030(a)002:5453: rgyal sras dpa' bo rnal 'byor kun gshegs pa'i //
NK030(a)002:5454: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK030(a)002:5455: lung dang man ngag zab mo kun bsdus pa //
NK030(a)002:5456: gsang sngags nang nas sgyu 'phrul dbang gi rigs //
NK030(a)002:5457: theg pa'i nang nas spyi blugs rgyal thabs te //
NK030(a)002:5458: yang gsang gter du spas ba'i man ngag 'dis /
NK030(a)002:5460: / 'gro ba kun gyis spyod yul ma yin yang //
NK030(a)002:5461: khams gsum 'khor ba'i duh kha brtsad gcad phyir //
NK030(a)002:5462: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dbang bskur bas //
NK030(a)002:5463: blo sbyangs skal bar ldan pa'i bu rnams kyis //
NK030(a)002:5464: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi don rtogs shog /
NK030(a)002:5465: gzhan yang sku dang gsung thugs yon tan las /
NK030(a)002:5466: ngo mtshar rmad byung 'bras bu ci snyed pa /
NK030(a)002:5467: thabs shes 'gro don lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK030(a)002:5468: ces dril bu gsil zhing me tog dor la /
NK030(a)002:5469: ru lu gar gyis dkyil 'khor lan gsum bskor ro //
NK030(a)002:5470: de nas bzhi pa bslab bya brjod de /
NK030(a)002:5471: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyis //
NK030(a)002:5472: he ru ka ni nga yin gyis //
NK030(a)002:5473: nga yis 'di skad bgo ba bzhin //
NK030(a)002:5474: bu khyod kyis ni bya dgos so //
NK030(a)002:5478: bslabs bya thams cad nan chags su bya'o //
NK030(a)002:5479: de nas lnga pa gtor ma btang par bya ste /
NK030(a)002:5480: gtor ma rnams cha gsum du gcad la /
NK030(a)002:5482: chos kyi dbyings kyi gtor ma zhes bya ste /
NK030(a)002:5483: gter du sba ba'i cho ga bya /
NK030(a)002:5484: bar pa de ye shes rol ba'i gtor ma zhes bya ste /
NK030(a)002:5486: tha ma de thugs rje sprul pa'i gtor ma zhes bya ste /
NK030(a)002:5487: las mkhan gyi mkha' 'gro chos skyong thams cad mchod /
NK030(a)002:5490: nang du las bzhi'i bro bya'o //
NK030(a)002:5491: de nas drug pa bkra shis gsol te /
NK030(a)002:5492: dkar tshal btegs la me tog dor zhing /
NK030(a)002:5493: bkra shis kyi cho ga rgyas par bya'o //
NK030(a)002:5495: bla ma la btang rag btang zhing //
NK030(a)002:5496: bu rnams kyis phyag 'tshal zhing zhabs la sbyi bos gtug go /
NK030(a)002:5497: de nas brgyad pa dkyil 'khor bsdu /
NK030(a)002:5500: bum chu lhag mas mched lcam rnams khrus bya /
NK030(a)002:5501: dkyil 'khor zhabs bsil rdul tshon sman ma dang /
NK030(a)002:5503: sbyin bsreg gi thal ba rnams chu bo chen po la bskyal /
NK030(a)002:5505: de nas dgu pa bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo'o /
NK030(a)002:5506: spyod lam thams cad lha dang ma bral bar bya ste /
NK030(a)002:5510: longs spyod dus bzhir nyams blangs tshe //
NK030(a)002:5511: rig phyir thams cad dkyil 'khor lhar //
NK030(a)002:5512: gsal byas tha snyad zhen las grol /
NK030(a)002:5514: sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i dbang gi them skas rdzogs so //
NK030(a)002:5515: de ltar sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i dbang rdzogs nas /
NK030(a)002:5516: lha dbang de dag chags par byed pa'i rten du lha sgom pa dang /
NK030(a)002:5517: man ngag bsgom pa gnyis las /
NK030(a)002:5519: sngar me tog phog pa'i lha gang yin pa de /
NK030(a)002:5521: de'i rjes su snying po rjes gnang byin pas gsungs ngo sprad /
NK030(a)002:5522: dbang rdzas mgo thog tu bzhag nas dbang bskur bas /
NK030(a)002:5524: de yang thog ma nas yin pa la yin pa ltar ngo sprad zhes pa ni /
NK030(a)002:5525: gser sprang ngo shes pa lta bu ste /
NK030(a)002:5526: de ni lha ngo sprad pa'o //
NK030(a)002:5527: de nas nye bar mtshon nas /
NK030(a)002:5528: snang grags thams cad lha dang gzhal yas khang gi
NK030(a)002:5529: dkyil 'khor du longs spyod pa ni lam du 'khyer
NK030(a)002:5530: ba'o // lhar snang ba thams cad sems nyid du thag chod pa ni lha la lhar rol ba'o //
NK030(a)002:5531: thams cad lha'i rang bzhin du blta ba'o //
NK030(a)002:5532: de'i ngang la gnas pa bsgom pa /
NK030(a)002:5533: spyod lam rnam bzhi lha dang mi 'bral ba ni spyod pa'o //
NK030(a)002:5534: de las mi 'da' ba ni dam bca' /
NK030(a)002:5537: glang po che rgun chang gis myos pa lta bu'o //
NK030(a)002:5538: thad ka ni ngang sgom chung ngu'i thad kar slob ste /
NK030(a)002:5539: de yang bdag cag lhar gsal ba'i spyi bor thig le dmar po sran ma tsam gcig bsgoms /
NK030(a)002:5540: de nas khru gang gis mtho bar thig le dkar po sran ma tsam gcig bsgoms /
NK030(a)002:5541: de nas sna bug g.yon nas 'od dmar po sran ma tsam gcig byung nas /
NK030(a)002:5542: spyi bo'i thig le dmar po la phog pas /
NK030(a)002:5543: des bdag rkyen byas nas thig le dmar po las 'od 'phros pas /
NK030(a)002:5545: byang chub sems dpa' la phog pas thugs mnyes pa'i mchod pa phul /
NK030(a)002:5546: 'od de tshur 'dus theg le dmar po la thim pas //
NK030(a)002:5547: thig le 'od du zhu bar bsam yang sna bug g.yon nas 'od dkar por byung nas /
NK030(a)002:5548: gong gi thig le dkar po la phog pas /
NK030(a)002:5550: de bzhin gshegs pa la phog pas thugs mnyes tshur 'dus /
NK030(a)002:5551: thig le dkar po la thim /
NK030(a)002:5552: de babs nas dmar po la thim pas /
NK030(a)002:5553: snying kha snying gi dkyil du thim pas /
NK030(a)002:5554: dkar dmar 'dres nas spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu ga nas mar thim /
NK030(a)002:5555: de nyid snying gi dkyil du dkar dmar 'dres pa'i
NK030(a)002:5556: ngo bo bde stong gnyis med kyi ngang la blo
NK030(a)002:5557: skyur bzhag go / de ni lha bsgoms pa'i man ngag ces bya'o //
NK030(a)002:5558: man ngag bsgom pa la steng sgo dang 'og sgo gnyis las /
NK030(a)002:5559: dang po ni ngang sgoms 'bring po'i thad kar sleb ste /
NK030(a)002:5560: rang gi lus rkyal stong sang nge ba'i nang na /
NK030(a)002:5561: rtsa a wa d+hu ti sbom phra mda' snyug tsam phyi dmar la nang dkar ba /
NK030(a)002:5562: yar sna rtse'u chung la thug pa /
NK030(a)002:5563: mar sna gnyer mo che la thug pa de ni srog shing yin /
NK030(a)002:5564: sgrom mdo'i 'khor lo dang 'og sgo rlung gi 'khor lo la gnyis khri 'phangs yin no //
NK030(a)002:5565: lte ba bang rim snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo bum pa mgrin pa longs spyod chos 'khor /
NK030(a)002:5567: lus mchod rten chen po gcig tu bsgom /
NK030(a)002:5568: de spyi bor srog mi shig pa'i thig le /
NK030(a)002:5569: ham gyi rang bzhin sran ma tsam gcig gnas pa las 'od phyogs bcur 'phros pas /
NK030(a)002:5571: sems can gyi don byas tshur 'dus gong gi yig ge ham gyi theg le la phog pas /
NK030(a)002:5573: rang gi rtsa ba'i bla ma ni mchod rten gyi tog gi tshul du bzhugs par bsgom /
NK030(a)002:5574: de la shes pa bcug bas bla ma yang 'od du zhu nas /
NK030(a)002:5575: spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu ga nas rang gi snying gi dkyil du /
NK030(a)002:5576: rang gi shes pa dang 'dres pa la blo skyur la bzhag go /
NK030(a)002:5577: da 'og sgo bde ba sgom pa ni /
NK030(a)002:5578: yang rang gi sbyi bor thig le dmar po sran ma tsam gcig bsgom /
NK030(a)002:5579: de las mda' gang gis mtho bar theg le dkar po sran ma tsam gcig sgom /
NK030(a)002:5580: dmar po de shes rab kyi cha yin la /
NK030(a)002:5581: dkar po thabs kyi cha yin no //
NK030(a)002:5582: de nas thig le dmar po de la shes pa bcug pas /
NK030(a)002:5583: chags pa'i rang bzhin yin pas 'dar bar bsgom /
NK030(a)002:5584: de 'dar bas bdag rkyen byas nas theg le dkar po'ang 'dar ste /
NK030(a)002:5585: mar la de babs nas dmar po la thim pas /
NK030(a)002:5586: dkar dmar dbyer med du 'dres nas /
NK030(a)002:5587: spyi gtsug nas mar thim pas /
NK030(a)002:5588: snying gi dkyil du bde stong dbyer med du blo skyur la bzhag go /
NK030(a)002:5589: de dag ma h+aa yo ga'i dbang gi man ngag sgom 'debs yin no //
NK030(a)002:5590: ma h+aa yo ga'i dbang gi them skas rdzogs so //
NK030(a)002:5591: su pra tish+tha badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
